K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:1b-0: @1b #// 'phags pa don yod pa'i zhags pa'i cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:1b-2: bsod nams kyi phung po chen po'i dge ba'i rtsa ba bsags par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:1b-3: rtag tu 'jig rten dbang phyug rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:1b-4: rtag tu phyag g-yas pa byang chub sems dpa' de'i spyi bo la 'jog par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2a-2: rtag tu zhal mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2a-4: yon tan chen po brjod pa'i gzungs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2a-8: mchog tu dkon pa yin no; ;gzungs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2a-9: dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga 'di thos pa tsam dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2a-10: rna ba'i bu gar 'di'i sgra lan bdun nges par lhung na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2a-12: bsam pa tsam gyis bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su skye bar 'gyur te; 'od dpag med kyi spyan sngar zhabs kyi drung du padma las brdzus te skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-0: rgyan thams cad kyis rnam @2b par brgyan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsungs pa'i mdo sde dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-4: phyag rgya rnams kha ton du kun tu gnas shing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-5: tshe rabs dran par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-6: dbang po drug yongs su dag pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-7: mngon par shes pa lnga yang so sor thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-8: tsam la rab tu skye bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-12: dbyibs yongs su dag pa de'i phyir stobs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-13: brtson 'grus kyis sems can thams cad sna tshogs 'dzin pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-17: ser sna'i dri ma dang bral ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-18: phrag dog dang bral bar bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-19: sems can thams cad byams pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:2b-20: snying rje la sogs pa mchog dang yang dag par ldan pas bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3a-5: phyi ma'i tshe ma yin par phul du byung ba'i don la brtson par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3a-7: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sgrub thabs kyi cho ga 'di ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3a-8: bla na med pa zhes bgyi'o; ;mang du smos ci 'tshal te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3a-9: de la 'gran sems kyis kyang mnyan par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3a-11: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis gzungs 'di gsungs pa'i de ma thag tu skad cig thang gcig yud tsam gyis po ta la'i ri bo 'di rin po che sna bdun gyi rang bzhin du gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3a-12: me tog gi shing ljon pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3a-13: 'bras bu'i shing ljon pa gang yin pa rnams kyang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3a-14: rin po che sna bdun gyi rang bzhin gyi khang pa brtsegs par rab tu gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-0: gang+g'a'i klung gi @3b bye ma bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag rnams 'bum phrag bye ba dgu bcu rtsa dgu'i rdul phra rab dang mnyam par rab tu gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-1: lha rdzas kyi me tog dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-2: 'bras bu rnam par bkra ba rnam pa sna tshogs pa rnams pham par byas pa'i rgyan rnam par bkra bas rnam par bkra zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-3: dril bu g-yer ka'i dra ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-4: gser gyi dril bu 'khrol ba'i bla res dpyangs pa rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-5: lha rdzas kyi seng+ge'i khri yongs su bshams pa rnams kyang re re zhing khang pa brtsegs pa'i dbus na seng+ge'i khri bshams pa brgya stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa dgur rab tu byung bar gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-6: seng+ge'i khri thams cad la phyogs bcu nas de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag par byon te bzhugs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-7: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyang phyag gser gyi kha dog can brkyang nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi spyi bo'i gtsug tu phyag 'jog par mdzad cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-8: legs so zhes bya ba'i sgra brjod par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-10: legs so legs so mchog tu khyad par du 'phags pa'i 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam chen por rab tu bstan pas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:3b-11: sems can thams cad pha rol tu 'gro bar byed pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-0: gang gis thos pa tsam gyis 'jig rten las 'das pa so sor @4a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-1: khyad par du 'phags pa'i sangs rgyas nyid kyi lam tshol ba la rjes su 'gro'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-6: 'jug pa ches mang ba'i dbang du byas pa'i sems can rnams dam tshig la rjes su 'jug par gyur pa de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-7: skye ba 'di nyid la de bzhin gshegs pa'i lus su rig par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-8: de nas po ta la'i gnas kyi ri bo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-12: nags de rnams thams cad la mi gang tsam du mtho ba nyid dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-13: shing rta'i 'khor lo'i tshad tsam pa'i rin po che sna bdun gyi rang bzhin can gyi padma rnams rab tu byung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-14: 'dab ma kha dog sna tshogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-16: 'dzam bu chu bo'i gser gyi kha dog ltar dmar ba'i mu tig gi ze'u 'bru dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-17: lha rdzas kyi mu tig gi ge sar gyi khor yug tu bskor ba gang yin pa la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams bzhugs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-18: byang chub sems dpa' de rnams thams cad kyang chos la gus pas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4a-19: thams cad pus mo btsugs te gzungs 'di'i dkyil 'khor dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-0: phyag rgya mthong ba'i don du mu tig gi do shal brgya stong ri ba byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs @4b dbang phyug la mngon par bkab par gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-1: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams rdo rje'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa 'di yang ches cher g-yos par gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-2: lha'i me tog gi char chen po mang po rab tu phab ste de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mchod pa'i don dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-3: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad mchod pa'i don dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-4: gzungs 'di'i dkyil 'khor dam pa la mchod pa'i don du char rab tu phab bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-5: de nas yang gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po lag na rdo rjes bzhin 'dzum zhing rdo rje bskor bzhin du bcom ldan 'das gang na ba der dong ste lhags nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs gnyis la mgo bos phyag 'tshal te bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-7: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gzungs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga 'di ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-8: shin tu rnyed par dka' ba ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-9: 'di lta bu'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-11: de bzhin gshegs pa bskyed pa blta bar bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-12: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar blta bar bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-13: de bzhin gshegs pa dang mnyam pa nyid du blta bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:4b-15: mthu chen po 'di 'dzam bu'i gling na mchog tu dkon par blta bar bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-0: phyi ma'i dus phyi ma'i tshe na @5a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-1: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-2: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-3: gang gis thos pa tsam gyis 'di lta bu'i yon tan dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-4: phan yon so sor thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-5: kun tu snang bar byed par 'gyur ba 'di nyid ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-6: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug ma gtogs par sems can thams cad kyi nang na gzhan su yang ma mchis so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-9: ji skad smras pa de de bzhin no; ;lag na rdo rje /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-10: 'dzam bu'i gling pa'i sems can thams cad ma dang phar gyur pa 'di /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-12: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug 'di sems can thams cad kyi re ba skong ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-15: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dpung gnyen byed pa nas ji srid bud med dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5a-18: bu mo sems can thams cad sangs rgyas nyid kyi bdag nyid kyi bar la rab tu 'god par byed do; ;de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi stobs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5b-0: pha rol gnon pas @5b sngon sems can rnams la phan pa'i don du zhugs pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5b-1: de nas gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po lag na rdo rje nyi ma'i 'od zer gyi snying po dri ma med pa zhes bya ba'i nor bu rin po che chen po thogs nas byang chub sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gang na ba der dong ste lhags nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi zhabs gnyis la mgo bos phyag 'tshal nas nor bu rin po che chen po de yang mngon par dga' bar phul lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5b-2: lha rdzas kyi me tog sna tshogs pas gcal du bkram pa mchod pa'i don du rab tu bkod nas rang gi stan la 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5b-3: de nas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pa don yod pa dri ma med cing rnam par dag pa rab tu gsal ba'i 'od zer zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5b-4: bcom ldan 'das ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs pa gang gis spyi bo'i gtsug tu gdugs kyi rnam pa'i khang pa brtsegs pa kun tu gnas par gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:5b-5: khang pa brtsegs pa de las kyang 'od zer rnam pa sna tshogs pa byung ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-0: 'od zer sna tshogs pa'i snang ba des kyang nam mkha'i mthil du rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam par 'phrul pa @6a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-2: cho 'phrul chen po sna tshogs pa bstan to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-3: 'od zer gyi snang ba re res kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa dgu rab tu bstan to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-4: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku de rnams thams cad kyis kyang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la legs so zhes bya ba byin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-6: mchog tu rnyed par dka' ba'i gzungs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-7: phyag rgya 'di bshad pa 'di legs so legs so; ;'jig rten las 'das pa shin tu khyad par du 'phags pa'i byang chub kyi snying por 'gro bar byed pa'i lam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-8: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar byed pa'i lam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-9: chos kyi rnam 'phrul 'bar bar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-10: chos kyi rgyal mtshan bsgreng bar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-11: chos kyi dung 'bud par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-12: bdud bzhi'i dkyil 'khor las rnam par rgyal bar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-13: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcus gnon par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-14: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad rab tu rdzogs par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-15: mi 'jigs pa bzhis gnon par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-16: de bzhin nyid dang yang dag pa'i mtha' pha rol gnon par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-17: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu rab tu rdzogs par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6a-19: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad sgom par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-0: 'di @6b ni; lam rab tu nyams pa rnams kyi lam du chags par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-1: bsam pa rab tu nyams pa rnams kyi bsam pa yongs su dag pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-2: ngan song du 'gro bar rgyu ba rnams kyi bde 'gro'i lam du 'gro bar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-4: byang chub chen po'i sa bon dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-5: 'bras bu rab tu ston par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-6: de nas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa sh'akya thub pas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-7: byang chub sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-9: 'jig rten las 'das pa khyad par du 'phags pa rnam par thar pa'i dkyil 'khor don yod pa'i zhags pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi nye bar spyod pa'i cho ga shod cig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-10: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan snga nas bskul ba thob nas bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'jig rten las 'das pa'i cho ga dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-11: dkyil 'khor gyi nye bar spyod pa'i cho ga dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-13: gnas bzang sa gzhi dge ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-14: sa gzhi gtsang zhing ne'u gsing la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-15: ljon shing me tog 'bras bus khyab //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-17: sa gzhi mnyen la dag pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-18: gang du chu bo 'bab ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:6b-19: gzi brjid ldan zhing yid dga' ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-2: yid kyi shing rta rgyas byed cing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-3: go skabs legs par gnas pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-4: shin tu dag cing thun tshags bral //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-5: rus pa gseg ma gyo mo dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-6: phub ma sol ba yongs su spangs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-7: gtsang zhing gtsang la legs dag pa'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-8: sa gzhi yongs su zlum pa der //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-9: mkhas pas rgyar ni gzings tshad du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-10: gzhal nas shin tu rnam 'byes shing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-11: gtsang zhing mnyan la 'jam par phye //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-12: gnas der dkyil 'khor legs par bsgrubs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-13: sangs rgyas byang chub bla na med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-15: de bzhin gshegs kun gyis byin brlabs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-16: sa yi cha las dbangs su ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-17: mi gang tshad du brko bar bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-19: yang na gur gum kha dog dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-20: sa rdul dkar po snum pa ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-22: sa yi khyad par dbye ba de //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-23: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyis bsngags //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-24: byang chub snying po sa der mtshungs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-25: ring bsrel bzhugs pa'i mchod rten dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-26: de ni mtshungs par gyur pa yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-27: brkos pa'i nang du mkhas pa yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-28: slar yang sa de dgang bar bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-29: ji srid dong bu mnyam par gang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-30: de ni dkyil 'khor yang dag pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-31: nyung dang lhag pa bsngags pa min //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7a-33: khru ni sum cu rtsa gnyis tshad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-0: mkhas pas dkyil 'khor thig dag @7b gdab; ;yang na khru ni bcu drug dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-1: yang na khru ni bco lngar bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-2: mnyam zhing grva bzhir legs par dbye //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-3: ba yi lci ba dag dang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-4: sa dang bsres te bsku bya ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-5: shin tu zhen par bsdig pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-6: 'jam zhing mnyan par bya ba yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-7: de la dkyil 'khor thig gdab pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-8: sna tshogs tshon gyis kun tu dbye //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-9: sgo bzhi rnam par 'byes pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-10: rta babs bzhi dang ldan par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-11: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi snying po ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-12: rnam par phye ste gru bzhi tshad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-13: khru gsum yang na khru bzhi ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-14: thig skud tshon gyis rnam par dbye //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:7b-21: phyi yi thig gi tshad dag tu //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8a-3: 'od dpag med pa'i mdun du ni //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8a-5: btud de thal mo sbyor ba dang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8a-17: lha mo sgrol ma rnam par brgyan //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8a-21: lha mo dkar mo rnam par brgyan //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8a-28: nub tu pho nya bzhin sgyur ma //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8a-29: g-yas phyogs su ni bzhin sgyur ma //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8a-31: byang du srin mo khro gnyer gdong //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8a-32: kun kyang me dbus 'jigs pa med //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-2: kun tu 'bar ba phreng bar bcas //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-6: tshangs pa khyab 'jug gshin rje dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-7: chu lha dbang po lus ngan po //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-8: dbang sgyur dga' ldan gnas dag gi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-9: lha nas 'og min gnas kyi bar //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-11: sum cu rtsa gsum lha rnams dang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-16: zhags pa dang ni dgra sta dang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-19: ngos la dbyug pa tho ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-21: 'khor lo dung dang ga d'a dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-22: ral gri dang ni to ma ram//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-23: bum pa gang ba dag dang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-24: mi snang ba yi 'bag sha dang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-29: nor bu rdo rje dag dang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-30: dgra sta rdo rje dag dang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-31: phyag rgya bzhi dang dga' ba 'khyil //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-32: bya ba bum dang kun di dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-33: ril ba bhring+ka ri dang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-34: ri dvags ae na'i pags pa dang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-36: steng du rgyu skar bcas pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:8b-37: zla ba nyi ma de bzhin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-2: so so cha ni dbye bar bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-3: mkhas pas shar gyi sgor bri ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-5: lag na rdo rje 'jigs pa med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-7: ki li ki la gtum po che //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-8: lho phyogs kyi ni sgo ru gzhag /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-10: mthong na 'jigs su rung ba yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-11: byang du nges par gnod mdzes bya //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-16: sgo srung ba dag bri ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-17: nor bu bzang dang gang ba bzang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-18: stobs kyi lha dang lngas rtsen yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-19: sgo yi gnas kyi bar dag tu //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-29: gtum mo dang ni me tog so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9a-30: de dag bri bar bya ba yin //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9b-20: kun tu gser gyi srad bu dang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9b-24: dngul gyi snod ni bzhi gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9b-25: dngul gyi bum pa gang ba bzhi la dngul dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9b-27: zangs las byas pa'i me tog gis spras pa'i mgo lcogs kyis spras pa gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9b-28: gser gyi bum pa bzhi bzhag pa la mu tig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:9b-35: me tog gis spras pa'i mgo lcogs gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-1: lha rdzas kyi tsandan gyi phye mas gser gyi snod bkang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-2: dngul gyi snod kyi nang du gser gyi me tog dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-5: rin po che sna tshogs pas spras pa gzhag par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-6: cod pan gyi rgyal mtshan bzhi gzhag par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-7: rin po che'i rgyal mtshan bzhi gzhag par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-9: dar dmar po dpyang bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-10: dngul gyi pog phor bzhi bzhag ste tsandan dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-13: gur gum gyi bdug pas bdug par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-14: sa las byas pa'i bum pa gser gyis g-yogs pa'i nang du dri chab rnam pa sna tshogs kyis bkang ste rin po che sna bdun dang ldan par bgyis la bkang ba la dar gyis bcings la rgyan rnam pa sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa'i steng du zangs las byas pa'i me tog gzhag nas snying po'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du padma'i steng du gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-15: de nas phyi rol gyi dkyil 'khor thog thag tu dri dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-19: 'bras bu la sogs pa rnam pa sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-20: mchod yon gyi chab kyis dngul gyi snod dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10a-21: zangs kyi snod bkang ba drug cu rtsa bzhi gzhag par bya'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-3: bdug pa sna tshogs kyis bdug par bya'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-5: sna ma'i me tog gis gdu bu'i steng du mda' la ba dan btags pa drug cu rtsa bzhi btsugs te tshon sna tshogs kyis bkra bar byas pa'i mda' dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-6: nor bu'i phreng ba rnam pa sna tshogs kyis dkyil 'khor brgyan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-7: de nas phyi rol gyi dkyil 'khor thog thag tu sa dang bsres pa'i ba'i lci bas dkyil 'khor byas la dri chab kyis bskus te tshon sna lnga'i srad bus thig btab la sgo bzhi rnam par phye ste seng ldeng gi phur bu tshad sor bcu gnyis pa drug cu rtsa bzhi gdab bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-8: tshon sna lnga'i srad bus dkyil 'khor kun tu bskor bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-11: bya ma bum drug cu rtsa bzhi'i gtor ma sna tshogs kyis bkang ba bzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-12: kham phor zlum po drug cu rtsa bzhi gtor ma sna tshogs kyis bkang ba gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-13: gtor ma tshul sna tshogs pa drug cu rtsa bzhi so sor gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-14: snod tshon sna lnga pa drug cu rtsa bzhi kha zas rnam pa sna tshogs kyis bkang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-15: bca' ba rnam pa sna tshogs blugs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:10b-16: gtor ma dkar po rnam pa sna tshogs gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-0: yo byad thams cad kyis yongs su gang ba ro rnam pa sna tshogs kyi @11a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-3: me tog sna tshogs dgram mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-4: phreng ba brgya nyi shu rtsa gcig dkyil 'khor du dpyang bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-5: byang phyogs kyi dkyil 'khor la drug cu rtsa bzhi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-6: snying po'i dkyil 'khor la sum cu rtsa gnyis gdags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-7: me mar gyi sdong bu bzhi bud par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-8: gtor ma brgya drug cu rtsa bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-9: dkyil 'khor thog thag tu mar me bud par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-16: la phug spangs pa'i gtor ma gzhan rnam pa sna tshogs gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-17: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi'i grva bzhir don yod pa'i zhags pa'i mdo sde bklag par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-18: sgo re rer bcom ldan 'das ma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bklag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-19: chos klog pa legs par khrus byas te lha rdzas kyi gos kyis dkris te gtsang ma la dri rnam pa sna tshogs kyis bsgos pa'i gos gtsang ma gsar pa bgos te chos kyi stan shin tu brgyan pa lha rdzas kyi stan la 'dug nas tshig 'jam po tshig mnyen pos bklag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-20: nub kyi phyogs cha la dkyil 'khor mthon po la bde ba can gyi bkod pa bris pa 'od dpag med dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11a-21: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang phyug dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-0: mthu chen thob pa'i gzugs bris pa'i ras kyi sku @11b gzugs dkyil 'khor la mngon du phyogs par gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-1: shar gyi phyogs cha la dkyil 'khor gru bzhi mthon po byas la rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor la sh'akya thub pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-3: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i khro bo'i gzugs bris pa ras kyi sku gzugs dkyil 'khor la mngon du phyogs par gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-4: lho'i phyogs cha la ri 'dra ba'i gnas mthon po byas la de bzhin gshegs pa 'jig rten dbang phyug rgyal po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-6: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-7: don yod pa'i zhags pa ras la bris pa'i dkyil 'khor la mngon du phyogs par gzhag go //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-8: byang gi phyogs cha la khro bo'i rgyal po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-9: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-11: sa'i snying po bris pa'i ras kyi sku gzugs dkyil 'khor la mngon du phyogs par gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-12: stegs bu'i rnam par mthon por byas pa thams cad legs par brgyan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-13: dar gyi phreng bas brgyan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-14: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-15: bum pa gang ba bzhag pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:11b-17: ro'i mchog rnam pa sna tshogs bza' ba'i ngo bo rnam pa du ma'i kha zas kyi ro dbul ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-0: 'bras bu rnam pa sna tshogs dang ldan pa'i bsod @12a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-7: gur gum dang bsres pa'i bdug pa ras kyi sku gzugs la dbul bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-8: de nas rig sngags 'chang bas dus gsum du khrus bya zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-9: gos lan gsum brjes te dus gsum du bzlas brjod dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-11: tshes brgyad nas brtsams te tshes bco lnga tshang gi bar du don yod pa'i zhags pa lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-12: khro bo'i rgyal po lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-13: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i lcags kyu nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-14: don yod pa rnam par lta ba'i zhags pa'i snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-15: 'jig rten las 'das pa rnam par 'phrul pa lan nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-16: rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis phyag byas pa stong rtsa brgyad bzlas brjod bya ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-17: rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi zhags pa'i snying po stong rtsa brgyad bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-18: zla ba nyar thug gi bar du zas dkar gsum bza' bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-19: tshes bco lnga'i nyin mtshan thog thag tu don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po dpag tu med par bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12a-20: mtshan thog thag bzlas brjod byas kyang ngal ba med pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-0: lus snyoms @12b pa dang bral bas bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-2: snying rje'i lhag pa'i bsam pa'i sems su bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-3: bzlas brjod kyi cho ga zin nas dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba mtshams bcad pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-7: dkyil 'khor bsdam pa byas nas de nas 'khor rnams dkyil 'khor du dam tshig la gzhug par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-9: dkyil 'khor gyi las zin nas mchod pa brtsam mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-10: mchod pa'i cho ga zin pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-11: de nas bzlas brjod brtsam par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-12: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi spyan sngar 'dug nas don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po bzlas brjod byas la khro bo'i rgyal po brgya rtsa brgyad kyis dbang bskur ro; ;bzlas brjod lan nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-13: dbang bskur ma thag tu ras kyi sku gzugs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-14: dkyil 'khor thams cad kun tu 'bar zhing 'od zer sna tshogs 'byin cing legs so zhes bya ba'i sgra 'byin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:12b-15: rig sngags 'chang ba'i snying dga' zhing lus 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-0: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug shin tu 'bar zhing 'od 'phro ba nyi ma stong bas lhag pa'i 'od zer can don yod pa'i zhags pa tshangs pa'i cha byad 'chang ba dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi nang nas mngon du gshegs te @13a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-1: phyogs bcu'i dkyil 'khor kun la rnam par gzigs shing rig sngags 'chang ba legs so zhes bya ba'i sgra phyung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-2: phyag g-yas pa brkyang ste rig sngags 'chang ba'i spyi bo la bzhag ste dkyil 'khor gyi mchog shin tu brgyan cing spras pa 'di ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-3: shin tu bzang ba yin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-5: 'di rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor don yod pa'i zhags pa rnams par 'phrul pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-6: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-7: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis phyag byas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-9: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi gsang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-18: srin po rnams kyi dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-19: bdud thams cad pham par byed pa'i dkyil 'khor; bgegs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-20: rnam par log 'dren thams cad 'joms pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13a-29: tha na byol song gi skye gnas su gtogs pa'i bya yang rung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-0: sems can thams cad 'khor ba'i gcong rong las sgrol ba @13b yin no; ;'di ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-8: 'chi ba las yongs su thar par byed cing 'jigs pa med pa'i khyim du 'jug par byed pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-10: rnam par thar par byed pa dkyil 'khor chen po snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-11: gsang sngags su bcas pa rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis phyag byas pa 'di rig sngags 'chang ba de dang des ming brjod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-12: gang dran pa tsam la sogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-15: ming 'dzin pa yang 'khor ba'i pha rol tu brgal bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-16: phyir mi ldog pa nyid du sa bcu bgrod nas bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir mi ldog pa 'thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-18: gang zhig dkyil 'khor chen po 'di 'dra ba mngon du mthong ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-19: rnam par grol ba'i gzungs 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gsang sngags kyi tshig bzlas brjod byed pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-23: lan 'ga' smyur bas mthong ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:13b-26: yud tsam gyis mthong ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-0: sems can de la de bzhin gshegs pa yin par yang 'dzin @14a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-2: 'jig rten las 'das pa yin pas spyi bos dbang bskur bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-3: rig sngags 'chang bas zungs shig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-5: ji ltar yid la re ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-6: bsam pa de thams cad rjes su gzung zhing sbyin par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-7: de'i tshe rig sngags 'chang bas yid la ji ltar bsam pa'i mchog smras na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-8: de thams cad sbyin par mdzad cing don yod pa'i ye shes bkod pa rnam par grol ba dri ma med pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-9: gzhan yang gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma dang mnyam pa khrag khrig stong phrag bcu'i ting nge 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-10: rdzu 'phrul gyis nam mkha' la 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-11: dkyil 'khor de'i dam tshig tu zhugs pa ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-12: dam tshig shes pa'i rjes su zhugs pa yin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-13: de dag thams cad sa bcu la rab tu gnas pa yin /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-15: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ba'i phyir mi ldog pa thob par 'gyur ba yin /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-16: lung bstan pa dang byin gyis brlabs par 'gyur ba yin; de ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-17: mngal na gnas par skye ba'i tha ma ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14a-18: phyis mngal na gnas pa'i dri mas gos par mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-0: shi nas bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su skye bar @14b 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-1: de padmo'i nang nas rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan par brdzus te skyes par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-2: tshe rabs kun tu tshe rabs dran par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-3: don yod pa'i rgyal po'i phun sum tshogs pa cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis byang chub kyi snying po chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dam tshig chen po 'di kha ton byed na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-4: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing na byang chub kyi snying po la bzhugs pa mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-5: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyan sngar legs so zhes bya ba thob par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-7: skye ba blangs pa legs par skye ba yin pas legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-8: phyir mi ldog par bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la rab tu gnas pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-9: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-10: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams 'od zer 'bum phrag bye bas mdzes par gyur cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-11: bsod nams kyis brgyan pa'i phyag gser gyi mdog can brkyangs nas spyi ngor phyag 'jog cing dbugs 'byin par yang mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:14b-12: byang chub kyi snying po la thug gi bar du chos 'brel ba'i gtam mngon sum du sgrog par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-0: tha na dkyil 'khor chen po rol mo'i @15a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-5: rol mo'i sgra gang dag grag pa la sems can gang dag gis sgra de thos nas sna ba'i bu ga tsam du song ba de thams cad phyir mi ldog par 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-6: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la rab tu gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-7: tha na byol song gi skye gnas su gtogs pa bya'i rna bar sgra thos pa de dag thams cad kyang phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-9: rnam par 'phrul pa'i cho 'phrul chen po dang ldan pa rnam par thar pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga mthu chen po rnam par 'phrul pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-16: sems can gzhan gang yang rung ba dge sbyong ngam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-21: 'ga' zhig gi rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga 'di 'khor mang po'i nang du klog pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-22: sems can gang gis sgra de thos nas sgra dbyangs de dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-23: ming thos pa rna ba'i bu gar song bar gyur pa de dag thams cad sgrib pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-24: sdig pa mi bzad pa las bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15a-26: sdig pa las rnam par grol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sras su rig par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-2: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi sras kyi thu bo yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-3: rtag par 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang phyug grogs mdzad cing rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-4: rtag tu dbugs 'byin par mdzad par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-5: mthar byang chub kyi snying po la gnas kyi bar du rtag tu rjes su srung bar mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-6: sems can gang zhig dkyil 'khor de'i sa phyogs su song ste sa gzhi snang ba tsam mthong ba de dag thams cad kyang phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-7: nyon mongs pa thams cad bsregs shing sgrib pa thams cad las yongs su grol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-8: de'i sa rdul rlung gis bdas te lus la phog pa gang yin ba de dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-9: tha na sems can ngan pa yang rung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-10: de dag thams cad phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ba'i gnas la rab tu gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-11: sdig pa thams cad las yongs su grol ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-12: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug rtag tu mthong ba dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-13: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgongs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-14: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis dbugs phyung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:15b-15: lha thams cad kyis srung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-0: bsod nams kyi phung po chen po yongs su bzung @16a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-2: dge ba'i rtsa ba chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-5: ming 'dzin pa tsam gyis 'bras bu chen po thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-6: de nas rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sbyin sreg gi cho ga bshad par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-8: sgrib pa thams cad sreg cing sdug bsngal drag po las rnam par grol bar 'gyur ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-9: nyon mongs pa drag po'i rgya mtsho dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-11: phyir mi ldog pa'i gnas bla na med par dbugs 'byin par mdzad pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-12: sangs rgyas thams cad dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i lam ston pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-13: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' ston pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-14: lha'i stegs sbyin sreg byas pa tsam gyi mod la the tshom med par me lha dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-18: dbang phyug dang gshin rje dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-21: gzhon nu rnams sbyin sreg byas pa 'di tsam gyi mod la thams cad 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16a-22: the tshom med par lha dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-0: grul bum thams cad @16b 'ong bar 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-1: de'i mod la rig sngags 'chang ba'i rkang pa gnyis la rtag tu 'dud par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-2: de bzhin du nyin mtshan du kun tu srung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-3: rgyal po chen po bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-4: phyag na rdo rje bdag nyid chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-5: gnod sbyin gyi dbang po chen po bcu yang phyogs bcur srung bar byed de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-6: mi srun pa ma rungs pa sel cing dmyal ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-9: sems can ma rungs pa rnams sel bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-10: de ma thag tu bsod nams chen po'i lhun po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-11: bsod nams chen po'i phung po bla na med pa skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-13: aa ga ru srang lnga dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-14: du ru ska srang bdun dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-16: gla rtsi srang gcig gi bzhi cha re re dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-18: lce pog kun tu ra srang lnga dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-20: 'di rnams gcig tu bsres te phye mar byas la kha ra dkar po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-21: sbrang rtsis ril bu zho re'i tshad tsam du byas pa stong rtsa brgyad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-23: 'bras yos bsres te ril bu dang bsres nas mar gyi nang du smyugs te sbyin sreg bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-26: shing sha mya'i yam shing gi me sbar te sbyin sreg gi cho ga bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-27: gang dang gang gi tshe stong rtsa brgyad sbyin sreg byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:16b-28: de dang de'i tshe sdig pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-2: de dang de'i tshe de nad thams cad las yongs su grol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-3: de dang de'i tshe gcong thams cad las yongs su grol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-4: de dang de'i tshe 'dzam bu'i gling gi sems can bud med dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-12: dmangs rigs la sogs pa thams cad kyi sdig pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-13: sgrib pa thams cad byang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-23: gzhan gyi 'khor gyi 'jigs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-24: phyir rgol ba'i dgras 'jigs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-25: sems can ma rungs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-29: gcan gzan gtum po'i 'jigs pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17a-30: sems can de dag thams cad 'jigs pa med par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-0: dmangs rigs gang dag gis de'i dri tshor ba de dag thams @17b cad kyang phyir mi ldog par 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-1: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la rab tu gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-2: tshe brjes nas thams cad bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su 'gro bar 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-3: padmo'i nang nas brdzus te skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-4: byol song gi skye gnas su gtogs pa rkang gnyis dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-5: rkang bzhi pa rnams kyis de'i dri tshor ba tsam gyis thams cad nges par phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-6: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyid las phyir mi ldog par 'gyur zhing mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-7: rig sngags 'chang ba de ji lta ji ltar sbyin sreg byed pa de lta de ltar de'i lus dri ma med cing yongs su dag par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-9: rig sngags 'chang ba'i lus 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-10: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas mang po'i sku mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-11: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku de dag gis rig sngags 'chang ba la legs so zhes bya ba'i sgra 'byin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-15: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i mchog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-17: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:17b-19: bdud thams cad rab tu 'joms pa'i sbyin sreg chen po'i cho ga yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-5: log 'dren tshar gcod ba'i sbyin sreg chen po'i cho ga yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-7: byang chub kyi snying por song ste chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i sbyin sreg chen po'i cho ga yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-9: byang chub kyi lam bla na med pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-10: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku de dag thams cad kyis phyag g-yas pa gser gyi kha dog lta bu brkyang ste rig sngags 'chang ba'i mgo'i spyi bo la phyag 'jog par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-11: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi rang gi ngo bo nyid kyi rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-12: don yod pa'i zhags pa dang tshangs pa'i cha byad 'chang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-13: dbu lcang lo cod pan gyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-17: rig sngags 'chang ba'i mdun na bzhugs te bka' stsol pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-19: khyod kyis don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-20: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga chen po grub pa legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-22: mchog ji lta ba dang ji ltar 'dod pa de thams cad sbyin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-23: de nas rig sngags 'chang bas ji ltar 'dod pa'i mchog smras na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18a-24: de thams cad thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-0: 'phags pa spyan ras @18b gzigs kyi dbang phyug gis phyag brkyang ste rig sngags 'chang ba'i mgo'i spyi bo la phyag bzhag pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-1: phyag bzhag ma thag tu rig sngags 'chang ba nam mkha' la 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-2: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad du 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-3: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mngon sum du mthong ba thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-5: phyir mi ldog pa'i gnas thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-6: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi zhing du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis dbang bskur ba thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-7: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi zhing la bsnyen bkur byas nas bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-8: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od dpag med byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor dang bcas pa chos 'chad pa byang chub kyi snying po la thug gi bar du mngon sum du thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-9: de nas hom khung bshad par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-10: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sbyin sreg gi gnas bla na med pa ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-11: padma kha bye ba 'dra bar byas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-12: zlum po khru gsum pas dang ba'i lci ba bsres pa dang ldan par byas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-13: padma'i snying po la hom khung zabs su brko ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-14: thad ka kun du khru gang pa brko bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:18b-15: nang du padma bcu drug pa 'bur du byas pa bzhag la tshon sna tshogs kyis padma de brgyan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-1: phyi 'khor du dkyil 'khor gru bzhir byas la dri sna tshogs kyis gtor ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-3: dkyil 'khor kun tu bum pa gang ba bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-4: dngul gyi snod gang ba bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-5: mchod yon gyi chus bkang ba gser gyi snod bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-6: ro sna tshogs kyi gtor ma bzhag pa ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-7: gtor ma dkar gsum rnam pa sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-8: 'bras bu rnam pa sna tshogs bzhag pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-9: dri dang me tog sna tshogs kyis gtor te phreng ba rnam pa sna tshogs dpyangs la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-10: dkyil 'khor kun tu tshon sna lnga'i ba dan gyis mda' la brgyan te gzugs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-11: sgo bzhi cha dbye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-13: legs par brgyan cing dri chus yongs su bkang ba bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-14: sgo bzhir chos smra ba shin tu brgyan pa'i stan la 'dug ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-15: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bklag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-16: grva bzhir chos smra ba chos kyi stan legs par brgyan pa la 'dug nas don yod pa'i zhags pa'i mdo sde bklag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19a-20: rin po che sna bdun gyis mchod par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-0: de nas rig sngags 'chang bas khrus byas gos gtsang ma bgos dri zhim bos bsgos te gtsang mar byas la ril bu la don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po brgya rtsa brgyad @19b bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-1: khro bo'i rgyal po brgya rtsa brgyad kyis dbang bskur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-2: don yod pa rnam par lta ba'i snying po brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-3: de nas don yod pa rnam par lta ba'i 'bar ba rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi zhags pa'i snying pos stong rtsa brgyad sbyin sreg bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-4: mi smra bar byas pa'i sems dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-5: snying thag pa nas brtse ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-6: snying rje bar bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-7: las bla na med pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-8: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-9: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug thugs rje chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-12: tsa ra tsa ra padma bhu dze /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-13: dzva la dzva la h'u ta sha ne /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-17: sarbba ma la na; aa mo gha pa ni ba ra de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-18: h'um h'um ni ra da ha /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-22: sa manta rashmi ba ra de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-28: de ni; rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor 'bar ba zhags pa chen po'i snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-29: gzungs kyi sbyin sreg gi cho ga 'jig rten las 'das ba bla na med pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-30: de nas rig sngags 'chang bas thal ba des rmad du byung ba chen po'i bya ba thams cad bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:19b-31: thal ba des gang lus la byugs pa de ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-0: sgrib pa dang sdig pa thams cad las grol @20a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-2: dpral bar thig le byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-3: de ma thag tu zhag bzhi pa'i rims las thar par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-14: lan 'ga' yang gnas shing phyir 'ong bar mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-15: dpag tshad brgya 'das te 'bros par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-16: mtshogs mar thig le byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-17: gdon stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi las thar par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-18: thams cad kyang phyogs bcur dpag tshad stong du 'bros par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-19: thal ba'i rdul bya rog gi mchu la gos pa phyogs kyi gnas gang du lhung ba der gnod sbyin dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-27: log 'dren phyir gnas par mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-29: phyogs kyi gnas der lhung na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-31: snying gar thig le byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-32: nad thams cad las thar par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-33: lte ba'i gnas su thig le byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-34: lto ba'i nang gi nad thams cad mod la sos par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20a-35: gdug pas zin pa la bskus na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-0: dug gis @20b myos pa la byin na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-6: dug thams cad rnam par zhig par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-15: chu dron po dang sbyar te bskus la mar la lan bdun bzlas brjod byas pas bskus na mod la nad thams cad las yongs su thar bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-19: ser ba thams cad mi 'bab bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-20: rlung ldang ba'i logs su gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-23: mtshams chen po bcad par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-24: yul 'khor kun tu gtor na; me tog dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-27: me tog gi ljon shing dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-34: nags tshal thams cad legs par srung par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-35: yul 'khor la dpag tshad brgya tshun chad kun tu mtshams chen po bcad pa byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-36: grong khyer gyi sgo bzhir gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:20b-38: phyir 'byung ba'i sems can bud med dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-3: byol song gi skye gnas su gtogs pa rkang gnyis pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-6: bya de dag thams cad sgrib pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-7: sdig pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-8: dgongs pa tsam gyis nad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-9: sdug bsngal thams cad las grol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-10: nad thams cad dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-11: tshe yongs su brjes nas bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su 'gro zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-12: sangs rgyas nyid du gnas kyi bar du phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ba'i gnas thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-14: ro bsregs pa'i steng du thal bas gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-15: dmyal bar skyes pa'i sems can de dag thams cad mdo la dmyal ba nas thar te mngon par dga' ba'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-16: bde ba can du skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-24: mtshams chen po bcad cing zhi ba chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-25: rgyal po'i pho brang gi sgor gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-26: rgyal po dang btsun mo'i 'khor dgra thams cad las legs par srung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-27: skye bo mang po'i nang du gtor ba tsam gyi mdo la skye bo mang po de dag thams cad sgrib pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21a-28: sdig pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-0: @21b nad thams cad dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-1: gzhan yang bye ba stong phrag brgya byed pas rang 'dod pa la rang gis blos thams cad du sbyar bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-2: de nas rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sku gzugs ras la bris pa bshad par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-3: dar ram ras gtsang ma legs par btags pa tshad khru do'am; khru gsum mam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-4: khru bzhi pa de'i dbus su don yod pa'i zhags pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-5: 'jig rten dbang phyug tshangs pa'i cha byad 'chang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-6: dbu lcang lo cod pan gyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-7: cod pan rgyal ba 'od dpag med dang g-yas su zla ba tshes pa can gyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-8: phyag bzhi ba rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-9: skyil mo krung bcas te bzhugs pa bri ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-10: ri bo po ta la lcug ma me tog can sna tshogs kyis gang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-11: rin po che sna tshogs kyi lcug mas gang ba bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-12: de'i steng du rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-14: seng+ge'i khri'i steng du padma'i gdan bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-15: de'i steng du 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug bzhugs par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-18: zhags pa thogs shing gzugs de phyag dbugs 'byin pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-19: dbu'i gong man chad gzhal med khang chen po lha rdzas rin po che sna tshogs kyis spras pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:21b-20: dbus su mtho ba dang bcas pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-0: @22a *// dbus mtho ba'i steng du de bzhin gshegs pa bdun tshad dang mthun par padma'i gdan la bzhugs shing rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-1: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i gong gi dbus su de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-3: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug 'od dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-4: de bzhin gshegs pa gsum rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa skyil mo krung bcas te gzhal med khang gi nang na bzhugs par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-5: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi 'od 'dom gang pa la 'khor bar de bzhin gshegs pa sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis brgyan par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-6: de bzhin gshegs pa'i nye 'khor kun tu 'od zer 'bar ba sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-7: mdung rtse gsum pa'i phreng ba bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-8: de nyid kyi nye 'khor du lha sum cu rtsa gnyis bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-9: gong gi dbus su rdo rje 'chang ba khro gnyer can rdo rje gsor bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-14: lha'i dbang phyug chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-15: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi snying po'i dbang po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-16: 'og min gnas kyi lha'i bu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-17: dga' ldan gyi lha'i bu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22a-21: rgyal po chen po bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-9: gnas gtsang ma'i rigs kyi lha dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-10: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-11: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha rnams me tog sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-12: nor bu rin po che sna tshogs lag pa nas 'phrul pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-13: mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-14: 'phags pa don yod pa'i zhags pa'i cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-16: lha rnams kyi phyi rol thog thag tu padma'i phreng ba rdo rje dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-17: mdung rtse gsum pas spras pa'i padma'i phreng bas kun tu 'khor bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-18: g-yas phyogs su 'phags ma sgrol ma skyil mo krung phyed du bcas te bzhugs pa autpa la dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-19: nor bu rin po che phyag na thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:22b-20: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56a-5: don yod zhags pa'i snying po de kho na nyid gces pa rmad du byung ba de kho na nyid kyi snying po'i sgrub pa bla na med pa bklags pas grub pa 'di rjes su zungs shig /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56a-9: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po dam par gyur pa gsang ba padma gtsug tor gyi dkyil 'khor de rnams du zhig lags pa de dag bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs shig /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-7: nor bu'i byug pa 'chang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-9: skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa; 'od zer 'bar bas yang dag par brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-10: gos rnam par bkra ba sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-12: zla bas lhag par 'bar bas rnam par mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-13: padma rnams kyi steng na mdzes bzhin pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-14: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad thugs mnyes par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-15: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi phyag bya bar 'os pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-16: lha thams cad kyis mchod par 'os pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-17: klu thams cad kyis rjes su gzung bar 'os pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-18: drang srong thams cad kyis dga' bar 'os pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-22: lto 'phye chen po thams cad kyis rjes su 'gro bar 'os pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-23: sems can thams cad kyi bla mar 'os pa mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:56b-24: de lta bu'i snang ba rgya chen po byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis de kho na nyid gces pa'i snying por gyur pa'i snying po nye bar bstan no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-0: de nas gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen @57a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-1: po lag na rdo rjes 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor chen po de mthong ba tsam gyi mong la snying po gsang ba don yod pa'i padma dri ma med pa'i gtsug tor 'od zer 'bar ba'i ting nge 'dzin so sor thob par gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-2: ting nge 'dzin so sor thob pa gang gis sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi nang du chud par gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-3: de rnams thams cad rab tu ma gu ba'i yid kyis zhabs dag gi rjes la phyag 'tshal bar gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-4: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis don yod zhags pa'i snying po'i gsang sngags 'di smras so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-5: aom aa mo gha p'a sha hri da ya padmo shni sha ku m'a ra pe sha dha ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-8: sarba aa mo gha ku la sa ma ya hri da ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-9: sarba siddhi aa mo gha pra yatstsha padma padma h'um h'um na mo stu te sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-11: don yod zhags pa'i snying po bklags pas grub pa'i sgrub thabs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-12: aom aa mo gha padmo shn'i sha shva ra; padme shva ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-13: sa manta ya sarba ta th'a ga ta n'am/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-14: aa mo gha padmo shn'i sha sa ma yam a'a karsha ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-16: sarba karma siddhim pra yatstsha me aa ba lo ki te shva ra h'um h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-17: ma h'a padmo shn'i sha bhu dze sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-18: rigs kyi rgyal po'i gsang sngags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-19: aom ma h'a tsanda padme shva ra bi bi dha r'u pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57a-21: padma dam sht'a ka ra la bh'i sha na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-0: bktra sarba dushta hri da yam kh'a da @57b ya; bighnam/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-4: khro bo'i rgyal po'i rigs kyi snying po'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-5: nang gi dkyil 'khor gyi gsang ba'i las rnams so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-6: aom aa mo gha padmo shn'i sha padma p'a sha kro dha ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-7: m'a yi karma pra be sha ya ma h'a p'a shu pa ti /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-12: ma h'a tsanda be ga aa mo gha ku la sa ma ya padma h'um h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-13: khro bo'i rgyal po don yod zhags pa'i padma gtsug tor gyi snying po'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-14: de nas don yod pa'i snying po'i las rnams su 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-15: dran pa tsam gyi mod la dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang mnyam pas gcig tu mtshungs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-16: tshe dpag med dang mnyam pa'i lus su 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-17: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnams thams cad dang mnyam pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang mtshungs shing mnyam pa nyid du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-18: mtshungs shing mnyam pa nyid kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyam pa nyid du mthong ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-19: padma'i phyag gi ting nge 'dzin rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-20: padma'i gtsug tor gyi phyag gis 'jig rten dbang phyug dang mnyam pa nyid du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-21: padma'i gtsug tor bcings pa nyid kyis sbyin pa'i gtsug tu mngon par dbang bskur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:57b-22: dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis mngon par dbang bskur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-0: padma'i gtsug tor gyis don yod par dbang bskur ba @58a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-2: padma'i gtsug tor gyi snying po rgyas par gyur pa thob ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-3: ting nge 'dzin brgya stong phrag dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-4: bla na med pa'i dpal 'thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-5: rigs kyi rgyal po'i gsang sngags rgyas par gyur pa padma'i gtsug tor gyi dkyil 'khor du rigs kyi rgyal po legs par grub par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-6: thams cad du rigs kyi rgyal po'i dngos grub bzang po rnams 'ong par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-7: rigs kyi rgyal po'i gsang sngags kyi rgyal po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-8: rig sngags kyi rgyal po mchog gi dngos grub thams cad rab tu sbyin par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-9: padmo'i phyag gis rjes su 'jug cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-10: don yod pa'i rigs kyi dngos grub ji lta ba bzhin du 'grub ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-11: bklags pas grub pa 'di la the tshom med do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-12: padma gtsug tor gyi rigs kyi dngos grub dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-14: don yod zhags pa'i dkyil 'khor du bklags nas bzlas ba tsam gyis 'grub ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-16: rig sngags kyi rgyal po gang yin pa de thams cad du dbang phyug tu 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-17: dkyil 'khor rnams kyi cho ga zhib mo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-18: phyag rgyas byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi rigs thun mong pa thams cad du rgyal po'i bya ba byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-19: sangs rgyas kyi zhing stong phrag rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58a-20: sangs rgyas kyi zhing brgya phrag rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-0: @58b gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma dang mnyam pa'i zhing du rgyal por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-1: rigs kyi rig pas lha'i dbang phyug dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-2: lha'i tshogs rnams kyi dbang phyug tu 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-3: rtag tu yang gnod sbyin rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-4: srin po rnams su gyur pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-7: srin po rnams kyi de bzhin nyid du thams cad du rgyal po dang dbang phyug tu rtag tu 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-12: thams cad du ji srid byang chub la yang dag par gnas kyi bar du rigs kyi rgyal por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-13: de nas khro bo'i rgyal po dran pa tsam dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-14: drag po de yid la sems pa tsam gyi mod la 'phral du ri rab ltung bar byed cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-15: khor yug gi ri rnam par 'thor bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-16: rgya mtsho chen po kun nas dkrug cing rgya mtsho chen po nye bar skye bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-17: kun tu gsal bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-18: klu'i gnas thams cad du klu'i gnas 'bar bar yang byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-19: bgegs dang log par 'dren pa thams cad kyi skad cig tsam gyis steng du bdug par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:58b-25: mi bzad pa de rnams thams cad khro bo'i rgyal po dran pa tsam gyis 'jigs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-0: khro bo'i rgyal po'i gsang ba pa thams cad kyi rigs @59a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-1: kyi dam tshig la gnas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-2: dkyil 'khor du phyag rgya gnas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-3: gsang sngags kyi lha gzhan gang yin pa rnams kyis khro bo'i rgyal po dran pa tsam gyis de rnams thams cad rig sngags 'chang la skyabs su 'gro bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-4: de rnams thams cad rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur zhing gnas par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-5: 'ga' zhig gang du 'gro ba'am 'dug pa de la dbang po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-11: chu lha dang klu'i rgyal po rgya mtsho dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-16: de bzhin du rgyal po chen po bzhi dus rtag tu rig sngags 'chang gi rjes su 'brang bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-19: de bzhin du drag po'i las rnams thams cad kyang h'um yig tsam gyis de la dngos grub mthong ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-22: sems can ma rungs pa shin tu mi bzad pa rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-23: pha rol gyi dmag tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-25: rnam par 'gras pa'i skye bo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-26: sdig pa de rnams thams cad h'um yig gis mchog tu gzir ba tsam gyis thal bar 'jigs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59a-28: ngan sems pa'i sems can dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-0: byas pa @59b mi gzo ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-1: byas pa la 'khon pa thams cad drag po'i h'um yig bzlas pa tsam gyis skad cig la sreg ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-2: dper na mes phye ma leb bzhin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-3: las gzhan stong phrag rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-4: las brgya stong phrag nyid bzlas pa tsam gyis 'grub ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-5: dran pa tsam gyi mdo la las thams cad 'grub bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-6: de nas don yod pa padma'i gtsug tor dran pa tsam gyis bya ba thams cad ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-8: ji ltar gang cung zad yid la byed pas las byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-10: gnas rnams pa gzhan thams cad du ji ltar yid la byed pa'i bya ba thams cad du byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-12: 'phags pa don yod pa'i zhags pa'i cho ga bzhi ba mo'i rgyal po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-14: de nas gsang sngags la 'jug pa rnams kyi dgongs pa thams cad so sor 'grub par 'gyur ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-15: aom zhes bya ba don yod pa'i zhags pa padma gtsug tor gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad du gsang sngags yi ge gcig pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-16: 'jig rten mgon po'i spyan sngar 'bum dran par byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-17: sa dang po la gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-18: sngon gyi sdig pa bsags pa sems can dmyal ba mi bzad pa gang ci yang rung ba de dag thams cad ji ltar rlung gis phyag dar gtor ba bzhin 'jig par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:59b-19: dngos grub thams cad thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-2: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-3: gang dkyil 'khor gyi lha gzhan dag kyang dgyes par 'gyur la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-4: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug rtag tu mchog sbyin pa mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-5: gsang sngags aom zhes bya ba dran nas tshe 'phos pa ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-6: 'jig rten gyi khams bde ba can du 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-7: gsang sngags kyi yi ge gcig pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-9: yi ge gnyis pa 'bum bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-10: sa gnyis pa thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-11: de bzhin gshegs pa snang ba mtha' yas kyi spyan sngar 'dug par 'gyur zhing mchog thams cad rjes su sbyin par mdzad /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-12: sdig pa thams cad kyang rnam par dag par mdzad /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-13: sngon gyi nad kyang sos par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-14: nor gyi dbang phyug nor bu bzang po'i bu dbang du 'gyur zhing nye bar gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-15: mi gang gis kyang phyir zhing bar chad byed nus par mi 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-16: tshe 'phos nas ri gru 'dzin du skye bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-17: don yod pa'i zhigs pa'i dngos rgub kyang thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-19: gsang sngags kyi yi ge gsum pa 'bum bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-20: sa gsum pa la yang dag par 'jug par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60a-21: padma yangs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi phags rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-0: gsang sngags gang @60b yin pa thams cad la zhugs par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-1: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gzhon nu'i cha byad can mdun na bzhugs par 'gyur zhing 'dod pa thams cad kyi mchog rjes su sbyin par mdzad /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-2: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i padma gtsug tor dkyil 'khor gyi ston par mdzad /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-3: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams ston par mdzad /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-4: thams cad du dngos grub rjes su sbyin par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-6: gsang sngags yi ge bzhi pa 'bum bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-8: 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa mi 'khrugs pa'i sku mdog gser gyi kha dog can mdun na bzhugs shing dpung pa brkyang nas phyag spyi bor 'jog par mdzad la rig sngags 'chang ba legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-9: zhes bya ba rjes su sbyin par mdzad de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-11: tshur shog khyod kyi sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad yongs su dag ste rang gi ngo bo thams cad shin tu dri ma med par yongs su dag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-12: mi'i 'jig rten 'di nas tshe 'phos nas nga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du 'ong zhing tshe rabs dran par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-13: phyir zhing nam yang mngal na gnas pas gos par mi 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-14: 'jig rten ba dgos pa thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:60b-16: gsangs sangs yi ge lnga pa 'bum bzlas brjod /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-0: @61a *// byas na; sa lnga pa la gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-1: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas padma'i bla ma rab tu ston pa mdzad /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-2: sgrib pa thams cad yongs su zad par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-3: rig sngags 'chang la legs so zhes bya ba'i sgra 'byin par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-6: khyod la bsod nams kyi phung po chen po skyes te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-8: khyod dge ba'i rtsa ba chen po bskyed pas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-10: khyod tshe brjes na de bzhin gshegs pa bye ba khrag khrig dgu bcu rtsa gnyis kyi drung du dge ba'i rtsa ba mtshungs bar bskyed par 'gyur zhing nga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du skye bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-11: khyod kyis don yod pa'i zhags pa padma gtsug tor gyi snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-13: phyag rgya chen po rim par phye ba grub cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-15: khyod sgrib pa dang sdig pa thams cad spangs kyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-16: bya ba thams cad gyis shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-17: yid la bya ba'i sgrub pa thams cad ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin de dag thams cad shin tu 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-18: aom padma aa ba lo ki te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-19: gzungs sngags yi ge drug pa 'bum bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61a-20: sa drug pa thob ste 'jug par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61b-0: de bzhin gshegs pa @61b thams cad snang ba mdzad par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61b-1: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi rdul phra mo snyed kyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams gzigs shing mngon sum du ston pa mdzad /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61b-3: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas padma gzigs pa'i rgyal mtshan rig sngags 'chang de la yang dag par dbugs 'byin par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:61b-5: nga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du byang chub snying po'i mthar thug gi bar du tshur shog /
