K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:159b-19: bgegs thams cad la 'bab pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:159b-26: klu sdang ba thams cad la bab na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-0: ji srid du zlog pa ma byas @160a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-2: chu dang yungs kar gyis bzlog pa byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-4: mdung rtse gsum pa bskyod bar 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-5: dkyil 'khor byas la thod pa gzhag par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-6: me tog dgram pa yang bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-7: gu gul gyi bdug pas kyang bdugs la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-8: mdung rtse gsum pa la til mar gyi rgyal pos bsku /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-9: phye mas gdab cing thig le bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-10: rtse'i rgyun gsum la padma chen po'i phye mas gtor nas thod pa'i steng du gzhag par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-11: yungs kar gyis gtor zhing h'um zhes se gol byas [?] na mdung rtse gsum pa 'bar bar byed /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-17: ji srid du zlog pa ma byas pa de srid du 'phar bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-18: chu dang yungs kar gyis bzlog pa byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-20: dung la til mar gyis byugs la phye mas gtor la thig le bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-21: yungs kar gyis kyang phyi nang gtor la bus na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-22: ji srid du sgra thos pa de srid kyi skyes pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-25: bu mo thams cad bro rdung bar byed /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160a-28: phyogs bcur rab tu rgyug par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-1: go cha thams cad btang nas bro rdung bar byed /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-3: phyogs bcur rgyug par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-4: gal te dung lan bdun bus na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-6: pha rol gyi dmag tshogs des nyon mongs pa skyed par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-7: ji srid du zlog pa ma byas pa de srid mchod zhing phyogs bcur rgyug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-8: sbos chus bzlog cing khrus byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-9: phyir bde bar gnas par 'gyur la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-11: dpal gyi mchog sbyin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-12: de nas sgyu ma de kho na nyid sgrub pa'i gsang sngags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-13: rnam par 'phrul pa'i dngos grub kyi dkyil 'khor bshad par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-14: sgyu 'phrul gyi dra ba rnam par 'phrul ba'i dkyil 'khor gang du dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs shing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-15: kun nas rgyan par yungs kar dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-16: til mar gyi rgyal po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-17: phye mar bsres pas byugs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-18: thig les kyang dbang bskur cing padma chen po'i phye mas byugs la lag pa padma'i phyag rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-19: h'um zhes bya ba'i sgra brjod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-21: yungs kar gyis gtor ba'i mod la gtor ma'i snod dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:160b-24: bum pa bkang pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-0: dkyil 'khor gyi steng nas nam mkha' la sor bzhi tsam gyis sgrags te 'dug la ji srid du dkyil 'khor gyi las su bya ba @161a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-1: thams cad rdzogs rdzogs kyi bar du nam mkha' la 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-2: rig sngags 'chang ba sa'i steng gi sor bzhi tsam gyi tshad kyi steng gi nam mkha' la 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-3: las su bya ba thams cad zin nas dkyil 'khor gyi yo byad dri chab kyi cho gas dbang bskur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-7: bum bu thams cad rang nyid 'phar bar byed la slar yang rang gi gnas su 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-8: go cha de lta bu ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-9: dkyil 'khor thams cad la bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-10: thams cad du yon tan ston par snang la; byas pa tsam gyis las thams cad sgrub par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-13: de'i phyir padma'i dngos grub bshad par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-16: zangs las shin tu legs shing mdzes pa snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-17: ze ba dang bcas shing sdong bu tshad dang ldan par byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-18: 'dab ma phyed kha phye ba 'khor bar 'dab ma drug cu rtsa bzhi yod pa khru gang tsam gyi tshad sdong bu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-20: ze ba'i tshad sor bzhi tsam du byas pa la til mar gyi rgyal pos bsku /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161a-24: thig ler byas pa dang bcas pas kun legs par bskus la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-0: padma'i sdong bu'i bar du nor bu rin po che bzhag nas lan stong rtsa brgyad @161b bzlas brjod bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-1: khro bo'i rgyal bos lan bdun gyi bar du dbang bskur nas rig sngags 'chang gtsang ma legs par khrus byas la gos gtsang ma bgos pas til mar gyis bdag nyid la bsku bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-4: bdug pas bdag nyid kyis lus la bdug par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-5: lag pa g-yas pa la nor bu gdags /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-6: lag pa g-yon par padma bzung la bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'dug ste 'khor gyi nang du bcom ldan 'das la padma'i mchod pa 'bum bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-8: mchod pa'i cho ga byas nas chu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-9: yungs kar gyis btab na yang 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-10: padma sprul pa gang yin pa de dag thams cad chu'i nang du por na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-11: padma mgal me bskor ba ltar 'khor bar 'gyur la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-12: padma 'bum rnams char du 'bab par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-13: padma'i chu'i nang du gzhag par bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-20: mtsho'i nang gang rung ba'i gnas su bzhag na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-21: gnas de dang de thams cad du padma'i mtsho chen po 'byung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-22: ji srid du padma ma phyung ba de srid du dus rtag tu padma'i mtshor 'dug ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:161b-26: sos ka tsha ba'i dus su rtag tu padma'i mtshor 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-0: tshal gyi 'gram du zhugs nas yungs kar @162a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-1: la til mar gyis bskus pa phye ma dang sbyar nas me tog gang yang rung ba zhig lag gis bzung ste bskor la yungs kar gyis gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-2: tshal gyi mtha'i shing thams cad la me tog rgyas par snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-6: skye bo'i nang du me tog ji snyed pa lag gis bskor la yungs kar gyis gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-7: me tog mang po 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-8: chu dang yungs kar gyis thams cad du zlog par byed pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-9: 'bras bu ji snyed pa lag gis bzung nas yungs kar gyis gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-11: gos lag pas bzung nas yungs kar gyis gtor te bskor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-12: gos dang bla re sna tshogs ston par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-13: rgyan lag pas bzung nas yungs kar gyis gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-14: lha'i rgyan bzang po sna tshogs pa lag tu 'byung bar 'gyur zhing skye bo 'dus pa thams cad kyi rgyan du byed la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-15: thams cad la rgyan btags par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-18: yungs kar la til mar gyis bskus /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162a-22: snu hva'i 'o mas kyang bsgos la de dag gcig tu byas nas grib ma la bskam mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-0: de nas 'bras bu gcig @162b khar bcug la phyogs bzhir gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-1: kha nas me 'bar bar snang zhing lus las 'bar ba sna tshogs 'byung bar snang ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-2: ji srid du yungs kar kha na yod pa'i bar du lus las 'od zer 'bar ba kha dog rnam pa sna tshogs 'byung ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-3: til mar dang lhan cig btags pa'i snying por bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-4: kong bur til mar gyi rgyal pos bkang ste mar me 'bum ston par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-5: me thab khung bu'i nang du bcug na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-6: ji srid du ma phyung ba de srid du me 'bar bar ston te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-7: mar me'i sdong bu'i nang du bcug la ma phyung na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-9: mgal me 'bar ba'i nang du bcug na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-10: 'bar ba'i 'phreng ba 'bum snyed du snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-12: bum pa'i nang du gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-14: bum pa thams cad 'bar bar snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-16: mtshon cha thams cad la byugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-18: bdag nyid kyi lus la byugs la ril bu gtsang ma spyi bor bzhag na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-19: lus thams cad gcig tu 'bar bar snang ba nas lus ril bsregs pa ltar snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-20: 'o ma dang yungs kar gyis gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-22: lag pa dang rkang pa la bskus la ril bu gtsang ma 'bar ba lag pa g-yas pas bzung ba'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-23: rkang pa'i mthe bos bzung na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:162b-25: rkang pa gcig pu 'bar ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-5: rig byed bzhi'i nang thams cad du yan lag nyams par snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-6: dri chab dang yungs kar gyis gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-8: mtshan mo'i ril bu bsregs ba lam gyi bzhi mdor bzhag nas yungs kar gyis phyogs bzhir gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-9: mar me 'bum phrag bye ba snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-10: kun nas phyogs bzhir chu dang yungs kar gyis bzlog par bya ba yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-12: nang du gtor la shing gcig la ril bu gtsang ma bzhag na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-17: lo ma thams cad gcig tu 'bar bar snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-18: ri'i rtse mor mar me bus nas ri kun tu gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-19: ri kun nas gcig tu 'bar zhing mched par snang la sems can thams cad kun nas ngo mtshar du 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-23: pha rol gyi dmag tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-26: phas kyi dgra thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-27: sdang sems can nas ri dvags gtum po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163a-28: bya la sogs pa'i bar ri la gnas pa rnams de'i mtshan mo nyid phyogs bcu kun tu bros shing ha ha zhes bya ba'i sgra 'byin to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-0: spos chab kyis bzlog par @163b 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-1: gzugs brnyan gyi steng du gtor la gtsang ma'i ril bu 'bar bar bzhag na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-2: gzugs brnyan thams cad gcig tu 'bar bar 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-4: yungs kar gyis bzlog par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-5: mar me'i ril bu grong khyer gyi shar phyogs kyi sgor sbar ste gnas gtsang mar bzhag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-6: dkyil 'khor gcig byas nas gtor ma'i cho ga bum pa bkang ba bzhag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-7: grong khyer kun tu yungs kar gyis gtor zhing don yod pa'i rgyal po yang dran par byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-8: grong khyer kun nas mar me'i phreng ba 'bar ba gcig tu snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-9: grong khyer gyi sgo bzhir dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga byas la shar phyogs kyi sgo nas zhugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-10: gang grong khyer na gnas pa skyes pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-13: bu mo de dag thams cad dga' ba chen po rgya che bas tshim par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-14: grong khyer de na gang sdang ba'i sems can phyir rgol ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-19: glags tshol bar gyur pa gnod sbyin dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:163b-24: mi ma yin pa gang yang rung ba grong khyer de na gnas pa de dag lang long du gyur cing gdugs la ngu zhing ha ha zhes sgra 'byin cing grong khyer gyi sgor byung nas phyogs bcur rab tu 'bros so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-0: grong khyer de yang kun nas @164a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-1: gnod pa med cing 'khrug pa med par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-6: nad thams cad rab tu zhi bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-7: mtshan mo 'das nas spos chu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-8: yungs kar gyis grong khyer gyis sgor gtor zhing dbang bskur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-10: 'phags pa don yod pa'i zhags pa'i cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-13: mthing shun gyi phye ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-17: pha gu'i 'o ma dang gcig tu sbyar ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-18: nya'i mig mkhris pa dang bcas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-20: padma'i chu rnams kyang lhan cig tu phye mas zhib mor bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-21: phye ma snga ma legs par sbyar la chus ril bur byas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-22: phye mas gzhan yang bcang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-24: padma chen po'i phye ma bcang ba lhan cig tu bsres pa'i phye mas lus bskus la phyogs bzhir yungs kar gtor te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-25: ril bu khar bcug la h'um zhes bya ba bsdams te brjod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-27: de kho na bzhin du rna ba gnyis kyang lha rdzas kyi chu 'byung bar snang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164a-28: lus las spos kyi rigs yid du 'ong ba rab tu sim par byed pa 'byung ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-0: nad thams cad grub par snang @164b ste; rgyal ba'i phyag bzhin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-1: yungs kar gyi phye ma blangs te nam mkha' la gtor la ril bu lag pas bskor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-3: ril bu nam mkha' la 'phangs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-5: g-yul chen po 'gyed pa'i nang du phye ma de yungs kar dang bsres te nam mkha' la gtor la ril bu de yang khar bcug ste steng du bltas la h'um zhes bya ba'i sgras pos la gnam lcags chen po 'bab ste yid mi 'chad pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-7: chu'i nang du zhugs te phye ma de gtor la yungs kar dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-8: ril bu chu'i nang du gdab par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-9: phyogs bzhir yungs kar gtor te til mar gyis lus la bskus na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-10: klu chen po'i gzugs su snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-11: ril bu dang yungs kar me'i mdog lta bu chu dang bsres pa'i yungs kar nam mkha' la gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-12: 'brug sgra chen po 'byung zhing glog chen po gsal ba snang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-16: chu lung nas phyogs kun tu 'bab par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-21: ril ba la phye mas byugs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-22: de'i steng du yungs kar gyis gtor nas chus bkang ste khrus byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:164b-23: de chu 'bab par snang zhing de'i snod ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-1: mang po byed de mchog tu grub pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-2: de nas ri chen po'i 'bru mar gyi rgyal po byas te 'bru mar gzhan dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-3: de bzhin du til las byas 'bru mar gyi rgyal po de bzhin du sbyar ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-4: lag pa dang rkang pa bzhag la 'dir nyams drod kyang shes par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-5: bzhag pa thams cad nyams drod shes par bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-6: mar sar bzhin du 'jam par 'gyur zhing skad cig de nyid la mtho ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-7: dma' ba ji ltar yid la 'dod pa bzhin du ri yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-8: snying po thur ma 'dra ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-9: zlum po'am; yang na lcug ma lta bur byas pas ka ba yang 'dud pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-11: yang na mthon por 'gyur bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-12: yungs kar dang padma chen po'i phye ma lhan cig bsres pa 'bru mar gyi rgyal pos bsgos pa phyogs bzhir kun tu gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-13: ri thams cad mi snang zhing 'brog dgon pa snang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-14: yang ri bor snang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-16: mis bgrod par mi nus pa'i ri'i rtse mo na seng+ge dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-17: stag gi gang lcug ma dang tsher ma can gyi shing ljon pa sna tshogs kyis gang ba'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165a-19: khong stong du snang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-0: ci ste rig sngags 'chang 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi pho brang ri bo po ta la'i gzhal med khang @165b mthong bar 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-1: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis zhag bdun gyi ngar du nas kyi 'o thug gi zas zos te gtsang ma shin tu khrus byas pa gos gtsang ma bgos pas ri'i gseb tu zhugs la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-2: sa phyogs gtsang ma'i gnas der shing dri zhim po'i me sbar ba la yungs kar phye ma dang bsres pa 'bru mar gyi rgyal po dang sbyar la 'bras so ba dang bsres pa stong rtsa brgyad zhag bdun du dus gsum du sbyin sreg bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-3: lha bshos dang gtor ma dkar po 'bul lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-4: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis tshes brgyad la nyin zhag gcig smyung ba byas la shin tu khrus byas pa gtsang mas spos sna tshogs kyis lus bskus /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-5: gos bzang po gtsang ma bgos te 'bru mar gyi rgyal pos rang gi lus la bskus /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-8: thig le byas la nor bus mgo bcing zhing mgul ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-10: rked par yang bcings la yungs kar dang mtshal bsres pas re'i phyogs bzhir gtor bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-11: padma chen po'i phye ma de yang phyogs bzhir gtor /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-12: rang gi lag pa g-yon pas zhags pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-13: padma bzung zhing g-yas pas rnam par lta ba bsnang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-14: don yod pa chen pos dri ma med pa'i phyag rgya bzung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:165b-15: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i mdo lan gcig bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-0: ji ltar don yod pa'i zhags pa'i @166a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-1: mdo sde bshad pa las bstan pa de ltar ri bo po ta la'i gzhal med khang mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-2: rig sngags 'chang de yang 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi gzugs su snang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-3: ji ltar ri bo po ta la'i gzhal med khang bzhin du ri de la yang gzhal med khang snang ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-4: ri de la rin po che'i shing ljon pa sna tshogs snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-5: me tog sna tshogs kyi gzhal med khang snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-18: dong ka'i me tog sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-21: na la ma li ka dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-22: ku ba bya ka sna tshogs snang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-23: bya'i tshogs sna tshogs kyis legs par brgyan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-24: ri dvags kyi tshogs sna tshogs kyis gang ba snang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-25: gang gi tshe phyir bsdu ba byed par 'dod pa de'i tshe gnas gzhan du 'gro bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-26: gzhan yang dgos pa sna tshogs la rang gi blo gros la ji ltar snang ba bzhin bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-27: dgos pa thams cad la rab tu sbyar ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166a-28: bklags pa tsam gyis 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-0: don yod pa'i zhags pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi rig @166b sngags 'chang gi cho ga gsang ba'o ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-1: don yod pa'i sgyu ma rnam par 'phrul ba zhes bya ba'i sgrub pa'i cho ga ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-2: de nas de'i 'og tu phyag rgya bri ba'i dkyil 'khor bshad par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-3: rtags mtshon phyag rgya'i de nyid ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-4: padma rgyas dang sna tshogs mtshon //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-5: padma kha ni phyed bye ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-6: phyag dag na ni rab tu 'dzin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-7: phyag gnyis phyung zhing brkyang nas kyang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-8: bskum pa'am 'dzin stangs de nyid kyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-9: kun nas phreng ba 'bar ba'i rtags //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-10: mtshon cha phyag rgya bsnams pa ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-16: yid bzhin gyi nor bu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-21: zur gsum ma zhes bya ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-28: me tog gi thum po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-34: me tog gi phreng ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:166b-49: mdung rtse gsum pa'i phreng zlum dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-12: mu tig gi phreng ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-17: kun nas 'bar phreng phyag rgya de //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-18: sna tshogs rmad du byung bas smras //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-19: mtshon cha sna tshogs bsnams pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-21: ras la bris pa'am dkyil 'khor ram //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-22: rtsig pa'am gang yang rung ba la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-23: tshon rtsi rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-24: gang du bris pa mthong ba de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-25: ngan 'gro sems can dmyal bar ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-27: 'jig rten dbang gis rtag mchog sbyin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-28: sdig pa thams cad rnam par spangs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-29: gang zhig nyes byas mi bzad pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-30: mtshams med lnga po byed pa nyid; ;mnar med pa yi gnas dang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-31: dmyal ba gzhan du gzhol pa gang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-32: phyag rgya de dag mthong tsam gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-34: skye dang 'chi las rnam par grol //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-36: de dag skye ba phyir mar ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-37: phyir yang mngal gyis mi gos te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167a-38: yang dang yang du padma las //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-0: brdzus te skye ba dag @167b tu 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-1: rtag tu bde ba can du 'gro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-2: gang na 'dren pa tshe dpag med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-3: bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar rtag tu der //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-4: skye 'gyur the tshom mi za zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-6: rig sngags sna tshogs bde bar 'grub //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-8: rtag tu mi ldog sa nas 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-9: phyag rgya 'di dag mthong tsam gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-10: sangs rgyas byang chub dang mnyam 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-11: dus gsum gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-12: bla med dge rtsa bskyed par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-14: bsod nams phung po chen po 'thob; ;de nas dkyil 'khor rab bshad pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-15: de nyid 'grub pa'i phyag rgya rnams //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-17: 'dod pa thams cad rab tu sbyin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-18: sdig pa thams cad mod la sel; ;gang zhig mtshams med byed pa dag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-19: mi bzad mnar med gnas pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-21: dmyal ba'i sgo rnams bcad nas ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-22: mtho ris sgo phye the tshom med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-23: sgo phye gyur pa rnams la ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-24: sangs rgyas zhing rnams snang bar 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-25: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis dgongs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:167b-26: mgon po 'jig rten dbang phyug gi phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor mthong ba tsam gyis sems can phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-0: shi 'phos pa'i mod la bde ba can du skye bar @168a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-2: dkyil 'khor 'dir zhugs pa tsam gyis gang na thub pa 'dren pa 'od dpag med bzhugs pa'i pho brang du myur du 'jug par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-3: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi lham pa la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-4: kun nas cha ni mdzes par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-5: gru bzhi go la'i tshad tsam la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-6: sgo bzhi them skas bzhi yis brgyan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-7: shin tu legs par bskus dang ldan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-8: 'jam zhing mnyen la mnyam pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-9: sa yi cha dang ldan pa la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-10: dkyil 'khor shes rab can gyis dbye //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-11: dkyil 'khor de nyid thig btab la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-12: phyag rgya bri ba rnam par dbye //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-13: phyogs bzhi'i cha ni mnyam pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-14: dbus na dkyil 'khor snying po yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-15: gru bzhi pa la kun nas kha khyer gyi rnam pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-16: mdung rtse gsum pa'i phreng ba rnam par dbye'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-17: gru bzhi pa'i dbus su phyag rgya don yod pa'i zhags pa'i phyag rgya kun nas 'bar ba bla na med pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-18: phyag rgya rgyan gyis brgyan pa tshon rtsi sna tshogs kyis bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-19: dbus kyis dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol gyi phyag rgya bri ba yang shin tu 'byin par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-22: rgyal mtshan gyis brgyan la kun tu yungs kar dkar po gtor ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168a-23: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol gyi gnas su phyogs bzhi kun tu bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-0: ba lang gi lci ba sa dang bsres pas shin tu legs @168b par byugs pa dang ldan pa la tshon rtsi'i phye mas kha khyer gyi rnam pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-1: kun nas padma'i phreng ba chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-2: mtshon cha bris la 'di'i sgo bzhi yang rnam par 'byes par bri'o; ;ji ltar phyag rgya dang mthun pa'i ro sna tshogs kyis gtor ma gzhag par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-3: phyag rgya re re la yang mchod yon phul la dbyib mo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-7: rdze'u gtor mas bkang la gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-8: kun tu bum pa gang ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-9: bdug spos kyi ni snod dag dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-10: me tog 'bras bu sna tshogs dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-11: gtor ma dkar po dag gis bkang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-12: me tog rnam par bkram byas la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-13: kun tu phreng bas gzhag par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-14: phreng ba bzang po bzhag nas kyang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-15: de bzhin kun tu bdug spos dbul //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-16: aa ga ru dang tsandan dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-24: ga pur gyi bdug pa 'di dag gis bdugs la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-28: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du 'jug pas don yod pa'i rgyal po dran par byas te bskor la phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor la phyag bya zhing phyag rgya thams cad la me tog bkram zhing me tog gtor ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:168b-29: gang phyag rgya'i de kho na nyid gsang ba 'di dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-0: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor 'di sgrub pa gang @169a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-1: dgos pa la sngar dkyil 'khor phyag rgya dang bcas pa la mchog tu mdzes par byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-3: rig sngags 'chang ba gtsang ma yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-4: gtsang ma yi ni gos bgos la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-5: ji ltar dkyil 'khor cho ga bzhin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-6: dkyil 'khor du ni gzhug par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-7: ji ltar dkyil 'khor la bgos pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-8: de bzhin du ni las bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-9: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bla med pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-11: thub pa snang mdzad kyis gsungs pa'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-12: spyi yi rigs ni thams cad du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-13: phyag rgya dkrigs dang gtams rnams kyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-14: dam tshig kun tu shes par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-15: spyi rigs kun gyi cho ga yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-16: dam tshig rjes zhugs de bzhin no; ;dkyil 'khor kun tu zhugs pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-17: rgyal bas lung ni bstan par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-18: kun gzigs de bzhin gshegs pa yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-19: phyag ni spyi bor 'jog par mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-20: chos kyi ro ni bdud rtsi yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-22: rnam snang mdzad gsung dkyil 'khor du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-23: don yod dngos grub stsol ba mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-24: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gang bzhugs pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-25: kun tu spyi yi rigs rnams kyi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169a-26: don yod dngos grub mchog myur thob //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-0: sangs rgyas bye ba gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma khrag khrig brgya stong phrag @169b dgu bcu rtsa dgu'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i drung du dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-1: bsod nams kyi phung po chen po dang ldan par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-2: yon tan gyi phan yon 'di dag ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-3: tshe 'di yin par khong du chud par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-4: bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su padma las brdzus te skyes par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-5: tshe rabs su tshe rabs dran zhing 'od zer bye ba 'bar ba'i lus dang ldan zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-6: tshe bskal pa brgya stong dpag tu med par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-7: yon tan thams cad dri ma med par snang ba don yod pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa bstan pa bkod pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin 'thob ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-8: gang ting nge 'dzin thob pas sgyu ma chen po lta bu'i rnam par 'phrul pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul ston par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-9: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi lha'i spyi'i rigs de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi byin gyi rlabs kyis rjes su 'jug par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-17: mi dang mi ma yin pa thams cad dbang du gyur nas rtag tu rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:169b-19: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis dkyil 'khor rnams 'byor ba gzigs nas srung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-1: thams cad phyi bzhin 'brang zhing mchod pa chen po byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-3: 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis mchod pa'i 'os chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-4: sems can thams cad gcig tu bla mar byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-5: nad thams cad med par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-6: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par dag par 'gyur ro; ;mtshan ma bri ba'i phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga'o ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-7: de nas sbyin sreg gi cho ga'i dkyil 'khor bshad par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-8: rig sngags 'chang ba rnam dag gi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-9: 'di nyid sgrub pa bsgrub pa'i phyir //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-10: spyi yi rigs rnams thams cad kyi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-11: cho ga zhib mo bla med yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-12: gang gis sbyin sreg byas tsam gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-13: phyogs kun rnam par gzigs pa yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-14: de bzhin gshegs nas byon 'gyur zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-15: byang chub sems dpa' dgongs par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-16: rigs rnams dngos grub rjes stsol cing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-17: rtag tu srung ba mdzad par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-18: mgon po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-19: the tshom med par myur du byon //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-20: mgon po 'khor bcas gnas nyid na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-21: rang gi gzugs su mthong bar 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-22: 'dod pa thams cad rtag tu stsol //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-23: rtag tu mchog ni stsol ba nyid //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-24: nyin dang mtshan du rtag par ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170a-25: rnam par gzigs 'gyur the tshom med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-1: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi shin tu mdzes par bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-2: rgya chen po ko la'i tshad tsam la legs par byugs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-6: them skas bzhi dang ldan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-9: dbus kyi dkyil 'khor gyi snying por yang bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-10: me yi gnas kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-11: gru bzhi nyid kyi rnam pa la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-12: kun nas them skas bzhi dag dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-13: steng du gra ni bzhi pa bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-14: rtag tu padma'i snying po dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-15: snying po rgyas pa'i steng du yang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-16: kun nas 'dab ma mdzes par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-17: gra bzhir padma'i phreng ba bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-18: de bzhin du gra gnyis kar rdo rje padma dang bcas pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-19: gsum par mdung rtse gsum padma dang bcas pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-20: bzhi par 'khor lo padma dang bcas pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-21: lnga par bum pa gang ba gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-22: sna tshogs tshon gyis rnam mdzes pa'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-23: kun nas 'dab ma'i myu gu bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-24: rin chen snod ni bkang ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-25: me tog phreng dang ngang pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-26: phye ma padmar bcas pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-27: de bzhin me tog rigs dag nyid //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-28: de bzhin sna tshogs brgyan pa 'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-29: nub kyi gnas dag gra dag tu; ;padma'i 'dab ma autpal bcas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-30: bum pa dur bas bkang ba bri //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-31: rtsa ba'i bum pa dbu ma la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:170b-32: 'dir ni kha khyer thig kyang gdab //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-1: ba; ;thig gis kun nas cha mnyam zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-2: sgo bzhi mdzes par bya ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-3: tshon sna lnga yi skud pas gdab //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-4: me 'bar mdog can bri ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-5: kun nas 'bar ba'i phreng ba can //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-6: gra dang grar ni me lha bri //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-7: lus ni me mdog 'bar ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-9: mtshan ma sna tshogs gzhan dag kyang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-10: cho ga bzhin du bri bar bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-11: dkyil 'khor gyi ni cho ga bzhin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-12: ba dan mda' dang sna lnga yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-13: skud pas bum pa gang dkris dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-14: de bzhin bdug spos snod dag gis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-15: kun nas dkyil 'khor brgyan par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-16: sna tshogs gzugs can rgya che yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-17: sna tshogs ro yi gtor ma gzhag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-18: rdze'u dang kham phor rnam gsum gyi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-19: dkar pos bkang ba gzhag par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-20: rdze'u dang dbyib mo bum pa ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-21: gtor mas bkang pa kun tu gzhag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-22: 'bras bu rnam pa sna tshogs gzhag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-23: kun nas me tog dgram bya zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-24: phreng ba sna tshogs gzhag par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-25: 'bras yos yungs kar gtor nas ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-26: kun tu mar me 'bar ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-27: sna tshogs dri dang de bzhin du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-28: dri yi phye ma lha bshos dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-29: dkyil 'khor kun la gzhag par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-30: dkyil 'khor dag ni thams cad la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-31: blugs gzar dur ba rtag tu gzhag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-32: shing ni aarga shi mi dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171a-33: yungs kar 'bras ni so ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-0: @171b zhun mar dang ni mar dkar dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-1: kun tu ru ka tsandan dkar //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-2: sbyin sreg cho gar 'dir bzhag ste //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-3: dus gsum rtag tu rig 'dzin gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-4: sbyin sreg brgya rtsa brgyad du bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-5: rig pa 'dzin pa gtsang ma yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-6: gtsang ma yi ni gos bgos la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-7: dkar gsum gyi ni zas bza' zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-8: gzhan ni bza' dang spyad mi bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-9: dkyil 'khor gyi ni nub sgo nas; ;dkyil 'khor shes pa 'jug bya zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-10: darbha'i stan la skyil krung du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-11: shar phyogs kha bltas 'dug par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-12: byams pa'i sems la mnyam bzhag ste //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-13: don yod rgyal po dran bya zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-14: snga dro'i dus su sbyin sreg bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-15: gung la slob ma gzhug bya zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-16: spyi yi rigs kyi sreg blugs ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-17: phye ma red dus su bya ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-18: gang zhig dkyil 'khor du zhugs la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-19: sbyin sreg dkyil 'khor de nyid dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-20: grub pa kun tu cho ga yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-21: bdag nyid dbang bskur me kun gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-22: sbyin sreg byed pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-23: kun tu gnas ni thams cad na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-24: rgyas pa gnas mchog rva gcig dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-25: ga ra ge de bzhin phur bu dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-26: mdun na 'don pa me lha ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-27: sbyin sreg byed pa 'jig rten pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-28: mtshungs zhes ston pas lung bstan to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-30: rig 'dzin dbang po chen po dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:171b-31: phyag na rdo rje tshangs pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-2: mnyam pa pas kyang lhag pa nyid //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-3: me yi sbyin sreg byed pa la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-4: de bzhin gshegs kun byin gyis rlob //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-5: gal te zhag bdun dus gsum du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-6: de la sogs pa'i las rnams ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-7: me la sbyin sreg byed pa la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-8: mod la mngon shes lnga thob ces //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-10: las ni byas nas de nas ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-11: sbyin sreg las ni brtsam par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-12: sreg blugs sbyin sreg byas tsam gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-15: de bzhin gshegs kun dgyes par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-16: byang chub sems dpa' byon nas ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-17: mod la mthong ba'i sbyin par mdzod //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-18: sdig pa thams cad sreg par 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-19: shin tu mi bzad sngon gyi las //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-20: sreg blugs tsam gyi mod la sreg /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-21: 'bar ba'i me yis phye leb bzhin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-22: de la sogs pa'i sdig pa ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-24: sdang ba'i phyir ni rgol nyid dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-25: mi bzad phas kyi dgra rnams dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-26: pha rol dpung gis 'jigs pa nyid //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-27: de bzhin du yang rgyal po'i dpung //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-28: de kun sbyin sreg byas tsam gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-29: mi snang bar 'gyur the tshom med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-30: de bzhin mi ngas gcod kun dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172a-31: nad kun rab tu zhi bar 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-0: mu ge'i dgon pa'i 'jigs @172b nyid kyang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-1: sbyin sreg byas pa tsam gyis 'jig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-2: gnod sbyin srin po 'byung po dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-3: de bzhin gshegs dang log 'dren dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-4: sha za brjed byed yi dvags dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-5: de bzhin rnam pa sna tshogs gdon //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-6: 'di kun sbyin sreg byas tsam gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-8: rtag tu 'jigs med lo legs shing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-9: gling dang bde bar 'gyur ba yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-10: rtag tu sems can thams cad ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-11: kun tu rgyal bar 'gyur ba yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-12: rgyal po dpung dang bcas pa nyid //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-13: btsun mor bcas pa nyid kyang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-14: rtag par kun tu gsal bar ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-15: mi 'jigs sbyin par the tshom med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-16: rtag tu nad med 'gyur ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-17: dga' zhing yid ni bde ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-18: lus can dag ni thams cad la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-19: rtag tu dga' bar byed cing gnas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-20: rtag tu me yi lha nyid ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-21: rgyun du mthong bar 'dod pa yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-22: me la sbyin sreg byas tsam gyis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-23: me lha nyid ni bzhugs gyur te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-24: rtag tu las ni thams cad mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-27: thams cad du ni mthong ba ster //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-28: rgyu skar zla ba nyi ma dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-29: gshin rje dang ni chu lha dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-30: rgyal po chen po bzhi po dag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-31: dpung bcas bzhon par bcas pa yang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:172b-32: nyin dang mtshan du rtag par ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-0: ci ste rig sngags 'chang don yod pa'i rgyal po'i @173a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-2: rig sngags 'chang gtsang ma des shin tu khrus byas la gos gtsang ma bgo bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-3: nyin zhag gcig smyung ba bya zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-4: shing aarga'i yam shing sreg gi me sbar la padma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-6: 'bras so ba'i sbyin sreg brgyad brgya byas nas sreg blugs lan gcig byas pas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-7: mtshams med pa lnga byed pa yang 'grub par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-9: yid gnyis bskyed par mi bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-10: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyi'i rigs kyi dngos grub 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-11: rig sngags 'chang des byang chub kyi shing gi me sbar la rigs spyir padma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-13: yungs kar dkar po dang zhun mar bsres pa'i sbyin sreg brgyad brgya byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-14: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyi'i rigs kyi dngos grub 'thob ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-15: thams cad cho ga chen po zhib mo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-16: sbyin sreg chen po'i cho gar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-17: de nas pha rol gyi dmag tshogs gzhom par 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-18: rig sngags 'chang gtsang ma des shin tu khrus byas la gos gtsang ma bgos /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-19: seng ldeng gi me sbar la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173a-23: gu gul gyi sreg blugs kyis sbyin sreg brgyad stong byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-0: dpag tshad stong tshun chad kyi pha rol gyi @173b dmag tshogs bcing ba byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-1: pha rol gyi dmag tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-4: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis shing kar ba ka'i me sbar la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-5: sbrul gyi pags pa brjes pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-7: lan tshva 'bras s'a lu dang bsres pa yungs kar mar dang sbyar ba'i sbyin sreg byas na dpag tshad stong tshun chad kyi pha rol gyi dmag tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-8: dgra la gnam lcags chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-9: rlung grang mo 'bab pas phongs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-10: yid mi bde ba skye bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-11: dgra thams cad rnam par 'jig par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-13: rig sngags 'chang des nyin zhag gcig smyung ba byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-14: shin tu khrus byas pa gtsang mas dri sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-17: sha ta pus pa zhun mar dang sbyar ba'i sbyin sreg mtshan gcig la dus gsum du byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-18: klu'i rgyal pos char gyi rgyun chen po 'bebs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-19: 'dzam bu'i gling mtha' dag tu zhag bdun gyi bar du char 'bab par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-20: char de nyid ha cang ches na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-21: thal ba nam mkha' la gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-22: ha cang ches pa 'chad par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:173b-23: yang me lha 'ong bar 'dod cing rang gi gzugs su mthong bar 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-1: gos gtsang ma bgos la nyin zhag gcig gnas par gyur pas shing sna ma'i me sbar la 'bras so ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-3: bu ram sha khar dang bcas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-5: sna ma'i me tog bsres pa brgyad stong sbyin sreg bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-7: me lha me'i nang nas lus phyed phyung ste 'dug nas rig sngags 'chang la ci bgyi bka' stsol cig ces zer zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-8: ji ltar rig sngags 'chang gi cho ga'i don du 'gyur ba de bzhin du smra'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-9: thams cad sbyin pa zhes bya ba; mchog thams cad sbyin pa zhes bya ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-10: bdud rtsi 'bar ba zhes bya ba'i me'i kha /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-11: kha'i mchog sbyin par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-12: gang bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i me'i kha thob pas gang du dbugs phyung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-13: rdubs pa der me 'bar ba 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-14: gang du phu zhes byas pa der me 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-15: mun nag tu dbugs phyung na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-17: tsandan dkar po'i sbyin sreg stong rtsa brgyad byas pas 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug nyid kyi gzugs ston par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-18: sa bon bdun gyi sbyin sreg gis nad thams cad zhi bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-19: 'bras so ba'i sbyin sreg gis ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-20: rgyal po dbang du byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174a-21: phub ma dang lan tshva'i sbyin sreg gis ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-1: 'bras yos dang yungs kar gyi sbyin sreg gis ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-2: sems can thams cad dbang du byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-5: zhun mar gyi sbyin sreg gis ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-7: k'a ra b'i ra'i me tog dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-8: gu gul zhun mar dang sbyar ba'i sbyin sreg gis ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-10: de bzhin du 'dir las thams cad byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-11: sbyin sreg gi dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga'o ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-12: ri mo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgrub pa'i cho ga bshad par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-13: kun tu thun mong sgrub pa'i mchog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-14: dge ba'i las kun byed pa ste //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-15: sangs rgyas thams cad mthong 'gyur zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-16: bla med bsod nams chen po gsog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-17: don yod rgyal po de nyid ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-18: rnam pa sna tshogs gzugs dag tu //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-20: mthu dang dngos grub sna tshogs pa'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-21: 'jig rten pa yi gzugs bya ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-22: grub pa sna tshogs byed pa'i gnas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-23: so so'i gzugs su bya ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-24: ras sam yang na dar dag la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-26: don yod pa yi rgyal po ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-27: khru gang tsam gyi tshad dam yang na tshad shin tu rnam par 'byed padma'i mdog lta bu phyag brgyad pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-29: de bzhin du spyan gsum pa zhi ba'i zhal du bri bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:174b-30: de bzhin du zhags pa 'dzin pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-2: ril ba spyi blugs 'dzin pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-3: yid bzhin gyi nor bu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-7: me tog thum po 'dzin par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-10: g-yas su 'phags ma sgrol ma thal mo sbyar la dbu yid tsam 'dud pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-11: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-12: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-14: dbu rgyan 'od dpag med kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-15: g-yas phyogs kyi dbu zla ba tshes pas brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-16: ri dvags kyi pags pa mnabs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-18: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-20: nang rim du padma'i phreng ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-21: rim pa gnyis par rdo rje phreng ba lcags kyu dang bcas par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-22: rim pa gsum par nor bu rin po che'i phreng ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-23: rin po che sna tshogs mdzes pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-24: rim pa bzhi par mdung rtse gsum pa'i phreng ba'o; ;rim pa lnga par kun nas 'bar ba'i phreng ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-25: steng dang g-yas phyogs kyi gnas su dbang po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-28: dbang phyug chen po me tog sna tshogs thogs par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175a-34: lha'i bu rnams bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-0: me tog sna tshogs @175b thogs par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-1: lha mo sgrol ma'i rgyab tu khro bo'i rgyal po don yod pa'i zhags pa bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-6: sku rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-8: 'od dpag med kyi dbu rgyan can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-10: g-yas pa zla bas brgyan cing ral gri 'dzin pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-12: mdung rtse gsum pa 'dzin pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-14: dkar mo'i rgyab tu rig sngags kyi rgyal po dbu gsum pa bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-16: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-17: dbu rgyan rgyal ba 'od dpag med can thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-19: nor bu rin po che 'dzin par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-27: pho nya mo zhi ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-30: rgyal po chen po bzhi bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-31: steng dang g-yas g-yon du sangs rgyas kyi sku gzugs skyil mo krung bcas pa sor bzhi ba'i tshad tsam bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-32: nyi ma dang zla ba'i lha rgyu skar dang bcas pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-33: ri mo'i gzugs kyi phyi rol gyi rim pa kun tu phyag rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-34: phyag mtshan sna tshogs rdzogs par bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:175b-35: klu brgyad bya zhing kun nas 'bar ba dang bcas par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-2: ri mo'i cho ga'i gnas 'di ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-3: sdig pa thams cad mod la sel //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-4: mtshams med lnga po sbyong bar byed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-6: dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa'i ri mo'i gzugs grub pa 'di ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-7: spyi'i rigs thams cad du 'jug pa ston pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-8: phyi'i rigs thams cad kyi de kho na nyid kyi ri mo'i dkyil 'khor 'di ni; dus gsum du gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-9: de bzhin du byang chub sems dpas kyang byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-10: don yod pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyi ri mo 'di ni; thub pa rnam par snang mdzad kyis byin gyis brlabs pa ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-11: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i de kho na nyid snying por gyur pa de kho na nyid gsang ba 'di mthong ba tsam gyis rnam par thar pa 'thob cing lung bstan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-12: mthong ba tsam gyis cho ga zhib mo bla na med pa thams cad 'grub bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-13: rnam par snang mdzad 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor chen po dang ldan par snang ba byed pa gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma khrag khrig brgya stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa dgu mngon sum du mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-15: rig sngags cho ga bla med pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-16: spyi rigs yang dag 'byung ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-17: thub pa rnam snang mdzad kyis bstan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176a-18: de bzhin gshegs rigs grub pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-0: @176b gang yang padma'i rigs de bzhin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-1: nor rigs de nyid 'byung ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-2: rdo rje'i rigs gang bla med pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-3: spyi rigs 'di nyid mthong ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-4: ri mo mthong ba'i khyad par yin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-6: dmyal ba ngan 'gro'i sgo bcad de //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-7: mtho rigs kyi ni sgo yang phye //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-8: bla na med pa ston pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-10: bsod nams bla na med pa yin; ;ci ste don yod pa'i 'jig rten dbang phyug gi gzugs mthong bar 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-11: rig sngags 'chang des tsandan dkar po las 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug don yod pa'i zhags pa sor brgyad kyi tshad tsam la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-12: gnad kyis gnas kyi cha'i so tshad shin tu rnam par mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-21: sen mo thams cad kyi cha'i mnyam zhing mdzes pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-23: sen mo tshad shin tu mdzes shing cod pan gyi rgyal ba'i g-yas phyogs na zla gam zhi ba'i gzugs can spyan gsum phyag bzhi shin tu mdzes pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-24: dbu skra shin tu mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-25: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa'i gzugs dang ldan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-27: g-yon pa 'od dpag can phyag na padma bsnams pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:176b-28: phyag g-yas pa mdung rtse gsum pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-0: @177a *// dbugs 'byin cing rtag tu mchog sbyin par mdzad pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-1: padma'i gdan la bzhugs par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-3: dkar mo yang 'od 'dom gang dang bcas par dgod do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-4: mgon po shin tu mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-6: mu tig gi rgyan gyi mtshams su gser gyi rgyan gyis g-yogs pa'i cod pan nam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-7: yang na spyi gtsug tu ring bsrel bzhag par byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-8: tsandan dkar po'i dkyil 'khor bya zhing gur gum dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-10: ga bur gyis mchod la dkyil 'khor gyi snying po 'di'i dbus su padma ge sar dang bcas pa'i 'dab ma sum cu rtsa gnyis pa bris la de'i dbus su 'jigs pa med pas 'jig rten dbang phyug dar gyi con pan gyis bcings pa bzhag la; aa ga ru dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-11: tsandan gyi bdug pa dbul zhing me tog dgram par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-12: me tog gi phreng bas mchod par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-13: rig sngags 'chang gtsang mar gyur pa shin tu khrus byas pa gos gtsang ma bgos pas smyung ba byas la mgon po 'jig rten dbang phyug mngon du phyogs par skyil mo krung bcas te 'dug la mchod yon dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-14: lha bshos phul la byams pa'i sems la mnyam par bzhag ste sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa bsgom mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177a-15: sems can thams cad la brtse bar gyur pa'i ting nge 'dzin yang bsgom zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-0: @177b gtam gzhan mi smra bar shin tu yongs su sbyar ba legs par spyod cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-1: gzhan 'jigs pa med pas bdag srung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-3: dkyil 'khor bcing ba bsrung ba dang bcas pa yang byas la bzlas brjod de nyid stong rtsa brgyad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-4: phyag rgya yang stong rtsa brgyad brtsams na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-5: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug 'bar zhing g-yo ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-8: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi mchog sbyin par mdzad pa'i phyag spyi bor bzhag ste legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-9: rig sngags 'chang khyod kyis mchod pa dam pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-10: gsang sngags kyi cho ga chen po byas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-11: sgrub pa dam pa byas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-12: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyi rigs 'di dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-13: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs thams cad kyi cho ga zhib mo gsang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-16: thams cad du spyi'i dngos grub rig sngags 'chang khyod la 'grub kyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-17: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po rjes su zungs shig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-18: rig sngags 'chang ji ltar yid la byed pa de ltar 'dod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-19: mchog thams cad ji ltar yid la bsam pa de thams cad rjes su sbyin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:177b-21: khyod kyi skye ba'i 'khor ba tha ma yin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-0: mngal du gnas pa las yongs su grol bar @178a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-3: khyod shi 'phos nas bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su padma las brdzus te skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-4: de bzhin gshegs pa tshe dpag med mngon sum du mthong bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-5: mngon sum du chos nyan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-6: byang chub kyi snying po la gnas kyi bar tshe'i tshad bskal ba brgya stong dpag tu med; grangs med /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-9: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis khro bo'i rgyal po gang la khro bo'i rgyal po me tog gam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-10: cod pa na la mngon par gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-11: des na 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug rang gi skur bzhugs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-12: rig sngags 'chang nam mkha' la 'gro zhing don yod pa'i ye shes bkod pa dri ma med pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin 'thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-13: yangs pa chen pos rnam par thar ba'i dkyil 'khor don yod pa'i zhags pa'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-14: sku gzugs sgrub pa de kho na nyid ces pa 'di gal te rig sngags 'chang skal pa chung ba mnar med par gzhol ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-15: mtshams med pa lnga byed pa de lan gcig nges par sgrub pa tsam gyis mdun du rang gi gzugs kyis nges par mchis par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178a-16: gal te de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-0: dus gsum du @178b gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas la sdang bas khrag dbyung bar sems bskyed pa des kyang de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-1: dus gsum du gshegs pa sangs rgyas gyis dgongs pa'i dam tshig chen pos byin gyis brlabs de rig sngags 'chang sgrub na rmi lam du bdag gis gzugs mthong ba stsal bar bgyi zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-2: yid la bsam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-3: mchog thams cad rjes su stsal bar bgyi zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-4: sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad rnam par dag par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-5: dri ma med par rnam par thar pa'i 'od zer gyi dkyil 'khor la rnam par lta ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin 'thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-6: sad nas 'jig rten pa thams cad kyi mchod pa'i 'os chen po gcig pur 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-7: skye bo thams cad kyis mchod par bya ba chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-8: sgrib pa dang bral zhing rnam par dag pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-9: sgo kun tu dri ma med par snang ba zhes bya ba'i lus yongs su dag pa 'thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-10: sems can gang dag gis de mthong bar gyur pa de dag thams cad sgrib pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-11: nad thams cad dang bral zhing nyon mongs pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-12: gdol pas kyang dad pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:178b-13: gus pas sgrub pa rnam pa gsum dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-0: cho ga gzhan gyis kyang nges par yid la bsam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs @179a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-2: rang gi gzugs kyis mthong ba stsal bar bgyi na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-3: mir gyur ba dad pa'i rjes su 'brang ba sdom brtson can gyis lta smos kyang ci 'tshal te; dran pa tsam gyis bdag rang gi gzugs kyis mdun na mchis par bgyi zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-4: yid la bsam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-6: yid gnyis bskyed par mi bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-9: sems can tshe gcig pu pa de la rig sngags grub pa'i dngos grub rjes su stsal bar bdag gis rngo mi thogs lags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-10: gang yang phyi ma'i dus na dge slong dag dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-11: rig sngags 'chang ba'i sems can ser sna can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-13: yid gnyis su mi byed pa; ngo gnyis can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-16: pha rol gyi rdzas la brkam chags can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-21: khengs pa; gzhan gyi rdzas 'phrog pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-22: mkhan po dang slob dpon phyag rgya dang dkyil 'khor ston pa'i bla ma la ma gus pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-23: rig sngags kyi cho ga zhib mo 'di ston pa la ma gus pa nyid brkam chags can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-24: byas pa mi gzo ba nyid dag 'byung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-25: sems can de dag la bskyang bar bstan pa'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179a-26: dngos grub bstan par rngo mi thogs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-0: @179b bdag la yang brnyas par bgyid pa'i sems can de lta bu mang du 'byung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-1: bdag la yang sun par bgyid pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-2: bdag la yang ma gus par bgyed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-4: sdang bas khrag 'byin par bgyid pa dag 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-5: bdag la yang 'khu bar bgyid pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-6: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-7: spyi'i rigs kyi dam tshig sun par bgyid pa'i sems can de ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-8: smad par 'os pa zhes brjod par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-9: rig sngags kyi cho ga zhib mo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-10: dam tshig kun nas 'joms par bgyid pa'i gdol ba zhes rigs par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-11: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba kun nas 'joms pa zhes rig par bgyi'o; ;de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-13: dkyil 'khor kun nas 'joms pa zhes rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-14: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi dam tshig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-17: phyag rgya kun nas 'joms pa zhes rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-18: de dag gis bdag la smad pas sems can de dag gi sdig pas gdol ba zhes bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:179b-21: smod par 'os par rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-1: pa lta bu; rig sngags nyams pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-3: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyis smad pa zhes bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-4: 'jig rten pa dang 'jig rten las 'das pa chud gzhan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-6: dmyal bar gzhol ba de dag ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-8: bdag gis yongs su spangs pa ma lags so; ;de lta mod kyi dus gsum du gshegs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa yongs su spangs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-9: dus gsum du gshegs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' yongs su spangs pa; rdo rje dam tshig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-11: phyag rgya thams cad spangs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-12: thub pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-13: dam tshig yongs su spangs pas bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-14: sdang ba thams cad kyis zin cing nad kyis yongs su zin par 'gyur ba de dag ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-16: bdag gis yongs sum spangs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-19: dkyil 'khor dang dam tshig bsregs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-20: phyag rgya byed pa dang bcas par bsregs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-22: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dang rigs sun par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180a-23: sdig pa'i dge slong mang po de dag ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-0: des na bskal pa mang po rdul phra mo @180b bsags pa'i bskal par sdug bsngal nyams su myong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-1: 'jig rten 'di dang 'jig rten pha rol gyi bde ba can med do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-3: sems can rig sngags kyi ched du rig sngags rjes su sems pas byams pa'i sems su bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-4: gang gi drung du phyag rgya dang gsang sngags rim pa phye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-5: rig sngags gsang ba rnyed par 'gyur ba de la des gus pa chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-6: bla mar bgyid pa chen po bskyed par bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-7: pha dang ma dang 'dra ba'i sems bskyed par bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-8: pha dang ma'i gus pa bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-25: dran pa tsam gyis kyang bdag gi gzugs mthong ba rjes su stsal bar bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-26: rgyun du rjes su 'brang bar bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-27: bdag rgyun du rjes su 'brang ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-28: ji ltar chab kyi nang du til mar gyi thigs pa stsal ba ltar dngos grub kun tu mchi bar bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-29: rgya mtsho'i dus rlabs bzhin du thams cad du mchi bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:180b-31: lcags kyus dmyal ba thams cad drang bar bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-1: gshegs pa'i lam la so sor gzhag par bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-4: gzi brjid chen po 'jug par bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-5: thams cad du sgrub pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-8: de nas tsandan gyi gzugs 'di mthong bas 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug nyid kyi gzugs mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-9: de mtshungs par 'tshal bar bgyis te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-10: bdag rang gi gzugs kyis rgyun kho nar gnas par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-11: gang na cho ga 'di gnas pa de mchod rten dang bcas par mtshungs par rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-13: ston pa bla ma bzhugs pa'i gnas su rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-14: gang na dus gsum du gshegs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyi'i dam tshig gnas pa 'di sangs rgyas kyi gnas so zhes rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-15: de gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor rmad du byung ba zhes rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-16: lha thams cad kyi gnas dang dam tshig go zhes rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-17: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs thams cad kyi gnas byang chub kyi snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-18: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181a-20: yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po yang dag par ston pa'i gnas so zhes rig par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-0: sa phyogs 'dir rin po che sna @181b bdun gyi gzhal med khang gi gnas bkod pas brgyan par rig par bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-1: de la the tshom dang yid gnyis bskyed par mi bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-2: de nas de'i 'og tu gnas thams cad du gtogs pa'i dngos grub chen po sgyu ma chen po'i rnam par 'phrul pa'i gnas byed par 'dod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-3: dgos pa thams cad byed par 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-4: rig sngags 'chang des dri sna tshogs la 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi gzugs sor bcu drug pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-6: sku shin tu tshad dang ldan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-8: de bzhin du zhal gsum pa bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-13: ral pa'i thor tshugs kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-14: 'od dpag med pa'i dbu rgyan 'chang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-17: khro bo'i rgyal po'i gzugs can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-20: ral pa'i thor tshugs kyi steng gi ral pa la 'od dpag med pa'i dbu rgyan 'chang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-21: zla gam g-yas phyogs na gnas pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-24: khros pa'i lta stangs su lta ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-27: 'od dpag med pa'i dbu rgyan 'chang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:181b-29: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-3: mdud rtse gsum pa thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-6: rin po che'i dbyug pa thogs pa; padma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-7: g-yas na lha mo sgrol ma thal mo sbyar cing 'dud pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-8: g-yon na dkar mo thal mo sbyar te yid tsam du 'dud pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-9: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-10: me tog sna tshogs kyis legs par brgyan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-11: zhabs kyi drung du rig sngags 'chang gser gyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-12: lag na me tog thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-13: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la kha bltas nas pus mo btsugs te 'dug par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-14: lhag ma ma yin pa'i tshon rtsis tshad dang ma 'dres par spyan dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-17: sen mo'i gnas su sbyar bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-18: 'phags pa don yod pa'i zhags pa'i cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-20: de nas rdzas bshad par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182a-21: 'jigs pa med pas spos kyi rigs tsandan dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-1: spra tshil dang lhan cig sbyar ba'i phye ma zhib mo shin tu 'jam pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-2: shin tu mnyen pa mchog 'di gtsang ba gtsang sbra spyod pas thub pa 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dge zhing shin tu dul ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-3: rab tu zhi ba'i rnam par shin tu mdzes par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-4: gsang sngags brgyad stong bzlas brjod byas pas lan gcig sgrub pa ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-6: 'di yongs su rdzogs nas khro bo'i rgyal pos thams cad la mngon du gtor te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-7: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis las brtsam mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-8: de nas rig sngags 'chang gtsang mar gyur pas gos gtsang ma bgos te shin tu khrus byas la dris byugs pas dkyil 'khor gru bzhi shin tu mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-9: gsal ba ko la'i tshad tsam gyi dkyil 'khor bzang po legs par byugs pa shin tu gsal ba bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-10: dri sna tshogs kyis byugs pa shin tu 'jam pa la tsandan dkar po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-11: gur gum gyis dbus su las kyi dkyil 'khor rnam par phye ba bri bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-13: 'dab ma brgya rtsa brgyad pa ge sar dang snying por bcas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-16: tsandan dang gur gum gyis bri bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-19: bum pa spos chus bkang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:182b-20: de bzhin du dri chu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-0: gtor ma thams cad dri sna tshogs @183a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-2: ci yod pa'i gtor ma bzhag ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-3: de nas 'dir dkyil 'khor bya ba'i gnas sam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-6: gang du gnas par 'gyur ba der khru gang tshad dam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-10: de bzhin du bdug spos dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-14: kun tu ru'o; ;ba dan kha dog sna tshogs pas dkyil 'khor kun nas brgyan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-15: me tog phreng ba dgram bya zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-18: kun tu mar me'i phreng ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-19: de nas dri las byas pa'i 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su padma'i ge sar gyi steng du bzhag pa la rig sngags 'chang mngon du phyogs par skyil mo krung bcas te 'dug nas gzhan mi smra bar bzlas brjod brgyad stong brtsam par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-21: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi sku las 'od zer sna tshogs 'byung zhing sa cher g-yo bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-22: rang gi lag pa g-yas pa 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-23: gzugs brnyan las rig sngags 'chang legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-24: khyod kyis 'dod pa'i las thams cad grub pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183a-25: don yod pa chen po'i 'khor lo rnam par 'phrul pa'i dngos grub dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-0: thams cad du dgos pa grub pa @183b de kho na nyid grub bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-1: khyod kyis don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po 'di mchog tu grub pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-2: khyod kyis sgrub pa'i cho ga rgya cher mchog tu sgrub bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-4: de nas rig sngags 'chang gi dgos pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga ji ltar dgos par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-8: de nas rig sngags 'chang gang gi tshe dgos pa byung ba de'i tshe dri las byas pa'i mgon po la sngar mchod pa bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-9: de nas dgos pa thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-10: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug mdun du bzhag la bzlas brjod brgya rtsa brgyad byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-11: dgos pa sna tshogs rmi lam du ston cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-12: ji ltar bsam pa thams cad ston par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-13: de'i mdun du tsandan dkar po las dkyil 'khor byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-14: tsandan dkar po'i sbyin sreg brgya rtsa brgyad bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-15: de nas thal ba la bzlas brjod lan brgya rtsa brgyad bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-16: rang gi lus mtha' dag khyab par bsku zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-18: yungs kar gyi byug pa phyogs bzhir gtor na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-19: 'jig rten dbang phyug gi gzugs ji ltar de ltar 'jig rten thams cad kyis mngon sum du mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:183b-20: ji srid du phyir bsdu ba ma byas pa de srid du 'jig rten dbang phyug gi gzugs su snang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-0: dri chu dang yungs kar gyis mngon du @184a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-1: phyogs par gtor na phyir bsdu ba byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-2: thal ba des rab tu bdugs te dur khrod kyi nang du zhugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-4: 'khor dang bcas pa mdun na nye bar gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-8: sha za thams cad mdun na nye bar gnas shing dbang du gyur nas gnas te bdag dang nor gyis bgyi ba ci mchis zhes bya ba byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-9: rang la byugs te tshogs kyi nang ngam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-10: dge 'dun gyi nang du zhugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-11: ston pa mthong ba ji lta ba de ltar rig sngags 'chang snang zhing mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-14: don dang mchod pa chen po 'thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-15: thal bas lus bskus te klu'i mtshor zhugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-16: klu'i rgyal po stong phrag drug cu rtsa brgyad thams cad dbang du gyur nas gnas te bka' bzhin byed par 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-17: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du nye bar gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-18: rang la byugs te rgyal po'i pho brang du zhugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-19: rgyal po'i btsun mo dang 'khor du bcas pa rnams dbang du 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-20: ci bgyi zhes bya ba byed cing mdun na nye bar gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-21: 'jig rten gyi bla ma ji lta ba de bzhin du mchod pa chen po 'byung bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184a-22: don chen po dang mchod pa chen po 'thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-0: ji srid @184b 'tsho'i bar du nye bar gnas par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-1: ston pa 'dren pa ji lta ba bzhin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-2: gang dang gang la thal bas reg pa tsam gyis de dang de'i nad thams cad bral bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-3: sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad rnam par dag par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-4: ngan 'gro'i sgo thams cad bcad par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-5: mchog tu bde ba dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-6: shi 'phos nas bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-11: rlom sems dang nga rgyal dang ldan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-16: nga rgyal can de dag gis gang du yang dngos grub yang dag par rjes su mi mthong ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-17: de dag yun ring por thar pa mi rnyed pas dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-19: gang yang rig sngags kyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyis smad pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-20: skye ba rgyud la dngos grub bsregs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-21: 'jig rten 'di dang pha rol chud gson pa dag ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-24: 'dir bdag gis cung zad kyang ma nongs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:184b-25: sdug bsngal mang po dang chen po'i sems can dgrol bar rngo mi thogs lags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-0: sangs rgyas thugs rje chen pos bka' stsal pa'i yid la bgyi bskal pa bgrangs par yid la @185a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-1: bgyis pas dgrol bar rngo mi thogs lags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-3: sdug bsngal mang po brgyud par nyams su myong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-6: byams pa dang gsang sngags kyi go cha bgos pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-7: byams pa'i ral gri thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-8: sems can thams cad la phan zhing mnyes gshin pa la de kho na nyid sgrub pa'i dngos grub 'di dag 'jig rten 'dren pas rjes su gnang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-9: mgon po 'di mthong ba tsam gyis spos kyi gzugs kyi 'jig rten mgon po mthong ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-10: 'jig rten 'dren pa rang gi gzugs su mngon sum du mthong ba mtshungs pa nyid du khong du chud par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-11: sangs rgyas bye ba gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma dang mnyam par mngon sum du mthong ba kho na dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-12: 'jig rten gyi mgon po mthong ba mtshungs pa kho nar khong du chud par bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-14: de nas phyir mi ldog pa'i gnas rig sngags 'chang gi 'khor los bsgyur ba chen po sgrub par 'dod pa'i dge slong ngam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185a-20: gzhan gang yang rung ba'i rig sngags 'chang gi phyir mi ldog pa'i gnas thob par 'dod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-0: dus gsum du gshegs @185b pa'i sangs rgyas mthong bar 'dod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-1: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi gnas mthong bar 'dod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-2: rig sngags 'chang gi dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad mthong bar 'dod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-3: 'phags pa rdo rje 'dzin mthong bar 'dod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-4: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs thams cad kyi spyi'i dam tshig mthong bar 'dod pa na cho ga 'di bsgrub par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-6: bya ba dang bcas pa des myur ba dang /
