K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-8: mgyogs par 'jig rten thams cad kyi mngon sum du cho 'phrul rmad du byung bar gsang ba ston par mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-10: nem nur bskyed par mi bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-12: yid gnyis bskyed par mi bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-13: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gser gyi mdog can sor bzhi'i chad tsam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-15: ral pa'i thor tshugs kyis brgyan pa bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-16: shin tu tshad dang ldan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-18: cha shin tu rnam par mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-21: 'od dpag med pa'i dbu rgyan can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-22: g-yas na zla ba tshes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-24: ril ba spyi blugs bsnams pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-25: phyag g-yas mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:185b-27: gla rtsi dang ring srel gyis bkang pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-0: g-yas na lha mo sgrol ma @186a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-1: dngul las byas pa thal mo sbyar te yid tsam 'dud pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-2: gser gyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-3: g-yon na dngul las dkar mo thal mo sbyar te yid tsam 'dud pa padma'i gdan la bzhugs par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-4: steng gi g-yas phyogs na 'od dpag med skyil mo krung bcas te bzhugs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-5: g-yon na sh'akya'i rgyal po skyil mo krung bcas te bzhugs pa dgod par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-6: 'od 'dom gang dang bcas pas legs par brgyan par bya zhing gnad dang gnad shin tu rnam par 'byes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-21: phyag gi sor mo mnyam zhing thams cad du mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-22: sku chu zhens gab cing mthon dman ran pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-23: mchod phyir thogs pa dkar po 'chang bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-24: las shin tu yongs su rdzogs shing shin tu mthar phyin pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186a-25: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi gzugs zin par rig nas rig sngags 'chang gis rgyu skar bzang po'i zla ba nya ba'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-0: rgyu skar bkra shis pa rgyal gyi nyi ma dang mthun pa rnyed nas dkyil @186b 'khor bsgrub par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-1: dkyil 'khor shin tu mdzes par bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-2: gru bzhi la cha legs par phyed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-3: ko la'i tshad tsam la them skas bzhis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-4: khru gsum par rnam par dbye bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-11: dbyibs legs pa la tshon rtsi sna tshogs kyis rnam par dbye zhing dkyil 'khor dam pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-12: thig gdab pa shin tu rnam par mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-13: sgo bzhi pa la dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi snying por padma'i rigs kyi dkyil 'khor don yod pa'i zhags pa'i dkyil 'khor bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-14: phyi rol gyi dkyil 'khor gyi gnas su cha rnam pa brgyad du phye la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-15: lho'i gra'i gnas su de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs sna tshogs kyis bri'o; ;de nas phyang gi grar bri ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-16: rdo rje'i rigs kyi dkyil 'khor tshon rtsi sna tshogs kyis rnam par bkra bar bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-17: de nas nub kyi grar bri ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-18: nor bu'i rigs kyi dkyil 'khor sna tshogs kyis rnam par bkra bar bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-19: de nas shar gyi grar glang po che'i rigs kyi dkyil 'khor tshon rtsi sna tshogs kyis rtag tu shin tu mdzes pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:186b-21: shar phyogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi sgor ri bo po ta la me tog dang shing ljon pa sna tshogs kyis legs par brgyan pa ri'i lha dang bcas pa bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-1: kyi sgor ri rab klu'i rgyal po dga' bo dang nye dga' bos kun nas dkris pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-2: sum cu gsum pa'i ris kyi lha bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-4: spos kyi ngad ldang dri za'i tshogs kyis gang ba shing ljon pa sna tshogs kyis shin tu mdzes pa bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-5: nub phyogs kyi sgor ri ti se lha rnams kyi gnas me tog sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-7: shing ljon pa sna tshogs mchog gis rtag tu gang ba bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-8: legs par zin nas kun tu ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-9: mdung rtse gsum pa'i bar phreng ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-10: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-11: rdo rje'i rigs nyid gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-12: nor bu'i rigs su de bzhin gshegs pa gzhag cing de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-13: thams cad rdo rje 'dzin pa bzhag na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-16: ri bo po ta la la gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-22: spos kyi ngad ldang la gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-23: shar phyogs kyi sgor pho nya mo bdun gyis yongs su bskor ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-25: srin mo ral pa gcig ma srin mo bdun gyis yongs su bskor ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187a-26: nub phyogs kyi sgor rdo rje lu gu rgyud lu gu rgyud bdun gyis yongs su bskor ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-0: byang phyogs kyi @187b sgor khro gnyer can mo khro gnyer can bdun gyis yongs su bskor ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-1: de nas 'jigs pa med pas mgon po 'jig rten gyi bla ma'i gzugs gser gyi mdog can ring bsrel dang ldan pa don yod pa'i rgyal po rnam par 'phrul pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi snying po padma rgya chen po'i dkyil 'khor du gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-2: grar rgyal po chen po bzhi stobs po che go cha bgos pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-4: mtshon cha 'bar ba thogs pa gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-5: gang zhig thub pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi sprul pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-6: spyi'i rigs yang dag par 'byung ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-7: don yod pa'i rgyal po rnam par 'phrul pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-8: 'jig rten dbang phyug mchog sbyin pa dang bcas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-9: don yod pa'i zhags pa rnam par 'phrul pa bsgrub pa'i ched du cho ga sna tshogs dran pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-10: sems can kun la phan pa'i phyir //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-11: rnam thar dkyil 'khor de nyid ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-12: legs par sgrub pa mthong tsam dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-13: bklags pas dngos grub bla med 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-14: de bas rtag tu 'bad pa yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-15: sgrub par byed pa ni mkhas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-16: de nas rig sngags 'chang gtsang mar gyur pa shin tu khrus byas pa gos gtsang ma bgos pas dar dang ba dan sna tshogs bzang pos dkyil 'khor brgyan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:187b-17: ro bro ba'i mchog rgya chen pos snod sna tshogs legs par bkang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-1: gyi snod du mchod yon 'bul zhing ro sna tshogs kyi gtor ma gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-2: de bzhin du 'bras bu sna tshogs gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-3: gzugs rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i kha zas kyi gtor ma yang bsgrub bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-4: me tog sna tshogs bkram zhing gtor ma sna tshogs kyis bkang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-9: dbyib mo dag kyang dgang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-10: kun tu dri chus bsgos pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-11: rgya chen gtor ma kun tu'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-12: sna tshogs pa yi pog phor nas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-13: sna tshogs bdug spos dbul ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-23: sa ra dza ra sa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-24: de bzhin du ga pur dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-27: sha kha ra'i bdug spos 'di dag ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-29: thams cad du sgrub pa bla na med pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-30: sna tshogs pa yi dri dag dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-31: phye ma byug pa sna tshogs nyid //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-32: shes rab can gyis kun tu ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-33: dkyil 'khor dag la gzhag par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-34: lha rdzas kyi rin po che sna bdun gyi me tog dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-37: byi ru dang ni mu tig dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-38: aindra n'i la dag dang ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188a-39: padma r'a ga dag kyang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-0: gser dang dngul gyi bum pa rin @188b po che sna bdun can yang gra bzhir gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-2: yungs kar dang bsres pas dkyil 'khor du kun tu gtor ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-3: kun nas me tog phreng ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-4: rmad byung dkyil 'khor la gzhag cing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-5: kun nas mar me'i phreng ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-6: dkyil 'khor rmad du byung la gzhag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-7: rig sngags 'chang nyin zhag gcig gnas par gyur pas yang bzlas brjod rgya cher byas la cho gas srung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-9: kun nas dkyil 'khor bcing ba byas la dkyil 'khor gyi las bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-10: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-15: blon po chen po la dam tshig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-18: mgon po 'jig rten gyi bla ma mthong zhing dkyil 'khor rmad du byung ba mthong nas phyag bya zhing mchod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-20: bdug spos dbul bar byas la bskor ba bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:188b-21: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis thams cad la byams pa'i sems mnyam par bzhag ste skyil mo krung bcas nas 'dug la mi smra bar ya mtshan du snang bar mthong gi bar don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po bzlas brjod byas la dkyil 'khor kun tu khro bo'i rgyal pos lan brgya rtsa brgyad dbang bskur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-0: chu dang me tog gis dkyil 'khor kun tu lan brgya rtsa @189a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-1: brgyad gtor ba'i mod la rtag tu phyag rgya lan brgya rtsa brgyad bcings la dkyil 'khor du me tog dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-3: dri phul nas mgon po 'jig rten dbang phyug don yod pa'i zhags pa mthong na don yod pa nyid mchod par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-4: de nas mgon po phyag na rdo rje dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-5: rig sngags kyi rgyal po bla na med pa mchod pa byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-6: de nas lha mo sgrol ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-7: kun tu lha mo thams cad la'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-8: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad la'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-9: de nas ri'i rgyal po rnams la gnas pa'i ri'i lha thams cad la'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-10: thams cad dang sgo bsrungs la rtag tu mchod pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-11: de nas phyogs bzhi kun tu rig sngags 'chang gis rtag tu mchod nas skyil mo krung bcas te 'dug la 'jigs pa med pas lag pa'i phyag rgya bcing bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-12: byams pa'i sems dang snying rje'i lhag pa'i bsam pa nyid kyis don yod pa'i zhags pa rtag tu dran par bya zhing sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa bsgom mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189a-13: gsang sngags brjod ma thag tu dkyil 'khor dang sa gzhi g-yo zhing gang dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i mod la snying dga' ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-0: 'od zer bye ba kha dog sna tshogs rnam par bkram pa 'byung zhing dkyil 'khor gyi snying po na don yod pa'i zhags pa 'gul @189b bar 'gyur dkyil 'khor gyi snying po 'bar bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-2: de bzhin du phyag na rdo rje 'bar bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-3: dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i lha dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-5: lha g-yo bar 'gyur zhing dkyil 'khor kun nas legs so zhes sgra grags par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-6: de nas ji ltar gser bkod pa de ltar dbus kyi dkyil 'khor gyi snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-7: mgon po de bzhin gshegs pa sh'akya thub pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-8: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-11: dkar mo gser gyi mdog gis bkod pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor kyi nang nas bzhengs par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-12: sku gser mdog can gzugs bzang pos bdag nyid kyis rang gi ngo bo ston pa snang bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-13: phyogs bcu kun tu rtag tu gzigs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-14: thams cad du rtag tu sems brtan por bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-15: rig sngags 'chang byams pa dang bcas pa'i sems brtan por gyur pas me tog dang rol mo'i sgra dbul zhing don yod pa'i rgyal po yang dran par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-16: de nas de bzhin gshegs pas phyag gser gyi mdog can brkyangs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:189b-17: rig sngags 'chang gi spyi bor bzhag nas lags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-0: zhes bya ba sbyin par mdzad cing rig sngags 'chang khyod kyis don yod pa'i zhags @190a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-2: cho ga zhib mo mtha' dag dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-4: phyag rgya rim par phye ba grub ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-5: skyes bu dam pa khyod bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su lung bstan gyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-6: rang gi ngo bo nyid kyis yongs su dag nas bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas kyi bar du skyes bu dam pa khyod rang gi ngo bo phyir mi ldog pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-7: don yod pa'i rig sngags 'chang gis 'khor lo bsgyur bar 'gyur bar byos shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-8: dkyil 'khor 'di la brten ba'i skye bo dge ba dang lhag pa'i bsam pa la zhugs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-9: sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i mya ngan las 'das par lung bstan gyi bar du phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:190a-10: ci ste sems can ngan pa rig sngags kyi gdol pa smad pa dag der zhugs na /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212a-15: gsang sngags 'dis gzir bas thams cad du mngon du gnas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212a-16: de bzhin gshegs pa sh'akya thub pas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la legs so zhes bya ba byin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212a-17: sems can dag pa chen po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212a-18: khyod kyis spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po rig sngags kyi rgyal po don yod pa'i lcags kyu smras pa legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212a-19: rig sngags 'chang thams cad kyi don dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212a-20: sems can thams cad kyi don chen po'i phyir sems can dag pa chen po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-0: @212b khyod kyis de'i dus la bab par shes na da smros shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-1: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis bcom ldan 'das kyis bskul bar rig nas bzhin 'dzum zhing mig mi 'dzum par bcom ldan 'das ga la ba de logs su mngon du phyogs te bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'khor mang po'i nang du 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po'i lcags kyu don yod pa'i zhags pa 'di smras so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-2: dus gsum du gshegs shing so so na bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-3: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-4: 'phags pa rdo rje 'dzin rig sngags kyi dbang po chen po 'khor gyi tshogs dang bcas pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-5: dkyil 'khor gyi rig sngags kyi lha thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-7: gsang sngags rim par phye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-8: cho ga zhib mo thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-10: 'phags pa nyan thos kyi dge 'dun 'das pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-12: da ltar byung ba thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:212b-13: 'phags pa byams pa la sogs pa dga' ldan gyi byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'khor gyi tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-0: 'phags ba de bzhin gshegs pa 'od dpag med bde ba can na gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs @213a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-2: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i 'jig rten gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-4: phyag rgya rim par phye ba cho ga zhib mo dang bcas pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-5: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-6: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po snying rje chen po dang ldan pa 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug rig sngags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-7: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi sku sems can thams cad la byams pa kun nas don yod pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi rig sngags kyi rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-11: bdud la sogs pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar mdzad pa'i sems dpa' chen po mchog sbyin lcags kyu la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-15: mah'a aa mo gha aam ku shi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-22: bhu dza bar da bhu dza aam ku sha p'a sha dha ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-26: pa ta la dha ra aam ku sha /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-30: be sha dha ra aa mo gha r'u pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-32: ta ra ta ra; ta ta ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-36: aa mo gha aam ku sha ba ra da /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213a-37: ma h'a k'a ru ni ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-0: pa ra ma @213b k'a ru ni ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-2: shva ra ya ma ba ru na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-6: ma h'a ka sha ma ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-15: ma h'a aam ku sha aa ksha dha ra h'um h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-17: sam bha ra sam bha ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-18: sa manta munda manda lam p'u ra ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-20: hri da ya aam ku shi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-22: man s'a dha ya siddhi ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-23: a'a karsha ya munda manta manda la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-25: bighni na pra s'a dha ya m'a ram/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-27: sarba pra ba ki la bi sha ma la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-30: ma h'a aa ku shi h'um h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-32: bo dha ya bo dha ya; tu ru tu ru /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-33: ma h'a bo dhi satva aam ku sha ratna p'a sha dha ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-35: a'a bha ra na bi bhu shi ta /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-37: dzi na ma ku ta dha ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-39: padma p'a sha aam ku sha dha ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-40: sarba bidya mantra munda manda la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-41: pra ba ra s'a dha ya s'a dha ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-42: bi shva r'u pa dha ra /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-45: so so ma mu kha ba ra ma h'a k'a ru ni ka satva bat sa la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-46: sarba mantra munda pra sa dha ka /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-47: padma ba ra da sa d'a na mostu te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-50: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis 'do smras ma thag tu ri bo po ta la chen po brag dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-52: skyed mos tshal du bcas ba'i gnas kyi gzhal med khang rnam pa drug tu rab tu g-yos te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:213b-53: lha rdzas kyi me tog gi char chen po bkra bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-0: @214a *// don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis phyag byas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-1: rnam par thar pa'i dkyil 'khor phyag rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-2: gsang sngags dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor rim par phye ba'i cho ga zhib mo 'di yang so so le'ur phye ba mtha' dag rdzogs par nam mkha' la gnas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-3: gang gsang sngags kyi yig 'bru yang gser la bee d'u ryas yi ger bris pa sprin gyi rim pa na snang ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-4: yi ge'i phreng ba mnyam zhing gsal la zur phyin par bris pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-5: thig gi phreng ba gshibs pas brgyan pa snang ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-6: gang lag pa'i phyag rgya yang padma'i nang nas byung ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-7: phyag rgya bcing ba sna tshogs 'od zer 'bar ba nam mkha' la gnas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-8: gang mtshan ma'i phyag rgya yang rin po che sna bdun gyi padma la rab tu gnas pa'i nam mkha' la gnas par gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-9: gang ras kyi ri mo'i sku gzugs gzugs rnam pa sna tshogs 'dzin pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-12: yo byad dang bcas pa rim par phye ba bris pa yang nam mkha' la gnas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-13: gang dkyil 'khor rim par phye ba de dkyil 'khor rnam pa sna tshogs gru bzhi pa gra bzhi cha mnyam pa rnam par phye ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-14: dkyil 'khor shin tu spras shing brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214a-15: gzugs rnam pa sna tshogs kyis mdzes pa'i gzhal med khang yang nam mkha' la gnas pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-0: dkyil @214b 'khor chen po na gnas pa'i rig sngags kyi lha pho nya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-1: khro bo dang bcas pa gzhal med khang na rjes su rgyu ba dag kyang nam mkha'i dkyil na gnas te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-2: bcom ldan 'das la mchod pa byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-3: phyogs so so'i de bzhin gshegs pa mang po bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong gang+ga'i klung gi bye ma snyed kyang phyogs bcu kun gyi nam mkha'i dkyil na de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku bzhugs par gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-4: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku de dag thams cad kyis kyang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la legs so zhes bya ba byin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-7: rig sngags kyi mchog dam pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-8: don yod pa'i lcags kyu'i rig sngags kyi rgyal po mtha' dag rdzogs par smras pa gang gis don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po rnam par thar pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga zhib mo'i gsang sngags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-10: gsang sngags rim par phye ba de dag thams cad don yod pa'i lcags kyu'i gsang sngags kyi zhags pas kun nas drangs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:214b-11: 'khor 'di'i nang na nam mkha'i dkyil na rab tu gnas pa de phyi ma'i tshe phyi ma'i dus na rigs kyi bu'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-2: gzhan su yang rung ba bud med dam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-5: bu mo rig sngags 'dzin pa thams cad kyis don yod pa'i zhags pa'i lcags kyu 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po'i gzungs 'di dran par byed na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-6: lan gcig dran pa tsam gyis kyang mdo la don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis phyag byas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-7: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-8: rnam par thar pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyag rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-10: dkyil 'khor rim par phye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-11: cho ga zhib mo de thams cad so sor de la kha ton nyid du gnas te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-12: de dag thams cad rim gyis dran pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-13: blo rgya mtsho bsags pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-17: gsang sngags rim par phye ba so so la blo 'jug par 'gyur ro; ;nam yang blo dman par mi 'gyur zhing nam yang brjed ngas bar mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215a-18: de nas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa sh'akya thub pas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la legs so zhes bya ba byin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215b-0: mchog tu snying rje can khyod kyis cho ga rgya chen po @215b sa pa legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215b-1: de nas gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po phyag na rdo rjes rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam par 'phrul pa'i cho 'phrul gyi yon tan mtha' yas pa 'di mthong nas dbugs char 'byin par gyur cing mchog tu dga' ba thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215b-2: de nas byang chub sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'khor 'di'i nang du 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po don yod pa'i lcags kyu'i bya ba'i yo byad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215b-5: de nas rig sngags 'chang gang 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po don yod pa'i zhags pa byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis phyag bgyis pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215b-6: rnam par thar ba'i dkyil 'khor 'di sgrub par 'tshal ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215b-18: gzhan su yang rung ba bdu med dam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215b-22: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po 'di bklag par 'tshal ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:215b-24: bzlas brjod kyi cho ga bgyi bar 'tshal ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-1: sgrub par 'tshal ba des sngon rol tu phyogs bcur thal mo sbyar te phyag 'tshal nas shar phyogs su kha bltas te mchis la gzhan mi smra bar don yod pa'i lcags kyu'i snying po 'di lan gsum dran par bgyi zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-2: yang thal mo sbyar te phyag bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-3: des na dran pa tsam gyi mdo la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug bkug par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-4: ri bo po ta la'i gzhal med khang dang bcas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-13: lto 'phye chen po dang bcas pa bkug par 'gyur ro ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-14: 'phags ba don yod pa'i zhags pa'i cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-15: bam po nyi shu gnyis pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-16: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis phyag bgyis pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-17: rnam par thar pa'i dkyil 'khor phyag rgya dang bcas pa gsang sngags rim par phye ba'i cho ga zhib mo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-18: sgrub pa'i cho ga'i rnam pa rgya chen po mtha' dag rdzogs pa 'di yang bkug par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216a-19: dkyil 'khor gnas pa'i rig sngags kyi lha 'khor dang bcas pa bkug par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-0: thams cad yid rab tu dga' bar gyur pas dngos grub dam @216b pa rjes su stsol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-1: de nas don yod pa'i rgyal po'i snying po dran par bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-2: ji ltar shin tu rgya cher yid la bgyis pa de ltar sgrub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-3: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug nyid kyi kha nas dran pa mnyan zhing rgya che ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-4: blo dang mdangs dri ma ma mchis pa 'jug par bgyid de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-5: zhugs pa tsam gyi mod la lce padma'i 'dab ma lta bur 'jam par 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-6: kha nas autpa la'i dri 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-7: dbyangs snyan cing mnyen pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-10: tshig rnam par dag par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-14: dga' bar byed pa'i dbyangs su 'gyur zhing ka la pinga ka'i dbyangs su 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-15: ci ste dus gsum du dran par bgyid na; gsang sngags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-18: phyag rgya rim par phye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-20: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs spyi'i dngos grub de rdzogs par 'gyur zhing spyod par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-23: bdud la sogs pa sdang ba'i 'jigs pa thams cad dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-25: dmyal bar mchi ba'i sdig pa thams cad dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:216b-26: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-0: rig sngags kyi rgyal po chen @217a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-1: po don yod pa'i lcags kyu 'di lan gsum dran par bgyis pa tsam gyis skad cig de nyid kyi mod la bdag rang dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-5: 'khor dang bcas pa mi gtsang ba yang gtsang bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-6: yongs su ma dag pa yang shin tu yongs su dag par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-7: dri ma dang bcas pa yang shin tu dri ma ma mchis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-8: zhe sdang dang bcas pa yang zhe sdang dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-9: gti mug dang bcas pa yang gti mug dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-10: 'dod chags dang bcas pa yang 'dod chags dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-11: sgrib pa dang bcas pa yang sgrib pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-13: bdud dang log 'dren gyis yongs su zin pa yang bgegs dang log 'dren dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-14: bdud la sogs pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-15: sems kyi sdig pa yang sdig pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-16: thun mong ma yin pa yang thun mong du gyur cing srung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-17: mi smra ba'i brtul zhugs ma mchis pa yang mi smra ba'i brtul zhugs chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217a-18: smyung ba ma bgyis pa yang smyung ba bgyis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-0: rig sngags kyi gnas dang yul dang dkyil 'khor thams cad du tshangs par mi spyod pa yang @217b tshangs par spyod pa chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-1: tshangs pa'i gnas chen po la gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-2: dge pa mi sbyod pa yang dge ba chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-3: chos mi spyod pa yang chos spyod pa chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-4: bsod nams mi bgyid pa yang bsod nams kyi phung ba 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-5: dul ba'i spyod pa ma mchis pa yang dul ba'i spyod pa chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-8: gsang sngags mi mthong ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-9: dam tshig ma mchis pa yang dkyil 'khor dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-14: 'khor thams cad du sangs rgyas dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-15: chos mthong bar mi 'tshal ba yang byang chub dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-17: dam tshig dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-18: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis ma bsam pa yang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis bsam par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-19: sangs rgyas kyi sa bon gyi yul du ma gyur pa yang byang chub kyi sa bon dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-20: pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi spyod pa dang mi 'bral zhing pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs par bgyi ba la mkhas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:217b-21: tshul khrims dang mi 'bral zhing ting nge 'dzin rab tu 'thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-0: sbyin pa dang yongs su gtong ba dang mi 'bral zhing @218a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-3: sbyin pa'i tshogs chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-4: bzod pa dang mi 'bral zhing bzod pa chen po'i bzod pa'i rjes su spyod par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-5: brtson 'grus dang mi 'bral zhing brtson 'grus kyi stobs chen po'i go cha brtan pa bgos par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-6: bsam gtan dang mi 'bral zhing bsam gan chen po 'thob ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-7: ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-8: shes rab dang thabs la mkhas pa rgya chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-10: gsang sngags nyams pa yang gsang sngags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-11: phyag rgya yongs su tshang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-12: cho ga la mkhas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-13: dge pa'i bshes gnyen dang bral ba yang dge ba'i bshes gnyen chen po'i lam la rab tu gnas par 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-14: 'jigs rten thams cad du snying du sdug pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-16: sems can thams cad kyis mchod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-17: mngon du phyag bgyi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-19: bsam pa yongs su dag par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-20: de ltar don yod pa chen po'i cho ga rgya chen po 'di dag ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-21: thams cad du dngos grub don yod pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-22: mchog tu rnyed par dkar ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218a-23: dge ba don yod pa 'di don yod pa'i lcags kyus 'dren par bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-0: @218b dngos grub thams cad 'gugs par bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-1: sgrub pa thams cad 'dren par bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-2: sangs rgyas kyi chos ji snyed pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-3: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-5: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-9: stong pa nyid 'dren par bgyid de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-10: don yod pa'i lcags kyu 'dis 'dren par bgyid /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-12: dngos grub mchog 'dren par bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-13: de ltar mthu che ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-15: yon tan chen por brjod pas bsod nams kyi 'bras bu chen po stsol bar byid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-16: de ltar dge ba'i rtsa ba chen po dang ldan zhing kun tu gsog par bgyid pas rig sngags kyi rgyal po don yod pa'i lags kyu /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-17: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-18: mchog tu grub pa bla na med pa lags so; ;de nas rig sngags 'chang rigs kyi bu'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:218b-28: gzhan su mang rung ba bud med dam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-0: bu mo 'phags ba spyan ras gzigs @219a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-1: dbang phyug rang gi gzugs kyis dgug par 'tshal ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-2: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug bdag nyid kyi rang gi gzugs su mthong bar 'tshal na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-4: gtsang ma shin tu khrus bgyis pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-6: ba'i rnam lnga'i chus bsang ba'i mchod phyir thogs btags pas ras dmar po'i skud pa'i mchod phyir thogs kha dog bzang po gnas bdun du yongs su gzung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-9: gnas gsum pa dpung pa gnyis su bcing pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-10: lag ngar gnyis su bcing ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-11: de nas rked par bcings pa sa phyogs gtsang mar 'dug nas sam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-12: gnas gzhan gang yang rung ba dben zhing 'khrugs pa ma mchis pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-13: dkyil 'khor gyi stegs gru bzhi pa shin tu rnam par mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-14: gru bzhi'i tshad tsam la 'phang sor brgyad kyi tshad tsam kun nas zlum po legs par byugs pa shin tu 'jam par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-15: de nas tshon sna tshogs kyi skud bas rnam par mdzes par thig gdab cing tshon rtsi sna tshogs kyis bri bar bgyi'o; ;snying po'i dkyil 'khor ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-16: khru gang tsam gyi tshad la gru bzhi pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219a-19: gru bzhi kun kha khyer gyi rnam pa can bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-2: 'dab ma thams cad la lcags kyu bri zhing dbus kyi snying po ge sar dang bcas pa rin po che sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-3: 'od kyi phreng ba zlum po tshon rtsi sna tshogs kyis rnam par mdzes par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-4: snying po'i dkyil 'khor gyi gra bzhir lcags kyu dang zhags pa kun nas zlum po yang bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-5: phyi rol gyi dkyil 'khor kun tu mtshan ma'i phyag rgya sna tshogs kyang bri bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-6: dkyil 'khor gyi gra bzhir rnam par phye bar rgyal po chen po bzhi 'bar ba'i nang na go cha bgos pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-7: drag shul gyi gzugs can 'jigs par bgyid pa bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-8: sgo bzhi rnam par phye bar yang dkyil 'khor gyi lha bri bar bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-9: shar phyogs kyi sgor rdo rje 'chang zhi ba'i gzugs can bzhin 'dzum pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-10: rdo rje 'gying bag can du 'dzin pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-11: ri rab kyi steng na 'bar ba'i nang na mchis pa bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-12: lho phyogs kyi sgor khro bo'i rgyal po drag shul gyi gzugs can 'jigs par bgyid pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-13: padma dang zhags pa thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-14: me tog kha phye ba'i steng na 'bar ba'i nang na mchis pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-15: nub phyogs kyi sgor dbang po rdo rje thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-16: mig gsum pa ri'i steng na 'bar ba'i nang na mchis pa bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-17: byang phyogs kyi sgor don yod pa'i zhags pa gdong khro gnyer can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:219b-18: padma dang zhags pa thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-1: nang na lcags kyu dang lhan cig mchis pa bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-2: dkyil 'khor khor khor yug tu gos dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-5: rgyal mtshan kun gyis brgyar par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-6: tshon sna lnga'i skud pas khor khor yug tu dkri bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-7: gtor ma thams cad dkar po gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-8: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol kun tu dngul dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-9: gser gyi snod rnam pa sna tshogs pa gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-10: snying po'i dkyil 'khor khor khor yug tu dngul gyi snod bkang ba bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-13: zhabs bsil ba'i snod bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-15: dris bkang ba'i snod bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-16: dngul gyi phog phor aa ga ru dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-18: du ru ka'i bdug spos bsregs pa bzhi gzhag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-19: phyi rol gyi dkyil 'khor kho ra khor yug tu sa las byas pa'i snod bkang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-20: gtor ma'i snod bum pa yongs su bkang ba drug cu rtsa bzhi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-21: bdug pa sna tshogs bsregs pa'i pog phor brgyad 'jigs pa med par gzhag par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220a-22: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis tshes bcu bzhi nas zla ba nya ches bco lnga'i bar gyi nyin zhag gcig smyung ba bgyis pas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-0: yungs kar la don yod pa'i rgyal po'i snying pos lan brgya rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas pas @220b dkyil 'khor du gtor bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-2: dri chab la khro bo'i rgyal pos lan brgya rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas pas dkyil 'khor kun tu gtor zhing dkyil 'khor dbang bskur bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-3: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol du mar me drug cu rtsa bzhi sbar bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-4: me tog ji snyed pa mang po bkram zhing kho ra khor yug tu phreng ba gzhag par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-5: rig sngags 'chang gis don yod pa'i lcags kyus yungs kar la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig yongs su bzlas pas dkyil 'khor kun dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-9: dkyil 'khor bcing ba bgyis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-12: bdag srung ba bgyis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-18: bdud la sogs pa thams cad bcings par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-26: lto 'phye chen po gang dag mthong ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-27: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bslab pa'i gzhi 'dzin pa de thams cad bkug par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-28: dkyil 'khor kun nas bsrung ba'i slad du gshin rje dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:220b-32: rgyal po chen po bzhi dpung dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-3: dkyil 'khor kun nas srung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-6: 'og gi sa'i lha mo sa'i 'og na gnas pa rnams dang lhan cig dkyil 'khor bsrung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-8: sba ba'i slad du mchis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-9: steng nas nam mkha' la tshangs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-15: zla ba rgyu skar bcas par bsrung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-18: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis phyag bgyi ba'i las bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-19: rig sngags 'chang gis rtsva ku sha'i steng du shar phyogs kyi sgor dkyil 'khor la mngon du phyogs par skyil mo krung bcas te mchis la gzhan mi smra bar don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po lan brgya rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas pa bgyis la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-20: dkyil 'khor gyi snying por 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug bzhag par bgyi zhing me tog re re la bzlas brjod bgyis pas 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi mdun du dor bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221a-21: de nas khro bo'i rgyal pos yungs kar gyi 'bru re re la lan brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas brjod bgyis pas gtor bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-0: de nas 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs @221b dbang phyug gi snying po don yod pa'i zhags pa'i lcags kyus bzlas brjod stong rtsa brgyad bgyis pas dbul bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-1: ril bu re re la bzlas brjod bgyis pa'i bdug spos dbul bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-2: yungs kar re re la bzlas brjod bgyis la snying po'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du dor bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-3: stong rtsa brgyad rdzogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-4: thun tha ma'i nam nangs kar gya nom pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-5: yid du 'ong zhing dga' ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-6: rab tu dga' bar bgyid par sa g-yo bar 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-9: yid du 'ong ba zab mo zab mo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-11: mi'am ci'i sgra dbyangs lta bu 'byung bar 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-12: rig sngags 'chang gi sems brtan por bgyi zhing mchog tu dga' bar yid la bgyid pas bzlas brjod bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-13: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi snying po nas 'od zer rnam pa sna tshogs mang po 'byung zhing phyogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-14: phyogs mtshams kun tu mchi zhing snang bar 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-15: nam mkha'i dkyil na sprin brtsegs pa'i phung po bzhin du 'od zer gyi gdugs su gyur nas gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-16: de nas sngon ma byung ba'i dri zhim po rmad du byung ba 'byung bar 'gyur zhing lha'i tsandan dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:221b-18: tsandan sbrul gyi snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-0: dpag tshad brgya khor khor yug tu dri gnas par @222a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-2: lha rdzas kyi bdug spos kyi dri zhim po sngon ma byung ba rmad du byung ba bee d'urya sngon po'i sprin brtsegs pa lta bu'i bdug spos kyi sprin nam mkha'i dkyil na gnas par yang 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-3: phyogs bcu kun tu bdug spos kyi dri rgyas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-4: de nas snying po'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus nas 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug bdag nyid kyi rang gi gzugs kyis 'byung bar 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-5: tshangs pa bzang po'i cha lugs can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-6: ral pa'i thor tshugs kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-7: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i gzugs su lag pa bzhi pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-8: padma dang zhags pa thogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-9: rgyal ba 'od dpag tu med pa'i dbu rgyan can /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-10: dbu rgyan zla ba tshes pas brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-11: mdung rtse gsum pa thogs shing dbugs 'byin pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-12: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-13: mtshan dang dpe byad bzang pos brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-14: rang gi 'od dang gzi brjid kyis shin tu 'bar ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-15: bzhin 'dzum zhing nyi ma stong bas lhag pa'i 'od zer gyi snang ba dang ldan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-16: khru brgyad tsam gyis lus bzang pos dkyil 'khor gyi snying po'i padma'i stan las langs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222a-17: nam mkha' la mchis nas zhi ba'i gzugs can byams pa'i sems dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-0: snying rje chen po yid la bgyis pas dkyil 'khor kun tu lta zhing phyogs bcur rtog par bgyid @222b [?]; ;de nas rig sngags 'chang la legs so zhes bya ba'i sgra 'byung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-1: rig sngags 'chang chen po legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-2: lag pa g-yas pa brkyang ba'i lag mthil shin tu bzang po 'od zer bye ba brgya stong phrag stong gis legs par brgyan pa'i lag pa rig sngags 'chang gi spyi bor 'jog par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-3: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis lag pa spyi bor bzhag ma thag tu de nas rig sngags 'chang de nam mkha' la mchis te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-4: don yod pa'i zhags pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-5: lcags kyu rgya chen po 'od zer snang ba bkod pa rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya ba sgyu ma lta bu'i shugs kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin 'thob ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-6: ting nge 'dzin gzhan yang bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong gi bye ma snyed 'thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-7: kun tu don yod par lta ba nor bu'i snying po rgya chen por grags pa don yod pa'i lcags kyu'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-8: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi snying po'i gzungs 'thob par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-9: gang gis gzungs thob pa'i mod la don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po'i phyag rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-10: gsang sngags rim par phye ba'i cho ga zhib mo byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis phyag bgyis pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:222b-11: rnam par thar pa'i dkyil 'khor mtha' dag rdzogs par kha ton nyid du gnas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:223a-0: gzhan yang padma rgya chen po'i dkyil @223a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:223a-3: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:223a-6: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs kyi dam tshig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:223a-7: gsang ba chen po'i snying po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:223a-8: phyag rgya dang bcas pa'i gsang sngags rim par phye ba gsang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:223a-9: cho ga zhib mo'i rnam pa thams cad kha ton nyid du gnas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:223a-10: rig sngags 'chang gi 'khor los bsgyur ba bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma dgu bcu rtsa gnyis pa rnams kyi gtso bo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:223a-12: rig sngags 'chang gi 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal por 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224a-13: bu rnyed pa de thams cad smra bar 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224a-15: rgyal rigs su skye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224a-16: khyim bdag gi rigs shing s'a la chen po lta bur skye ba de thams cad smra bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224a-17: gzhan yang rigs mthon po dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224a-22: gzhan yang 'phags pa sbyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis 'jig rten pa'i mchog sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224a-24: grub pa de thams cad de la stsol bar bgyid de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224a-25: 'di lta ste nor bsgyur ba smra ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224a-27: mig sman gyi dngos grub dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-8: nad zhi bar bya ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-11: yul gyi bdag po nyid dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-12: chu klung chen po rgal ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-14: gsang sngags sna tshogs sgrub pa'i dngos grub pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-15: 'jigs pa chen po brgyad zhi bar bya ba dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-18: gzhan yang ji ltar yid la bgyid pa de thams cad stsol bar bgyid do //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-23: yid la re ba'i dgos pa de thams cad shin tu ring po nas kyang don yod pa'i zhags pas bcings nas zhags pa thams cad drangs te lag tu thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-24: sgrub pa mchog gi dngos grub kyi de kho na nyid thams cad 'grub par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:224b-26: rig sngags 'chang ba nam mkha' la mchi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-0: 'jig rten gyi khams gang du sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams gang dang gang du mchi 'tshal ba de dang de thams cad du mchi bar @225a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-2: thams cad du gtso bor 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-3: thams cad du mchod par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-4: ci ste rmi lam mthong bar 'tshal na gu gul la lan brgya rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas nas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-5: nyal kar 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la bdug spos su phul te nyal na /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-8: gang dris pa de thams cad smra bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-9: ji ltar bsam pa'i mchog stsol cing sgrib pa dang sdig pa thams cad ma mchis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-13: tshangs pa dgug par 'tshal zhing mthong bar 'tshal na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-14: de'i tshe shing aarga'i 'o ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-16: rgya skyegs ril bur bgyis pa la bzlas brjod brgya rtsa brgyad bgyis la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-17: tshangs pa la bdug spos su phul na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-18: tshangs pa rang gi gzugs kyis mdun na mchis shing mchog 'tshal ba thams cad rjes su stsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225a-19: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten la thug pa'i bar gyi tshangs pa'i gnas dang gzhal med khang mthong bar 'gyur zhing tshangs ba'i gzugs kyi cha byad 'chang ba'i mchog stsol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-0: lha'i gnas thams cad du mes bo yin no zhes tshig mngon par brjod bar [?] @225b 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-2: 'dzam bu'i gling pa'i mi bud med dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-10: dmangs rigs de thams cad thams cad du tshangs pa'o zhes sems par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-12: 'khor du bcas pas mchod pa'i sprin chen po bgyid par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-13: de nas sred med kyi bu dgug par 'tshal na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-14: des lha'i gnas su sred med kyi bu'i gzugs brnyan gyi mdun du nye bar sbyin sreg gi cho ga bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-15: rig sngags 'chang gtsang mar gyur pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-18: sna ma dang shing aarga'i ya ma sreg shing gi me sbar ba la gu gul dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-21: zhun mar bsres pa'i sbyin sreg brgya stong bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-23: sred med kyi bu rang gi gzugs kyis mdun na mchis shing rig sngags 'chang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-26: sgrub pa dam pa 'di don yod pa'i lcags kyus 'gugs shing rig sngags kyi rgyal po'i chos lugs chen pos bkug na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-31: ci zhig don du gnyer ba de smros shig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:225b-32: thams cad rjes su sbyin par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-0: de nas rig sngags 'chang gis don @226a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-1: gang yid la bsams te smras pa de thams cad stsol bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-2: gzugs sna tshogs pa'i mchog kyang rjes su stsol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-3: gzhan yang gzugs sna tshogs pa mchog gtso bo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-4: dgos pa'i las sgrub pa'i mchog rjes su stsol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-5: de nas lha chen po dgug par 'tshal na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-6: rig sngags 'chang gtsang ma shin tu khrus bgyis pa gos gtsang ma bgos pa des lha'i gnas su mchis pa la lha chen po'i mdun du gu gul dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-7: padma'i phye ma dang zhun mar bsres pa'i sbyin sreg stong rtsa brgyad bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-8: stong rtsa brgyad rdzogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-9: lha chen po rang gi gzugs kyis mdun na mchis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-10: de nas nag po chen po dgug par 'tshal na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-11: rig sngags 'chang shin tu khrus bgyis pa gos gtsang ma bgos pas dur khrod du mchis la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-12: zla ba mar gyi ngo'i ches bcu bzhi la nyin zhag gcig smyung ba bgyis pas padma gsar pa'i phye ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-16: zhun mar dang sbyar ba brgyad stong don yod pa'i lcags kyu'i bzlas brjod kyis dur khrod kyi shing gi me la bzlas brjod bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-17: ra khrag gi gtor ma dang 'bras thug po che'i chan gyis lha bshos dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226a-18: me tog dmar po dbul bar bgyi'o /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-0: @226b las 'di yongs su rdzogs par bgyis na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-1: nag po chen po ma mo'i tshogs kyi 'khor dang bcas pa mdun na mchis shing rig sngags 'chang la legs so zhes bya ba gsol te; rig sngags 'chang legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-2: sgrub pa'i cho ga bzang po 'dis bdag yongs su mgu yi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-4: mchog rjes su sbyin par bgyi'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-6: ji ltar yid la byed pa re ba de thams cad rjes su sbyin par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-8: yongs su bskyang ba'i don du bdag rtag tu rjes su 'brang bar bgyi'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-11: gang don du gnyer ba de thams cad 'thob cing thams cad du rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-12: thams cad du thams cad bgyid par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-13: dran pa tsam la sogs pas las thams cad bgyid cing nye bar gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-14: rtag tu lta zhing spyir thams cad bgyid par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-15: gzhan yang dgos pa sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-16: las su bgyi ba bgyid par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-17: ma mo'i tshogs kyi 'khor thams cad dbang du gyur nas gnas te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:226b-18: las thams cad bsgo ba bzhin du bgyid par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227a-2: thams cad rjes su 'brang zhing las thams cad bgyid bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227a-3: ci ste 'dod pa'i gzugs can ma dgug par 'tshal na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227a-4: de nas rig sngags 'chang gtsang ma shin tu khrus bgyis pa gos gtsang ma bsgos pas shin tu dri zhim po'i dris lus lhag par bsgos la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227a-5: gang na me tog gi shing ljon pa mchis pa der mchis la zla ba mar gyi ngo'i tshes bcu bzhi'i nyin zhag gcig smyung ba bgyis pas shin tu dri zhim pa'i dri'i shing gi me sbar ba la pu shel tsi dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227a-11: zhun mar dang sbyar ba'i sbyin sreg lan stong rtsa brgyad bgyi'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-15: ci ste sring mor gyur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-16: de'i tshe longs spyod thams cad kyis yongs su skyong bar bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-17: ji ltar yid la bsam pa'i bud med dpag chad brgya'i pha rol nas kyang bkug ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-18: yongs su longs spyad pa'i phyir yongs su spyod par bgyid cing /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-20: ci ste chung mar gyur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-22: lha rdzas kyi gzhal med khang dam pa yongs su longs spyod pa'i gzhal med khang mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-23: lha rdzas kyi bza' ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-25: longs spyod stsol bar bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-26: ro bro ba'i mchog ro brgya dang ldan pa ches khyad par du 'phags pa'i longs spyod stsol bar bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-27: mchog tu dga' ba'i rtsed mos 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i longs spyod la yongs su spyod par bgyid do; ;lha rdzas kyi dri dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:227b-33: lhab lhub kyis brgyan pa'i gzhal med khang du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-2: bang ba yongs su gang zhing mchis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-12: dngul skyogs dpag tu med pa thob pa'i gter stsol bar bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-18: bran mo rab tu mang po mang por 'phel zhing mchis par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-19: mal cha'i longs spyod sna tshogs stsol par bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-20: lha rdzas kyi chung ma'i longs spyod bud med gzugs sna tshogs pa'i 'khor brgya dang ldan pa nyin gcig bzhin du gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-21: yo byad thams cad phun sum tshogs pas ji srid 'tsho'i bar du gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-22: tshe lha'i lo stong thub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-23: rig sngags 'chang gis bag yod par bgyid ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-24: dkon mchog gsum la mchog tu gus pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-25: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-26: rdo rje 'dzin la mchog tu gus par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-27: rtag tu sbyin pa la mngon par dga' bar bgyi zhing sems can thams cad la mchog tu snying brtse bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-28: gzhan du mi smra bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228a-29: gal te las byed par gyur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-0: de'i tshe rgyal po la bgyi ba bzhin du las thams cad bgyid @228b de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-1: shin tu yongs su rdzogs kyi bar du las la mngon par brtson par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-2: ci ste mngag gzhug mar gyur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-3: gnas gang du mngags pa de'i gnas thams cad du mchis te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-4: dpag tshad stong gi pha rol tu mchi zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-5: skad cig gis slar yang mchi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-6: thams cad du gter chen po 'byin par bgyid /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-23: ci ste pho nya mor gyur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-24: phyogs bcu thams cad du mchi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-27: lha ma yin gyi gnas su mchi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-28: nam mkha' lding gi gnas su mchi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-30: lto 'phye chen po'i gnas su mchi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:228b-33: 'byung po'i gnas su mchi zhing thams cad du pho nya'i bya ba bgyis nas slar mchi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:229a-0: skad cig gis dpag tshad stong du mchi zhing @229a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:229a-2: skad cig gis dpag tshad stong du thams cad du phyin nas pho nya'i bya ba bgyid do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:229a-3: ji srid sa'i 'og gi bar du 'jug cing phyir yang mchi'o; ;bya ba shin tu yongs su rdzogs par bgyis nas bag yod pas yang las thams cad bgyi ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:229a-4: nyin gcig bzhin du mchod yon dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:229a-5: rkang pa bkru ba stsal bar bgyi'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:244b-1: de nas rang rang gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing na rab tu bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gi bsod nams kyi phung po chen po yongs su bzung bar 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259a-19: gang dang gang du 'gro ba na bde bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259a-20: de'i lus la mes mi tshugs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259a-21: chu chen pos 'khyer bar mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259a-22: lcags kyu'i rig sngags dran pa dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259a-29: de la byad kyis mi tshugs /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259a-32: gsang sngags dran pa tsam dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259a-33: bdug pas bdag bdug pa ni /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259b-2: dgra dang phyir rgol ba'i mi sems can ma rungs pa mi bzad pa rnams dang 'thab mo 'gyed cing g-yul 'gyed pa na bdag nyid bdug pas bdug cing rig sngags lan gcig dran par byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:259b-3: sa thams cad du rgyal bar 'gyur te /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260a-1: ro; ;bde ba thams cad kyis tshim par thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260a-2: gnas gcig nas ril bu bdun blangs pa las khro bo'i lcags kyu lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260a-4: gzhan gang rung ba nas dge sbyong dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260a-20: rgud pa thams cad rnam par zhig par 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260a-27: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par zhig par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260a-28: sngon bsags pa'i sgrib pa thams cad mod la rnam par zhig par 'gyur te /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260b-1: bdug pa mchgo gis bdugs par byas pas dogs par mi bya'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260b-11: thams cad du sbyar ba la dogs par mi bya'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:260b-13: sgo chen por nam langs ka dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261a-6: klu mthu bo che thams cad bdug pa'i dri bla na med pas skrag par 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261a-24: dus thams cad bla na med pa'i gzi byin skyed par byed do //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261a-26: thig le skar ma lta bu ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261a-27: lha yi nyi ma bzhin du dpa'//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261a-28: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od dang mtshungs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261a-29: bsod nams gzi brjid dag gis 'bar //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261a-31: mun pa'i nang na snang bar 'gyur //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261b-0: tshogs kyi dkyil na mdzes pa @261b ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261b-1: skar ma'i tshogs dang zla ba bzhin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261b-2: bsod nams bye ba stong phrag dang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261b-14: kun tu bla med grub par 'gyur //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261b-19: kun tu 'grub pa bla na med //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:261b-26: gos gtsang ma bgos shing gtsang mas zla ba yar gyi ngo tshes bcu gsum skar ma rgyal la bab pa'i tshe chu gtsang ma dang zhib tu btags la rgya shug gi 'bru tsam byas te grib ma la bskams la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:262a-0: gang gi tshe dgos pa rtsom pa de'i tshe khro bo'i rgyal po'i lcags kyu la lan nyi shu rtsa gnyis bzlas brjod byas te smin mtshams su thig @262a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:262a-2: smin mtshams su thig le bzang po de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyi rlabs kyis byin gyis brlabs pa mtshan nyid bzhin du thig le byas te byin gyis brlabs pa byas pa'i mod la de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gtsug tor gyi mtshan nyid rnam par mdzes pa'i thig le dang mnyam par mtshungs par brgyan par 'gyur /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:262b-18: mchog tu mdog sdug cing 'khrig pa dang ldan pa /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:262b-21: lus ngo tsha tsha ltar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:262b-23: spyi bo yid tsam btud nas gser gyi snod rin po ches bkang ba thogs te rig sngags 'chang la 'bul bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:262b-24: rig sngags 'chang bas cang mi smra bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-0: rin po che'i snod kyang blang @263a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-2: gsang sngags 'ba' zhig dran par bya zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-3: yungs kar gyis gzhon nu ma la brdeg par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-4: ci ste mi sdug pa 'byin cing bzhin bsgyur ba; khro bo'i gzugs mchu 'phyang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-6: skra ral pa ser la gyen du brdzes la ral pa cod pan gyis brgyan par ston na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-7: rig sngags 'chang bas skrag par mi bya'o; ;khro bo'i lcags kyu 'ba' zhig dran par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-8: yang yungs kar gyis mgo'i spyi bor brdeg cing khros pa'i gzugs kyis dran par byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-9: de'i tshe de sa la 'gyel te 'dre ldog cing kye rig sngags 'chang thugs rje can khyod rig sngags 'chang khyab 'jug gi gzugs can gum mo gum mo zhes sgra 'byin to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-10: de nas rig sngags 'chang pas rjes su brtags te gal te kha chu dbu bar 'byung na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-11: rig sngags 'chang bas de blangs la rkang pa dang byin par bskus na rlung gi phung po bdun pa'i rlung la zhon te nam mkha' la 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-12: rig sngags 'chang ba'i 'khor los bsgyur bar 'gyur zhing rig sngags 'chang ba'i 'khor brgya phrag bye ba dgu bcu rtsa dgus bskor bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263a-13: skad cig tu stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams gyi mthar song zhing slar yang 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-0: skyes nas lo bcu drug lon pa dang @263b 'dra zhing skra yid tsam 'khyil zhing 'khyil ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-1: rnam chag du bu dri ma med cing spen tog 'phyang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-2: mkhrig ma gdu bus brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-3: lus padma 'dra zhing dkar sham du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-4: tshe bskal pa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis thub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-5: rig sngags 'chang ba'i 'khor los bsgyur ba stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa gnyis kyi 'khor gyis bskor bar 'gyur ro; ;gnas thams cad du dpon por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-6: gal te thig le byas te mi snang bar gyur na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-9: 'byung po thams cad kyi khyim sgo phye ste 'dug par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-12: 'byung po 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad bgyi ba ci mchis zhes dbang du 'gyur zhing bka' bzhin du 'jug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-13: mngags pa'i dgos pa thams cad byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-14: khyim thams cad du re rer yang dbon po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-15: bka' bzhin byed pa'i rgyal por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-16: gal te mtshog mar thig le byas na brgya byin dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-17: lha rnams kyi dbang po sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i ris kyi bdag po'i lha dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:263b-18: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi ris kyi lha'i bu dang bcas pa thams cad kyis mchod par 'gyur te; rig sngags 'chang ba la bya ba thams cad kyis bsnyen bkur byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-0: shin tu mthong ba'i lha'i rigs kyi lha rnams dang lhan cig tu rtse dga' kun tu spyod par @264a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-2: tshe lha'i lo stong legs par thub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-3: lte ba'i gnas su thig le byas te klu mtshor zhugs pa tsam gyis mod la klu'i rgyal po dpung dang g-yog tu bcas chung ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-5: thams cad mdun na 'dug cing 'di skad ces smras te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-6: rig sngags 'chang ba bka' stsol cig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-8: dgos pa thams cad bgyi zhing rnam 'tsho'i bar du nye bar gnas par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-9: yo byad thams cad kyis mi bral bar bsgrub par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-10: klu'am lha'i longs spyod mchog tu longs spyad pas rtse bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-11: lha'i lo stong gi bar du rjes su gnas par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-12: nor thams cad rjes su stsal bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-13: rin po che rnam pa sna tshogs gser dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-25: shin tu bzang po rnams su stsal bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-26: lha rdzas kyi bza' ba mchog dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-27: lha rdzas kyi nor gyi phung pos bang mdzod rnams rab tu dgang bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-28: shin tu char ches pa gcad par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-29: char dkon pa na char bab par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-30: dus ma yin pa'i char gcad par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264a-31: dus su char dbab pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-0: @264b dus su char ba'i rgyun 'byung bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-1: lha rdzas kyi me tog sna tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-2: lha rdzas kyi 'bras bu sna tshogs nye bar bsgrub bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-3: nam 'tsho'i bang du gnas te bsnyen bkur bgyi'o; ;rig sngags 'chang ba'i rkang pa spyi bos blang bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-4: rig sngags 'chang ba de'i tshig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-5: bsam pa rjes su bskyang bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-6: dpung pa gnyis kyi bar du thig le byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-7: glang po che stong gi stobs yod par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-9: dgra thams cad kyi stobs kyis mi thub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-10: 'thab cing dmag gi g-yul 'gyed pa thams cad kyi nang du pha rol gnon pa'i stobs thogs pa med pa rgyal ba sbyin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-11: lha ma yin kun las kyang rgyal bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-12: lha thams cad 'di la bsrung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-14: bskyang ba'i phyir rtag tu zham 'bring du 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-20: g-yul 'gyed pa thams cad du rgyal ba sbyin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-21: lto bar thig le byas te khro bo'i lcags kyu'i rig sngags lan gcig dran par byas pa yid la ji ltar bsam pa ji bzhin byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-22: ci 'dod pa'i kha zas thob par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:264b-23: 'khor nyi shu dang bcas pas ji ltar 'dod pa thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-0: sker thig le byas te khro bo'i lcags kyu sker lan gcig bzlas brjod @265a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-1: byed cing rgyal po'i pho brang du song na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-6: btsun mo'i 'khor dang bcas pas mchod par 'os pa'i mchog tu 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-7: dbang phyug chen po'i chen po thob pa grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-8: lag mthil du thig le byas te lan gcig bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-9: gang la reg pa de dbang du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-10: gang 'dod pa de thams cad sbyin zhing bsgo ba de thams cad byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-11: lag pa g-yas pa la bskus la lan gcig bzlas brjod byas te grong khyer gyi sgo la brdabs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-12: grong khyer na gnas pa'i gnod sbyin dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-13: srin po thams cad dbang du 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-14: mdun na gnas shing de thams cad bsgo ba bzhin byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-15: grong de na skye bo gang dag gnas pa bud med dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-18: bu mo de thams cad dbang du 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-19: mdun na gnas shing ji srid grong khyer der 'dug par 'dod pas de srid du thams cad ci bya ba thams cad byed cing gnas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-21: lag pa g-yon pa la bskus te rgyal po'i sgo la brdabs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-22: ji srid 'dug par 'dod pa de srid du thams cad dbang du gyur pa sbyin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265a-23: lag pa g-yas pa la bskus shing lan gcig bzlas brjod bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-0: @265b [?] gi gsang ba'i sgo la brdab ba byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-1: gsang ba'i khyim thams cad sgo phye ste 'dug cing khyim na gnas pa de dag thams cad dbang du gyur te 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-2: rkang pa gnyis la bsku zhing gsang sngags lan gcig dran par byas te dur khrod du song na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-3: dur khrod na gnas pa'i gnod sbyin dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-6: sha za thams cad mdun na gnas shing dbang du 'gyur ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-7: khyim gyi sgo thams cad phye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-8: thams cad bya ba ci yod pa byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-9: bral gnyis la bskus te nags tshal gyi nang du zhugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-10: zhugs pa tsam gyis khyim na gnas pa thams cad mdun na gnas shing khyim gyi sgo thams cad phye ste 'dug par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-11: sman gyi rdzas thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-15: mgo lcog gi nags tshal gyi rang gi ngo bo thams cad ji ltar 'dod pa blang ba bzhin du mdun na 'dug par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-16: dpal lha mo chen mo'i nu ma'i bar du bsku zhing khros pas gsang sngags lan gcig bzlas brjod byas shing gu gul la bzlas brjod byas te bdug pa dbul zhing mig mi 'dzum par bltas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-17: dpal lha mo chen mo bka' stsol cing mchog thams cad sbyin par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-18: nor shin tu mang po rnyed pa sbyin par mdzad do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:265b-19: dpal lha mo chen mo rtag tu khyim na gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-1: thams cad kyis yongs su skyong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-2: nam 'tsho'i bar du bsnyen bkur byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-3: mi'i 'o ma dang lhan cig tu bdar la lan gcig bzlas brjod byas te mig la bskus na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-4: gter thams cad mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-5: mtshan mo yang nyin par bzhin mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-6: mchu'i thor to la thig le bya zhing lan gcig bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-7: gang la smra ba de dbang du 'gyur zhing gang 'dod pa de thams cad thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-8: tshig gzung bar bya bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-9: kha nas autpa la'i dri mnam par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-10: gdon la thig le byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-13: gdon thams cad la thig le byas shing lan cig gsang sngags dran par byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-14: mod la tshangs pa'i srin po la sogs pa'i bar du thams cad du zhing 'bros par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-15: thig le tsam dang dran pa tsam gyis thams cad las yongs su thar bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-16: 'jigs pa thams cad la thig le byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-18: phrag pa gnyis la thig le bya zhing khro bo lan gcig dran par byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266a-20: mtshal dang sbyar te dri chab dang bsres nas lag pa dang rkang ba la bskus shing gsang sngags lan bdun dran par byas nas phu zhes byas na me 'bar bar 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-0: ji tsam 'dod kyi bar du 'bar ba 'byung bar 'gyur @266b ro; ;mchu la bsku zhing bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-1: dbugs rgyu ba rnams me 'bar ba 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-2: lus mtha' dag bsku zhing gsang sngags mang du bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-5: nyung kar gyis bskrad nas bum pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-6: bum pa la zhi ba'i thig le byas te dri chus steng du gtor ba dang bcas pa byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-7: phyir yang gnas par 'gyur ro; ;ral gri dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-15: mdung la bsku zhing rjes su dran par byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-16: skad cig du thams cad 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-21: dung la bskus te gnas mthon por bus na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-22: sgra gang thos pa tsam gyis sems can thams cad kyi khro ba thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-23: sdig pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-24: ngan pa dang ma rungs pa thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-27: ser ba thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-28: grong khyer gyi sgo bzhir bus na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-29: byur dang gnod pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:266b-37: 'khrug pa thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-3: grib gnon gyi 'jigs pa thams cad 'byung bar mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-4: rims thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-5: nad thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-9: dug gi 'jigs pa thams cad las yongs su thar bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-11: pha rol gyi dmag tshogs kyis 'jigs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-13: phyir rgol ba'i 'jigs pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar 'gyur zhing lan 'ga' yang 'byung bar mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-24: nad thams cad kyi 'jigs pa chen po 'byung ba la khang pa'i steng du skad drag pos lan gcig dung 'bud cing bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-25: bus pa tsam gyi mod la thams cad rab tu zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-26: char mi 'bab pa'i tshe klu'i gnas mtsho 'gram du bus na mod la klu'i rgyal po rnams char pa'i rgyun gtong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-27: char ches pa'i tshe sprin logs su bus na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-28: shin tu char che ba zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-29: lan 'ga' yang mtshan ma ngan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267a-30: bkra mi shis pa 'byung bar mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-0: ri mthon po'i khar bus te ji @267b tsam dung sgra thos pa de tsam du chun chad mtshams chen po bcad pa byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-2: bskor zhing bus na dkyil 'khor gyi mtshams bcad par byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-3: de nas khro bo'i rgyal po'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga grub pa bla na med pa thams cad bya ba la sems can thams cad zhi bar bya ba la nas dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-5: mar bsres la shing aarga'i me bus te lan nyi shu rtsa gcig sbyin sreg byas pa tsam gyis dpag tshad kyi nang kun tu zhi ba chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-6: yams kyi nad kyi gnod pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-9: 'gyed pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-10: lan brgya rtsa brgyad sbyin sreg byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-11: dpag tshad stong tshun chad kun tu zhi ba chen po'i las byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-17: mar dang bsres te sbyin sreg bya ba ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-18: lan bdun sbyin sreg byas na dpag tshad brgya kun tu rgyas pa chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-19: lan nyi shu rtsa gcig sbyin sreg byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-20: dpag tshad brgya tshun chad rgyas pa chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-21: lan brgya rtsa brgyad sbyin sreg byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-22: dpag tshad brgya stong kun tu rgyas pa chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:267b-23: shing dri mi zhim pa'i me bus te 'bras kyi phub ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-0: yungs kar mar dang bsres te shing tsher ma can gyi yam sreg shing gi me sbar te sbyin @268a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-4: yid la ji ltar sems shing 'dod pa thams cad du mngon spyod kyi las rnams byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-9: sbrang rtsi rnams mar dang sbyar te shing aarga'i yam sreg shing gi me sbar te sbyin sreg lan bdun byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-10: rang gi khro bo'i gsang sngags sgrub pa 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-12: don yod pa'i lcags kyu 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-13: nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas brjod dang sbyin sreg byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-14: don yod pa'i zhags pa'i snying po 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-15: lan brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas brjod sbyin sreg byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-16: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs kyi spyi 'grub par 'gyur ba 'di lta ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-17: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-21: gzhan yang khro bo chen po stong phrag brgya mchog tu grub pa chen por 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:268a-27: mar rnams sbyar te chang ba bdun sbyin sreg byas na; bram ze thams cad dbang du 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-3: mnar med pa la gzhol ba dang /
