K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-7: sngon gyi sgrib pa bsags pa dang bcas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-8: bskal pa brgyar bsags pa'i sdig pa de dag thams cad rnam par 'jig par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-9: nad dang 'jigs pa thams cad las yongs su grol bar 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-12: phyir rgol ba thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-13: mi mdza' ba rnam par 'jigs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-14: ras ris kyi sku gzugs shin tu chung ba byed pa gang yin pa de yang phan bar byed par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-19: dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa byed pa'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-20: khrus kyi bum pa gang bkod pa'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-21: rdul sel bar byed pa tsam yang rung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:278b-22: rig sngags 'chang de'i rigs kyi bu'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-0: dge bsnyen mas de bzhin gshegs pa gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa dgu'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i drung du @279a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-1: dge ba'i rtsa ba chen po bskyed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-2: bsod nams kyi phung po chen po yongs su 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-3: pha rol tu phyin ba drug yongs su rdzogs par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-4: mtshams med pa lnga rnam par sbyangs shing bskal ba'i mthar thug par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-6: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis gzigs 'dod par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-7: skye ba rjes nas kyang 'jig rten gyi khams bde ba can du 'gro bar 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-8: padma las brdzus te skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-9: skye ba'i skye ba dran par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-10: rnam par grol ba'i dkyil 'khor gsang ba padma yangs pa'i dkyil 'khro do nyod zhags pa'i snying po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-11: don yod pa'i khro bo lcags kyu'i gzungs 'di yang mtha' dag yongs su rdzogs par kha ton du gnas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-12: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i rigs kyi dam tshig gsang ba rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-13: gsang sngags rim par phye ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-16: dkyil 'khor rim par phye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-17: cho ga zhib mo thams cad mngon sum du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-18: sangs rgyas kyi zhing nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing du 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279a-19: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mngon sum du mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-0: yon tan thams cad kyi pha rol tu @279b phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-1: dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad yang dag par sdud par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-2: bsod nams kyi tshogs chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-3: 'jig rten thams cad kyi bla mar yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-5: 'jig rten thams cad dga' bar yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-6: thams cad du mchod par 'os par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-7: rig sngags thams cad grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-8: yid la bsam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-9: dgos pa thams cad grub par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-10: thams cad du thogs pa med pa mkhas pa'i blo ru 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-11: de nas khro bo'i lcags kyu'i dkyil 'khor cho ga zhib mo thams cad kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-12: gsang ba'i phyag rgya bla na med pa bshad par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-13: 'khor yug tu them skas bzhi dang ldan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-14: sa dang ba byung bsres pa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi pa bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-15: gzings kyi rgya dang tshad mnyam pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-16: shin tu tshad la bab cing legs par rnam par 'byes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-17: legs par byugs shing shin tu 'jam pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-18: 'jam zhing mnyen pa dang ldan pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-19: tshon sna tshogs pas rnam par phye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-20: dkyil 'khor mchog gi thig btab la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-21: sna tshogs tshon rtsis rnam par dbye //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-22: sgo bzhi shin tu rnam 'byes pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:279b-23: 'khor yug them skas bzhi dang ldan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-2: dbus kyi dkyil 'khor snying por yang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-3: shin tu rnam 'byes tshad la bab //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-4: khru yi tshad du bya ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-5: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi mnyam ba yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-6: snying po'i dkyil 'khor dbus su yang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-7: mkhas pas shin tu rnam 'byes pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-9: lcags kyu phyogs dang rtse gsum dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-10: ge sar padma'i khor yug tu; ;snying por gyur pa'i dbus mchog la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-11: khro bo zhags pa yang bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-12: drag po'i gzugs can 'jigs par byed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-13: ral gri dang ni dgra sta'i phyag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-14: ral ba'i cod pan gyis brgyan cing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-15: rgyan rnams kun gyis rnam par brgyan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-17: zhags pas kun nas dkris pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-18: mdung rtse gsum pa nam mkha' la phyir phyogs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-19: padma dang bcas la byas pa la gra grar 'bar ba'i gdong bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-20: mdung rtse gsum dang padma la rab tu gnas pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-21: drag po'i zhal 'jigs par byed pa chen po mche ba rnam par gcigs pa; zhal 'jigs su rung ba 'bar ba'i snying por chud pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-22: nang gi ri mo la lcags sgrog dang mdung rtse gsum pa'i gdong bri bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-23: 'bar ba'i snying po dang bcas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-24: kha dog sna tshogs pa'i tshon rtsis bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-25: ri mo gnyis pa'i nang du padma kha phyed bye ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-26: gser 'bar ba dang bcas pa'i padma bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280a-27: ri mo gsum pa'i nang du 'khor lo'i rnam pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-0: mu @280b khyud kyi phyi rol tu lag pa'i phyag rgya yang bri bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-1: mtshon cha sna tshogs pa 'dzin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-22: rtse gsum dag kha dog sna tshogs 'bar ba khor yug tu yongs su bskor ba bri bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-23: kha khyer byi rnam pas brgyan pa la kha khyer gyi phyi rol dkyil 'khor gyi gnas su mtshan ma sna tshogs bri bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-24: rigs chen po bzhi thun mong ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyag rgya bri bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-26: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi mtshan ma'i phyag rgya yang bri bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-27: lho ru padma yangs pa'i mtshan ma dkyil 'khor gyi phyag rgya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-28: nub kyi gnas kyi dkyil 'khor du nor bu'i rigs kyi mtshan ma'i phyag rgya rnams kyang bri bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-29: byang du rdo rje'i rigs kyi mtshan ma'i phyag rgya yang dag par bri'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-30: shar gyi sgo ru de bzhing shes pa'i rigs kyi khor bo'i rgyal po sgo ru bri bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-31: lho ru padma yangs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi khro bo rnams so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-32: nub tu nor bu'i rigs kyi khro bo'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:280b-33: byang du rdo rje'i rigs kyi khor bo bri bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-1: thams cad kyi gzugs 'bar ba'i snying po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-2: rgyan thams cad kyis rnam par brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-3: lag pa bzhi pa mtshon cha sna tshogs pa 'dzin pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-4: ri rab la gnas pa skyil mo krung phyed pa lus cung zad bskum pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-5: phyi'i ri mo'i dkyil 'khor du nor bu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-8: mdung rtse gsum pa dag go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-9: khor yug tu kha khyer 'bar bas dkyil 'khor gyi khor yug tu brgyan pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-13: tshon sna lnga pa'i skud pas kun nas dkyil 'khor la yang dag par brgyan pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-14: ro bro ba'i mchog dang ldan pa'i gtor mas gang ba'i snod ci 'byor pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-15: gtor ma'i las kyi cho gas 'byor pa dang rjes su mthun par gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-20: gtor ma dkar pos bkang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-21: 'bras bu rnam pa sna tshogs pa nyid dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-25: me tog kun nas bcal du dgram mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-27: yungs kar gyis gtor bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-28: snying po'i dkyil 'khor gyi grar mchod yon dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-30: rin po che sna bdun rab tu dgram mo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281a-31: dri'i chus bkang ba'i bum pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-0: legs par brgyan pa'i bum pa byas nas mkhas @281b pas dar bzang po bcings te dbus kyi dkyil 'khor du gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-1: sgo bzhir dri chab kyi gang ba'i bum pa dar gyis bcings pa gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-2: mkhas pas sgo dang sga ru ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-7: mdung rtse gsum la zho dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-10: mchog gi bza' ba ma nyams pas shin tu mdzes pa'i gtor ma gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-16: mu da ga'i la du ba hvags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-17: kha yy'a ni bzang po rnams gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-18: gtor ma'i las la khor yug tu me tog bzang po dgram zhing phreng bas brgyan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-19: 'bru'i rnam pa sna tshogs bzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-20: 'bras bu'i ngo bo rnam pa sna tshogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-22: lo ma mdzes pa bkram ste gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-23: khor yug tu mar me'i phreng ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-24: de bzhin du aa ga ru dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-31: hvags sbyar ba'i bdug pa ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-32: bdug pa 'di dag dbul bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-33: dkyil 'khor gyi khor yug tu bdug pa 'thul ba'i pog phor gzhag par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:281b-34: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la bdug pa dbul bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-3: gtsug tor bcing zhing bdag srung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-6: rig sngags dkyil 'khor mthong ba dang phyag bya zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-8: dam tshig kyang sbyin par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-9: rtag tu gsang ba'i las byas te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-10: de kho na bzhin du gsang sngags bzlas pa yang bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-11: dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga tshad ma las dgos pa 'di dag thams cad byas nas de'i 'og tu rig sngags 'chang gis las thams cad kyi dngos grub bla na med pa'o; ;rgyal ba rigs bzhis yongs su bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa de dag thams cad ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-12: 'gro ba bzang por skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-13: de bzhin du bde ba can du 'od dpag med kyi spyan sngar padma las brdzus te skye bar the tshom med do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-14: lha'i gzugs shin tu mdzes pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-15: rgyan thams cad kyis rnam par brgyan pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-16: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub chen po thob par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-18: 'jig rten pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi dngos grub bla na med pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-19: cho ga zhib mo'i dngos grub dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-21: khro bo'i rgyal po dngos grub bla na med pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282a-23: sgrib pa thams cad sel ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-0: mod la gdug pa thams cad 'jig @282b ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-1: dgra thams cad zlog pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-2: mod la nad thams cad rab tu zhi ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-4: thams cad du dngos grub bla na med pa gang yin pa grub par 'gyur ro; ;'jig rten thams cad kyi mnga' bdag dang rtag tu dga' bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-5: de rtag tu rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-6: rtag tu rgyal po dang blon por bcas pa rnams kyis dus rgyun du bla na med pa'i mchod pa'i gnas su 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-7: gzhan yang ljongs thams cad blta zhing mchod pas rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-8: de bzhin nyid du yang dge sbyong rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-16: bu mo thams cad kyang dga' bar 'gyur ro; ;rtag tu tshig btsan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-17: rtag tu lha rnams kyis mngon par bsrungs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-18: skabs gsum gyi dbang po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-20: rdo rje snying po bdag nyid chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-28: de bzhin du rgyal po chen po bzhi rnams rtag tu rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:282b-29: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs shing mthong ba la yang dus rtag tu srung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-1: rtag tu smra ba nyung zhing mkhas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-2: thams cad du dngos grub thob bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-6: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis kyang dgyes pa dang bcas pas byin gyis rlob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-9: de bzhin gshegs pas dbugs 'byin par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-10: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs las skyes pa'i sras ji lta ba bzhin no; ;'di ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-11: de rnams kyi mngal gyi gnas su skye ba'i tha ma yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-12: rtag tu skye ba dran par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-14: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub tu 'gro ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-15: rtag tu rgyal ba rnams kyi de kho na nyid mthong ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-16: rtag tu sangs rgyas thams cad la mngon sum du chos nyan par the tshom med do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-18: skye ba'i tha ma yin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-19: ji srid du sangs rgyas kyi byang chub tu rdzogs par sangs rgyas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-20: dgos pa gzhan rnam pa sna tshogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-21: khro bo lcags kyu'i las brgya phrag stong rnams rang gi 'dod pa'i blos bya'o; ;thams cad bu lan gcig bzlas brjod byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283a-22: thams cad du las thams cad bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283b-0: de nas byang chub sems dpa' @283b sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal du bltas te bzhin 'dzum pas khro bo chen po lcags kyu'i gzungs kyi kun tu snang bzhin pa'i 'od zer sna tshogs 'bar ba'i snying po lus las phyung ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283b-1: gang gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kun tu snang bar byas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283b-2: 'od zer gyi ba gang gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams su rin po che sna bdun gyi char 'bab pa'i snying po rab tu 'bebs par 'dod pa'i don dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283b-3: lha'i me tog sna tshogs kyi char 'bebs pa'i don dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283b-5: mthun par gsal ba'i dri dang rjes su mthun pa'i dri rnam par bkra ba'i char rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:283b-6: 'phags pa ras gzigs dbang phyug la phab bo //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300a-15: cho ga dang bcas pa rjes su 'thob ste /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300a-18: mchog sbyin yang so so 'thob cing thams cad du mngon par dbang bskur bar yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300a-19: lnga par rmi lam mthong ba na rnam par thar ba'i dkyil 'khor du brtags pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300a-20: don yod zhags pa'i dkyil 'khor du brtags pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300a-21: po ta la ka'i ri'i gzhal med khang dang bcas pa mthong ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300a-23: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300a-25: rig pa'i rgyal po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-0: de la yang 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug rang nyid sems can @300b de la rab tu 'jug par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-1: dam tshig dang phyag rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-4: gzungs kyi dngos grub so sor 'thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-5: rang nyid kyang don yod pa'i rig sngags kyi dbang gis mngon par dbang bskur te mngon par dbang bskur bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-6: cho ga zhib mo thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-7: dngos grub kyang rjes su stsol par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-8: mchog thams cad rab tu sbyin pa so sor 'thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-9: drug par rmi lam mthong ba na dkyil 'khor chen po mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-10: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug phyag stong pa mthong ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-11: gzhal med khang dang bcas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-20: de la yang rab tu 'jug par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-24: mngon par dbang bskur ba so sor 'thob ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-25: rig sngags thams cad kyi dngos grub kyi mchog sbyin pa so sor 'thob bo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-26: bdun par rmi lam chen po mthong bas de bzhin gshegs pa byang chub kyi snying por gshegs nas rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs pa mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:300b-27: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-0: de la yang de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad phyag gser gyi kha dog can brkyang ste rang nyid phyag gis bzung nas rab @301a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-2: rang nyid mngon par dbang bskur zhing mngon par dbang bskur bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-3: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs thams cad kyi dam tshig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-5: gsang sngags kyi dngos grub kyi mchog sbyin pa rjes su stsol bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-6: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing ston par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-7: nad sna tshogs pa dang ldan pa'i 'jig rten pa thams cad rig sngags 'chang gi rgyal po gcig por 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-8: skye ba brje ba 'chi 'pho ba'i dus su dran pa nye bar gnas shing dus byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-9: bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su padma las brdzus te skye ba'i skal ba dang bcas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-10: don yod pa'i rig sngags 'chang gi 'khor los bsgyur bar skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-11: de bzhin gshegs pa bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa dgus mchod par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-12: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mngon sum du mthong nas nye bar ston par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-13: thams cad du yang de rnams rang rang gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing nye bar ston par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-14: thams cad du yang rang gi gsang ba de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi dam tshig nye bar ston par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301a-15: bskal pa brgya stong phrag gi bar du yang sngon gyi skye ba rjes su dran par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-0: de @301b bzhin gshegs pa'i khyu mchog thams cad kyi rdzu 'phrul dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-4: dkyil 'khor gyi rim par phye ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-6: gzungs sngags rnams la mngon du phyogs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-7: skye ba skye bar yang rang gi bsod nams kyi las kyi tshogs dge ba'i rtsa ba rjes su dran par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-8: thams cad du gnas thams cad yongs su dag pa'i las kyi sgrub thabs kyi cho ga'i dngos grub tu 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-9: zhes rtsa ba'i snying po'i dngos grub bla na med pa bklags pas 'grub pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-10: de nas 'di'i yo byad dang cho ga sems can thams cad kyi re ba yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'i dngos grub tu 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-11: sdig pa thams cad nges par sreg pa la brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas sdig pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-12: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par nyams par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-13: gang dang gang gi las kyi sgrib pa rnams rjes su bcings par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-14: de yang nyi ma bdun gyis rang gi lus de yang rang gi gzugs kyis nges par 'gro ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-15: mdun du nye bar 'dug ste sbyin par byed pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-16: sngon gyi sgrib pa nye bar bsags pa 'di dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-17: sdig pa thams cad yongs su zad pa nyid dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:301b-18: dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-0: 'khrugs pa mtha' dag bzlas pa tsam gyis yang dag par smra bar @302a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-1: byed cing mi snang bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-2: rims thams cad la skud pa dkar po la mdud pa nyi shu rtsa gcig bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-3: brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas rims thams cad yongs su grol bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-4: nad thams cad la byabs pas yongs su grol bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-7: mdas kyang rung ste nad thams cad las yongs su grol bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-8: gdon thams cad la tshon skud sna lnga'i skud pa la mdud pa lan nyi shu rtsa gcig byas te bzlas brjod lan brgya rtsa brgyad byas te gdon gyis zin pa de'i mgul par bcings te lan bdun du byab par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-9: gu gul bdug pa sbyin par bye /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-10: bzlas brjod lan bdun bya bzhin pa dang bcas pas gang dang gang gi gdon gyis zin par gyur pa de yang rang gi lus kyis nges par 'gro ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-11: rig sngags 'chang gi mdun du nye bar 'dug nas thams cad smra bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-12: rang gis dris pa de thams cad smra bar byed do; ;bka' bsgo ba thams cad byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-16: 'gyed pa rnams thams cad la smra ba'i mchog tu 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-18: sbyin sreg gis yongs su grol lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-19: khar mur te rgyal po khab tu zhugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302a-20: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa dbang du gyur nas gnas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-0: dug 'thungs @302b pas chu la yongs su bzlas te sbyin par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-2: dug gis zos pa la byab bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-7: phye ma'i sbyor ba thams cad la dri dang bsres pa'i bum pa la stong phrag brgyad yongs su bzlas pa byas la bkru bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-8: bkrus pa tsam gyi mdo la thams cad nyams par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-9: gang yang lus zad pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-12: rgyal po'i dpal med pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-13: lus yongs su gdungs pa la rig sngags 'chang des ma rig pas dril chus yongs su gang ba'i bum pa dgu yungs kar gyis gtor te stong phrag brgyad yongs su bzlas brjod bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-14: de nas a'anta ra sa sta dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-22: lus kyi mar gyis bsku mnye byas nas lan brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas brjod byas te a'a ta byug par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-24: gong bu de mtshon chas dum bu brgyad du bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-25: snod yongs su gang ba bzhir 'phang bar bya zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-26: snod gang ba bzhi mtshams bzhir 'phang bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:302b-27: de nas snying pos lan brgya rtsa brgyad du byab par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-0: de nas ne'u gsing sngon po gang du chu rgyun 'bab par dri'i chu'i bum pas khrus byas shing gos dkar po dgus g-yogs @303a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-2: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la mchod pa bya zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-3: dkon mchog gsum la mchod pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-4: ji ltar 'byor pa'i bram ze'i ston mo yon dang bcas pa bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-5: de nas rang nyid byams pa dang ldan par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-6: ji ltar 'byor pa gya nom pa gya nom pas dkar ba'i zas kyi bza' ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-8: de nas dpal med pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-11: log par 'dren pa thams cad kyis ma rig pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-18: log 'dren gyis zin pa las yongs su grol lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-21: 'jigs pa thams cad las yongs su grol par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-22: lus kyi phung po yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-23: thams cad du 'jigs pa 'jigs par byed pa'i 'jigs pa med par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-25: sgrib pa dang kun nas nyon mongs pa thams cad las yongs su grol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-27: nad thams cad dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-28: skye ba brjes nas bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams su skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303a-29: skye ba'i skye ba dran par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-0: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis rtag tu yang dgongs par @303b 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-2: lha thams cad kyis ji srid byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas kyi bar du nge 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-3: mig na ba la pa la sha'i chu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-5: dri ma med pa'i chu la lan brgya rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas te sbyar bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-6: mig nad 'phral du zhi bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-8: gzhogs phyed na ba la mar dang til mar la lan brgya rtsa brgya yongs su bzlas nas 'jam par bsros pas sman shu ti la bsgos nas mgo la sku mnye byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-9: mgo bo'i nad thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-10: gzhogs phyed na ba'i nad thams cad yongs su grol lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-11: so'i zug rdul me tog sna ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-12: so shing la lan brgya rtsa brgyad du yongs su bzlas nas bza' bar byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-13: so'i zug rdu yong su grol lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-14: rna ba'i zug rdu la shu ti dang til mar la brgya rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas pas bkang bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-15: rna ba'i zug rdu thams cad yongs su grol lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-16: kha na ba la sman ma sh'u ro'i chu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-17: mar la brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas nas 'jam par bsros pa btung bar bya ste kha'i nad thams cad yongs su grol lo; ;lto ba'i zug rdu la lan tshva dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-18: chu la lan brgya rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas nas btung bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:303b-19: lto ba'i zug rdu yongs su grol lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-0: snying gi zug rdu la so so @304a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-3: bu ska ra'i rtsa ba rnams bzhi 'gyur gyi chu'i sum cha lhag mar lus kyi bar du bskol bar byas nas btung bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-4: lan brgyad bzlas pas snying gi zug rdu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-11: de bzhin du nad thams cad 'phral du sel bar 'jig rten gyi mgon pos 'di gsungs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-12: rgyal po'i 'jigs pas 'jigs pa rnams kyis yungs kar la yongs su bzlas nas rgyal po rnams kyi sgor gtor bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-13: rgyal po'i 'jigs pas 'jigs pa thams cad yongs su grol bar 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-14: thams cad du yang rgyal ba ster bar 'gyur ro; ;na le sham la stong rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas te na le sham gyi 'bras bu kha'i rtse mor bcug ste bcangs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-15: gang smras pa de dbang du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-16: gang blangs pa de so sor rnyed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-17: gnas thams cad du 'gro ba rnams la rgyal ba'i mchog chen po sbyin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-18: klu'i char 'bebs pa la bal po se'u'i lcug mas bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-19: gang du 'dod pa der klu'i char 'bebs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-20: klu'i mtshor song nas mtshan mo bdun du zho dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304a-23: yungs kar gyi sbyin sreg lan stong rtsa brgyad du byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-0: @304b gter chen po rnyed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-1: dbang phyug thob pa la 'bras yos dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-3: mar dang bsres pas sbyin sreg lan stong rtsa brgyad du byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-4: dbang phyug chen po so sor thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-5: dgra 'joms pa la s'a lu'i phub ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-7: tsha ba'i til mar dang bsres pas lan stong rtsa brgyad sbyin sreg byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-8: dgra thams cad med par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-9: dgra rnams thams cad rab tu 'dul bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-10: skrod par 'dod pas de nyid kyi thal ba las lan nyi shu rtsa gcig tu bzlas te dgra'i sgor gtor bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-11: mtshan mo gcig tu mi gnas te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-12: phyogs dang phyogs mtshams su 'bros par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-13: 'khrug pa'i g-yul ngor 'jug par 'dod pas yungs kar la lan stong phrag brgyad du yongs su bzlas te 'khrug pa'i g-yul ngo'i dbus su gtor bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-14: thams cad du rmugs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-16: rmongs par 'gyur te thams cad du rgyal pa ster bar 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-17: thams cad phyogs dang phyogs mtshams rnams su 'bros par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:304b-18: gnas na gnas pa thams cad kyi yang rgyal ba ster bar 'gyur ro; ;thams cad du thogs pa med pa'i stobs dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-0: ldong ros la lan stong phrag brgyad yongs su bzlas te mig gi mig sman du @305a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-1: byas na; mi snang bar 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-4: srin po thams cad kyis mi mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-5: gi ham la lan stong phrag brgyad yongs su bzlas te thig le byas nas bu ga thams cad du rab tu 'jug par byed cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-6: bu ga'i sgo thams cad bye ste sgor gnas par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-7: gang du 'dod pa der 'jug par byed do; ;gi ham gis snying gar thig le byas nas gang du 'jug par byed pa de dang de nyid du mchod pa chen por 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-10: lag pa gnyis la byugs pas gang la reg pa de dbang du 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-11: gang blangs pa de thams cad so sor rnyed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-12: rgyal po dbang du byed par 'dod pas lag pa g-yas pa la gi ham gis byugs nas lan stong rtsa brgyad yongs su bzlas te rgyal po'i sgo la thal lcag sbyin par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-13: rgyal po dang brtsun mo sras dang 'khro dang bcas pa bdag nyid dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-14: nor gyis kyang dbang du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-15: bud med dbang du byed pa la me tog dang 'bras bu la lan stong phrag brgya rtsa brgyad du yongs su bzlas nas sbyin par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-16: yang na mngag par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-17: 'phral nyid du dbang du byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-18: gang du 'dod pa de dang de nyid du 'gro'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305a-20: yang na ming smos pas nam mkha' la 'phang bar bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305b-0: gang gi ming @305b smos pa de 'gugs par 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305b-2: mthu stobs kyis slar yang phyir ldog ste 'gro'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305b-3: skyes pa dbang du byed pa la dz'a ti dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305b-4: sna ma'i me tog la lan bdun yongs su bzlas te sbyin par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305b-5: yang na mngag par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:305b-6: reg pa tsam gyis bdag nyid dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:317b-1: rnam pa sna tshogs par mdzes pa'i bstod pa'i rnam pas rol mo'i cho ga zhib mo ji lta ba bzhin tu gsang ba'i phyag rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:317b-2: dkyil 'khor gyi rim par phye ba dang rjes su mthun pas yang dag par bstod par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:317b-3: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang bcas pa'i rig sngags kyi lha dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:317b-10: rnam par 'phrul pa sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin byin gyis rlob pa'i rnam par 'phrul pas rig sngags 'chang thams cad kyi rmad du byung ba'i mchog gi dngos grub ster bar byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318a-5: nad thams cad sel bar byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318a-6: sdug bsngal mi bzad pa gdug pa thams cad 'joms par byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318a-9: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis yang dag par skul bar byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318a-11: rig sngags kyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad spyan 'dren par byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318a-21: dbugs ma phyin pa rnams kyi dbugs 'byin par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318a-22: ma grol ba rnams grol bar byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318a-25: mgon med pa rnams kyi mgon du gyur pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-0: 'khra sa med pa rnams kyis @318b 'khra sa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-1: bsnyen gnas ma byas pa rnams la bsnyen gnas sbyin pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-6: mi dge ba'i las kyi lam la spyod pa rnams dge ba'i chos la sbyor ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-7: 'jigs pas nyam thag pa rnams la mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-8: dbul bo rnams la nor sbyin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-9: 'bru dang bza' ba dang bral ba rnams la 'bru 'phel ba chen po sbyin pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-11: lam nyams pa rnams kyi lam ston par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-12: dus ma yin par 'chi bar 'gyur ba rnams kyi dus ma yin pa'i 'chi ba so sor 'gog pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-13: long ba rnams kyi mig sbyin par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-14: 'on pa rnams rna ba sbyin par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-15: sna nyams pa rnams kyi sna rnam par sbyong bar byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-16: reg pa med pa rnams kyi bde ba'i reg pa la nges par sbyor bar byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-17: longs spyod kyis nyam thag pa rnams kyi longs spyod sbyin par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:318b-18: dran pa nyams pa rnams kyi dran pa yongs su sbyong bar byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-1: tshul khrims nyams pa rnams kyi tshul khrims sbyin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-2: sbyin pa la rgyab kyis phyogs pa rnams la pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-3: brtson 'grus nyams pa rnams la stobs dang brtson 'grus kyi mchog sbyin pa'o; ;bzod pa dang bral ba rnams la bzod pa dang zhi ba sbyin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-4: bsam gtan nyams pa rnams la bsam gtan dang ting nge 'dzin ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-5: yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-6: shes rab nyams pa rnams la shes rab kun tu snang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-8: shes rab chen po'i snang ba yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-9: dam tshig mi shes pa rnams la dam tshig sbyin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-10: phyag rgya dang bral ba rnams kyi phyag rgya yongs su sbyor bar byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-12: gsang sngags la mi mkhas pa rnams la rig sngags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-13: gsang sngags rab tu sbyin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-14: mu stegs rnams la mu stegs smra ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-15: 'jug ngogs bzang po dang lam rab rab tu sgrub par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-16: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub las rgyab kyis phyogs pa rnams la sangs rgyas kyi byang chub chen po'i mchog sbyin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319a-17: 'khor ba las ma bsgral ba rnams sgrol bar byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-0: @319b mun pas long bar byed cing bsgribs pa rnams la myos pa'i mun pa sel ba sbyin par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-1: sgrib par bya ba rnams kyi sgrib pa dang bral bar byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-2: mtshams med pa lnga'i 'gro ba rnams kyis mtshams med pa lnga sbyong bar byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-3: ngag nyams pa rnams kyi ngag rnam par dag par byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-5: thun tshags dang bcas pa rnams kyi thun tshags dang bral zhing yongs su dag par byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-8: brda mi phrad pa rnams la brda sprod par byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-9: kun nas 'khrugs pa rnams kyi sems gnas pa'i mchog go /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-11: rmi lam ngan pa mthong ba rnams la rmi lam chen po'i mchog ston pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-13: skom pa rnams btung ba chen po'i ro la yongs su longs spyod par byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:319b-18: gdon gyis zin pa rnams kyi gdon dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-3: dgra bo phyin ci log pa rnams kyi dgra rnams dang bral bar byed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-4: dbul po rnams la nor sbyin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-5: bu bza' can rnams kyi bu bza' cher 'phel bar 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-7: nyi ma'i 'od zer stong gis kun tu snang ba'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-8: rgyal pos bcom pa rnams la longs spyod rgya chen po cher sbyin pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-9: 'khon pa rnams gcig tu byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-11: 'dod chags la chags pa rnams kyi 'dod chags rab tu 'joms pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-12: rmongs pa chung ba ma yin pa rnams kyi rmongs pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320a-14: gzhan gyi dbang du gyur pa'i sems can rnams kyi 'jigs pa med par 'gyur zhing /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320b-4: byang chub sems dpa' mthong ba dang bral ba rnams kyi byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen po mthong bar 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320b-7: sgrib pa thams cad las yongs su grol bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320b-9: don yod pa'i mchod pa'i nor bu'i snying po'i gzungs spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis gsungs pa ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320b-11: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi mchod pa'i sprin /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:320b-13: sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad du rin po che sna bdun gyi mchod pa'i sprin gyi char 'bebs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-0: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang mtshungs par dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa rnams kyi dpag bsam gyi shing chen po'i mchod pa'i sprin gyi char 'bebs par byed pa'i @321a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-2: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs kyi dam tshig rig sngags kyi dkyil 'khor gyi kho na nyid sgrub par byed pa /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-5: rig pa'i rgyal po'i lha rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-6: gsang sngags kyi lha thams cad spyan 'dren zhing 'gugs par byed pa'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-15: dus kyi chu rnam par nyams pa la so sor bskyed pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-16: de nas rig sngags 'chang gtsang mas khrus byas gos gtsang ba bsgos te yid rtse gcig tu byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-17: sems can thams cad la mchog tu brtse ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-18: byams pa'i sems bsgom par bya'o; ;mchod rten gyi yan lag dang nye ba'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-24: dge 'dun gyi kun dga' ra ba'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321a-30: rgyal po'i pho brang yang rung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321b-0: der rig sngags 'chang gtsang mar gnas pas sa @321b gzhi yongs su brtags pa cha mnyam pa mdzes par khru gnyis kyi tshad kyi dkyil 'khor byas las dang ba byung du ldan pas gru bzhi par cha gzhal ste legs par byi dor byas la shin tu 'jam par bya'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321b-18: rig sngags 'chang gis ches mngon du don yod zhags pa lan bdun bzlas par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321b-19: khro bo'i rgyal po la lan gcig bzlas pas mngon par dbang bskur bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321b-20: don yod pa'i lcags skyu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:321b-21: khro bo lcags kyu dus gcig tu brjod do //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:334a-2: brjod pa tsam gyi mod la dus gsum du gshegs pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi sras gcig pur 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:334b-16: rkun pos rnam par skrag pa dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:334b-22: me dang chus dus byed pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:334b-26: ser ba rnams kyis mi tshugs so //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:334b-28: thams cad byams pa'i yid du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:334b-32: bu mo thams cad dbang du gyur par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:334b-34: bklags pa tsam gyis 'jig rten pa rnams kyi yon tan chen po bskyed pa dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:335b-9: dmyal ba'i 'gro ba chen po bcu drug tu gzhol ba de rnams thams cad skad cig gcig gis yongs su grol lo //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:336a-7: padma'i 'dab ma lta bu'i kha dog dang 'dra bar 'gyur te; phyir zhing de'i lus la reg pa ngan pa 'byung bar mi 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:336a-19: klu ma rungs pa mi bzad pa dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337a-14: de nas bsod nams kyi phung po brjod par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337a-15: 'di bzlas pa tsam gyis bsod nams kyi phung po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337a-16: dge ba'i rtsa ba dang ldan par 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337b-2: dngul gyi me tog gis bkang nas phul ba de bas kyang dge ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337b-3: bsod nams kyi phung po ches mang bar bskyed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337b-4: gang zhig dus gsum pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa mchod cing /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337b-6: bsod nams kyi phung po chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337b-8: de bzhin du bsod nams kyi phung po dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:337b-14: dngul gyi me tog gis bkang pa rnams kyis dus gsum pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:349a-18: de nas rig sngags 'chang gtsang mas gos gtsang ma bgo bar bya'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:349b-3: don yod zhags pa'i lcags kyu dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:350b-12: rdo rje'i ri mo gsum pa dag go /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:350b-23: drag po sna tshogs pa'i gzugs 'chang ba /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:351b-5: dri sna tshogs kyi byug pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:351b-6: bdug pa sna tshogs pas mdzes pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:351b-7: me tog gi phreng ba gcal du bkram pa dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:351b-16: lhag pa nyid byed du bzhug go /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:352a-3: las kyi cho gas gtor ma sbyin par bya /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-5: aom dzva la bi ma le aa mo gha shuddhe h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-7: aom siddhi dzva le aa mo gha buddhi h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-9: aom aa mo gha ba ste tstsha da h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-11: aom aa mo gha ma ni h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-12: gtsug tor bcing ba'i sngags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-13: aom aa mo gha raksha na ba ra da h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-15: aom satva raksha na aa mo gha damshte h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-16: thams cad du gzhan bsrung zhing bde ba'i ched du srung ba'i sngags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-17: aom aa mo gha pra bi sha bhu ba ne h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-19: aom na mo aa mo gha ba ti h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-20: phyag byed pa'i sngags so; ;aom aa mo gha tsa kre h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-22: aom sa ma ya siddha aa mo gha ba ti h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-24: aom aa mo gha pushpe pra ba tsa gandhi ni dza ya sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-30: aom aa mo gha sa ra sam p'u ra ni ra sa ra sa gra ba ti h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-31: thams cad du gtor ma'i sngags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-32: aom aa mo gha tu ti sv'ah'a; mar me'i sngags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-33: aom aa mo gha ba ti tsa ra bi tsa ra sanytsa ra sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-34: thams cad du gnas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:358b-35: gnas thams cad du song ba na rig pa'i rgyal pos bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-0: @359a *// thams cad du las thams cad byed pa rig pa'i gsang sngags sbyar bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-1: gshegs su gsol ba nyid kyang sngags 'dis bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-2: las shin tu rgyas pa gzhan thams cad ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-4: legs par byas pa'i las dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-6: bya ba thams cad sgrub par byed pa gzhan rnams ni; don yod pa'i lcags kyu dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-8: rig pa'i rgyal po'i gsang sngags chen bo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-9: dpa' bo gcig pa'i gsang sngags 'di rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-10: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang gi las rnams bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-11: rtsa ba'i rig pa 'di nyid kyis las thams cad bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-12: de las phyi rol tu gyur pa'i rig pa gzhan ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-14: rig pa 'di ni; bklags pas grub pa'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-15: de nas de la yangs shing rgya che ba'i brtson pa bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-18: ji ltar gsal pa rnams 'byor ba dang bcas shing yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-19: shin tu gsal bar bya ba rnams bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-20: gtsang ma gtsang mas khrus byas te gos gtsang ma bsgo bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-23: mchog tu dang ba bskyed par bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-25: bden par phyi rol tu 'byung bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359a-26: bden par spro ba dang brtson pas 'byung bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-0: ser @359b sna med par 'gyur bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-2: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub kyi lam dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-3: bklags pas grub pa'i rig pa 'di sgrub par byed par 'gyur bar bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-4: sems can thams cad la brtse ba mchog tu bya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-12: cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po chen po 'di gsungs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-13: don yod zhags pa'i rnam par thar pa'i dkyil 'khor yang dag par rmad du byung ba 'di /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-14: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi phyag byas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-15: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs kyi dam tshig thun mong gi gsang ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-16: dkyil 'khor rim par phye ba thams cad kyi gsang ba phyag rgya dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-17: gsang sngags thams cad kyi gsang ba'i cho ga zhib mo 'di 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis gsungs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:359b-26: mi gang yin pa rnams kyang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor chen po dang bcas pa ga la ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-0: de bzhin gshegs pa mngon sum du gyur pa ga la ba der dong @360a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-1: ste lhags nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi spyan sngar song ste zhabs gnyis la mgo bos phyag 'tshal te thal mo sbyar bar gyur pas 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-4: don yod pa'i lcags kyu cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po yang lhag pa'i rgyal po cho ga zhib mo 'di yongs su bsrung ba'i don dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-5: mi nub cing rgyas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-6: cho ga zhib mo'i rgyal po ji lta rnyed pa de bzhin bris pa 'di yongs su rdzogs so ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-8: sngon gyi lo ts'a ba mkhas pa bzhi tsam gyis bgos nas bsgyur ba la bar skabs bar skabs su chad cing mjug ma tshang ba las /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-9: bla ma dus kyi 'khor lo pa chen po chos grags dpal bzang po'i phyag nas rgya dpe byung zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-11: mjug sgyur cig ces bkas bskul ba la brten nas bam po bcu pa'i nang du /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-12: las kyi don kun sgrub par byed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-14: gsang sngags bzlas pa mchog gyis shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360a-16: bam po bcu gnyis pa'i nang du bcom ldan 'das /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-0: 'on kyang don khyad par can gyi ched du zhes pa nas rig sngags 'chang @360b gi lus 'bar bar 'gyur te zhes pa'i bar dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-1: bam po bcu gsum pa'i nang du dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga 'di thos pa tsam dang zhes pa nas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-2: mi gang tshad du bskor bar bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-4: bam po bcu bzhi pa'i nang du padma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-6: yungs kar la yongs su bzlas te zhes pa nas ras dkar pos bkru bar bya zhing lan bdun du zhes pa'i bar dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-7: bam po bcu bzhi pa dang bco lnga pa'i mtshams su dngul gyi pog phor brgyad dang zhes pa nas gnas rnam pa gzhan thams cad du ji ltar yid la byed pa'i bya ba thams cad du byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-9: bam po bcu drug pa dang bcu bdun pa'i mtshams su de nas sbyin sreg gi cho ga bshad par bya ste zhes pa nas phyag rgya'i cho ga dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-12: bam po bcu bdun pa zhes pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-13: de ma thag par bam po bco brgyad pa'i mtshams su de nas rtag tu bzlas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga bshad par bya ste zhes pa nas 'jig rten mgon po'i 'od zer gyi sbyin sreg rab tu grol lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-14: zhes pa'i bar rnams kyi hor khong bas bas shing mjug yongs su rdzogs par sh'akya'i dge slong rin chen grub kyis bsgyur cing zhus pa'i yi ge pa ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-15: yo ga pa grub pa dpal bzang po'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-16: kun tu lha mo thams cad la'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-17: zhes pa nas gter bskul na zhes pa'i bar rgya dpe la mi 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-093-001:360b-18: 'gro ba sems can thams cad la phan par gyur cig
